 <office:body>
  <office:text text:use-soft-page-breaks="true">
   <text:sequence-decls>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Illustration"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Table"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Text"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Drawing"/>
   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">vis et acutula, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conclūsiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten (spetsfundig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slutledning:</text:span></text:span> contortula, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Disclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afstänga, utestänga från hwarandra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">från ngt:</text:span></text:span> pisces habere d-sos, Varr.; mons Arvernos ab Helvetiis, Cs.; Plato - iram et cupiditatem (partes animi) locis d-sit, C.; durare solum et d-re Nerea ponto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ute i hafwet),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dela, uppspärra:</text:span></text:span> mundum, Lucr.; roboris morsus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: i eg. och oeg. bemärkelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utestänga, -sluta, (utstöta), afwisa, hindra:</text:span></text:span> foras aliquem, Pt., Ter.; a portu et perfugio; patrocinium pacis e-sum est hominum errore aut terrore; amicitia nullo loco e-itur; ab omni doctrina oratorem; ab hereditate aliquem; honoribus, a republica; temporibus, tempore, angustiis temporis e-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom omständigheter, tidens knapphet förhindras);</text:span> petitor exceptione e-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på grund af en clausul i lagen förklaras sin talan förlustig),</text:span> C.; mensā hospitem, L.; fore e-i, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i militärisk men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskära:</text:span></text:span> a re frumentariā; Capuā, Cs.; reditu aliquem, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utkläcka:</text:span></text:span> pullos gallina, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluta, afsluta:</text:span></text:span> volumen genethliacon Lucani, St.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afsöndra:</text:span></text:span> locum, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Exclūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utestängande:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innesluta, innestänga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> (seminis) viriditas pubescens vaginis i-tur; in equum Trojanum, in carcere; sumus i-si in compagibus corporis, C.; in carcerem; carcere, moenibus, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inskränka:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spärra, hämma, hindra:</text:span></text:span> viam, L.; dolor vocem alicui, C.; pastinatio i-itur, Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innefatta, -sluta, infoga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Phidias sui similem speciem i-sit in clupeo Minervæ; orationem in epistolam; orationi aliquid; verba versu, C.; sententiam versu, Hor.; numeris i-sus, Ps.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> in populi Romani salute suam i-sam videbat, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluta:</text:span></text:span> crastinus dies fata, Ppt.; epistolam, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innespärrande:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afstänga, -skära, spärra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wägen för en kommande (jfr</text:span> intercipio): iter, C., Cs.; omnes aditus alicui, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en kommande l. hans rörelse):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af-, inne-, utestänga; förhindra:</text:span></text:span> adventum inimicorum suis corporibus; fugam; dolore i-or, quominus scribam, C.; angustiis aliquem, Cs.; animam, spiritum, spem, L.; sæpe illos æquore i-sit hiems et terruit auster euntes, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt, med härar och deras rörelser såsom object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskära:</text:span></text:span> hostem commeatu; a re frumentaria; aliquem ab exercitu, Cs.; a <text:soft-page-break/>castris aliquem, L.; metuo, ne i-amini, ut exire non liceat, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interclūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innestängning:</text:span></text:span> clausulas animæ i. atque angustiæ spiritus attulerunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Parenthes:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occlūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillsluta, -stänga, innelåsa:</text:span></text:span> fores pessulis, ædem, Pt.; tabernas; nihil obsignatum aut o-sum habere alicui, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innesluta, stäfja, tillstoppa:</text:span></text:span> odium pectore o-sum, C.; libidinem contumeliis, Ter.; linguam alicui, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I förwäg, framför, för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stänga, spärra; afskära, omöjliggöra, förhindra:</text:span></text:span> portas, Cs.; aditum alicui; curiam sibi aliqua re; orbem terrarum alicui; hiems cursus maritimos, C.; fores, Ppt.; linguam cani, Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öppna, upplåta:</text:span></text:span> armarium, Pt.; portas, Ov., Ppt.; domum; virtus immeritis mori caelum; pectus, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framdraga; blotta:</text:span></text:span> thesauros tellure; ensem, Vg.; operta, Hor.; iram <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(röja),</text:span> Enn. ap. C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillsluta, innestänga:</text:span></text:span> matronas in carcerem, Js.; templum, Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēclūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afstänga:</text:span></text:span> incientes oves <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(innestänga på afskildt ställe),</text:span> Varr.; aqua s-sa tenetur; impiis iter est s-sum a consilio deorum, C.; s-sum nemus, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skilja, utestänga:</text:span></text:span> corpore vitam, Pt.; solvite corde metum, Teucri, s-ite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låten fara)</text:span> curas, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēclūsōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskildt rum:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Claudo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Claudus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Claudus</text:span> (Clūdus, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halt, haltande, ofärdig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> sutor, Pt.; deus, C.; pes, Hor.; pars corporis, Vg.; altero pede, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. carmina alterno versu c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om det elegiska versmåttet),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda l. abstracta ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bristfällig; wacklande:</text:span></text:span> naves, L.; fides, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Claudeo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Claudo</text:span> (clodo), (-surus), 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och 3.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.</text:span> (clodo): pecus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. l. oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara ojemn, ofärdig, ofullkomlig, bristfällig:</text:span></text:span> oratio; orator; beata vita ex aliqua parte, C.; respublica altera parte, Liv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Claudĭco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clōdĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> graviter ex vulnere; hic clodicat, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wackla, sakna grund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stadga; brista, wara efter:</text:span></text:span> tota amicitia; in nullo officio, C.; in comoedia nos c-amus, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clōdĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Haltande:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Claudĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halthet:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clavicula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clavis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Claviger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clava <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Clavis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clāvis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> claudo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nyckel:</text:span></text:span> ædium, Pt.; horreorum, C.; portarum, Sa.; adultera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eftergjord),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en de gamles nycklar liknande krökt pinne, hwarmed trillan</text:span> (trochus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sattes i gång:</text:span> Ppt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clāvīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten nyckel:</text:span> Cs. Germ. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klyndig qwist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på winstocken, hwarmed den håller sig uppe:</text:span> vitis ut se erigat, c-is suis quasi membris, quidquid est nacta, amplectitur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clāvĭger</text:span>, ĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nyckelbärare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om</text:span> Janus), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conclāve</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kammare, enskildt rum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> atrium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> cavædium = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sal):</text:span> Pt., Ter., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stall:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clavo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clavus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Claus . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clavula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clava.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clavulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clavus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clāvus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spik, plugg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> trabalis, C., Hor.; ferreus, corneus; c-o figere aliquid, Cato; c-um defigere, pangere, L.; transtra confixa c-is, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i serskilda uttryck:</text:span> figere c-um, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom officiel årsbeteckning,</text:span> L. (VII. 3). - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> trabali c-o figere beneficium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra fast och beståndande);</text:span> c-o c-um ejicere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fördrifwa ondt med ondt),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liktorn;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> elakartad </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">knöl</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utwäxt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en kropp:</text:span> Pn., Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Roder, styrpinne:</text:span></text:span> c-um tenere, C.; regere, Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> c-um imperii tenere, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bräm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (inwäfdt) på tunica såsom ståndsbeteckning:</text:span> latus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på senators),</text:span> angustus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på riddares),</text:span> L., Hor.; Qu. XI. 3. 138.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clāvārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skospikspenningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för soldater):</text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clāvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med spik beslå, besätta:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bebräma:</text:span></text:span> vestimenta clavis intertexta c-ata dicuntur, Fs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clāvŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten spik, nubb:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angustĭclāvius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lātĭclāvius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se</text:span> Clavus 4): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med smalt, med bredt bräm = af riddare-, af senatorsstånd; riddare-, senators-:</text:span> tribunus a., l., Su.; tunica 1., Val. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Philologus, 1869. 277).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lazŏmĕnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i mindre Asien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clazŏmĕnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lĕanthes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clēmens,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sakta, stilla, lugn:</text:span></text:span> vita c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> dura), Ter.; flamina, Catl.; amnis, Ov.; gradus, Gell. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till sinnet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saktmodig, wänlig; mild, barmhertig, god;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tam:</text:span></text:span> servitus; c. cunctis arridens, Ter.; in disputando c.; castigatio c.; judex c. et misericors; cupio me esse c-em; ab innocentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till förswar för, mot),</text:span> C.; rumor, Sa.; legis interpres c., L.; c-ius genus columbarum, Varr.; c-ens peperci, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clēmenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stilla, sakta:</text:span></text:span> sequi c., Pt.; molle et c. editum jugum; juga c-ius assurgunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots. brant),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saktmodigt, mildt:</text:span></text:span> audire; accipere aliquem leniter et c., C.; jus dicere, Cs.; liberos tractare mollius et c-ius, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clēmentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mildhet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäderlekens l. klimatets:</text:span> hiemis, Col.; caeli, Luc. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinnets (isynnerhet mot felande):</text:span> mansuetudo et c.; placabilitas et c.; in crudelitatem conversa c.; popularis est c., C.; pro sua c-ā conservare aliquem, Cs.; spes in c-ā populi Rom. sita, Sa.; violare alicujus c-am, N.; ducis, Ov.; leonis in supplices, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclēmens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclēmenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hård, hårdt:</text:span></text:span> dictator; verbum i-ius, L.; i. dicere, invehi in aliquem, Ter.; Pt.; L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclēmentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårdhet, omildhet:</text:span></text:span> caeli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäderlekens),</text:span> Col.; divom, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lēmens, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn</text:span> (T.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lĕŏbis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lĕon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. Personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lĕōnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Grekland.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clĕōnæus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lĕŏpătra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clĕpo,</text:span> psi, ptum, 3.: v. arch. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enligt</text:span> Varro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besl. med</text:span> clam): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stjäla, bort-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppsnappa:</text:span></text:span> si quis clepsit - (aut) cui cleptum erit, Form. juris ap. C., Liv.; rape, clepe, Pt.; ignem dolo Prometheus, Acc. ap. C.; Spartæ pueri c. discunt, C.; a foro aliquid, Lucil.; auribus verba, Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clepta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjuf:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clepsy̆dra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattenur, timglas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwarur watten utrann genom ett fint hål):</text:span> ad c-am latrare (dicere) didicit, C.; c-am dare, addere, i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tid för föredrag,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clibănus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flyttbart kök, ugn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af metall):</text:span> Pn., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clibănārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pansarklädd:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cliens,</text:span> entis (C.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clienta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> (Pt., Hor.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> clueo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Client, skyddsling, skyddsförwandt, underlydande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om enskilde Romare i förhållande till deras</text:span> patroni, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett förhållande, hwilket i äldre tider war halfborgarens till hans </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wärjoman l. skyddsherre, i sednare tider blott den simple l. obemedlade mannens till en hög </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gynnare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stundom såsom sakförswarare):</text:span> a patriciis tentata res est, si dispositis c-ibus - (plebejos) singulos a coitionibus deterrere possent, L.; contra cognatos pro c-e testari, Cato; patrocinio se usos aut c-es appellari mortis instar putant, C.; Virgilius c. nobilium juvenum, Hor.; tritam lacernam dare c-i, Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> turba scriptorum c. Bacchi, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hela folk i förhållande till en förnäm Romare såsom</text:span> patronus: Siculi c-es mei, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> de off. I. 11).<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i icke romerska förhållanden om enskildes (stamhöfdingars) l. folks </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">underlydande: Vasaller:</text:span></text:span> c-es Orgetorigis (b. G. I. 4); equites Gallorum plurimos circum se ambactos c-es habent; c. Hæduorum, Cs.; Segestes (Germanus) cum magna c-um manu, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clientēla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clientel, skyddsförwandtskap:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstr. (förhållande af skyddsling):</text:span> commendare se alicui in c-am, Ter.; conferre se in alicujus c-am, esse in alicujus c-ā, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concr. (skaror af clienter):</text:span> Hæduorum magnæ c-æ erant, Cs.; c-æ et servitia alicujus, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clientŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ringa client:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clīma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. lutning):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luftstreck, trakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jordstycke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på 60 qvadratalnar:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīmactēr</text:span>, ēris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. trappsteg l. afsats; deraf): kritisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afsats</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">punkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i menniskolifwet, nemligen de med 7 multiplicerade talen, serskildt det 63:dje:</text:span> Pn., Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīmactērĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör en climacter (kritisk):</text:span> habes tempus c-um, sed evades, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīmax</text:span>, ăcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. stege): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stigande, stegring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttryck</text:span> (climax): Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clinamen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clino.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>līnĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīnĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läkarekonst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid sjuksängen,</text:span> κλίνη): c-en Hippocrates instituit, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīnĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läkare:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clīno,</text:span> 1.: (verbum fere inusitatum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böja:</text:span></text:span> ungula c-ta, Cic. (Arat.).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīnāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: principiorum c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">atomernas </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjning, afwikning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från den lodräta rigtningen:</text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acclīnis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lutad, lutande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stödd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> arborum trunco a., Vg.; torus a. gradibus eburnis, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjd för:</text:span></text:span> falsis animus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acclīno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta emot:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> castra tumulo, L.; se ad illum, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta åt:</text:span></text:span> ad causam senatus se a., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēclīno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, åt sidan:</text:span> atomi d-nt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från sin lodräta rigtning);</text:span> a <text:soft-page-break/>Capua, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortwända, böja; wika åt sidan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med:</text:span> se recta regione viāi, Lucr.; agmen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med tåget),</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wika af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> oratio illuc d-vit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid:</text:span> dies in vesperam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lutar),</text:span> Col.; d-ta jam ætate <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i framskriden ålder),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afwika, förirra sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sedligt hänseende):</text:span> consuetudo de via d-vit; a religione officii, C.; amor d-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(råkar på afwägar),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>4. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undwika</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">a re</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">rem</text:span>): ab his vitiis est diligenter d-dum; a malis d.; urbem; vitia; ea quæ nocitura videntur; ictum, certamen, C.; regionem, Sen.; impudicitiam uxoris - d-ns, T.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sitt tycke </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wända sig bort:</text:span></text:span> Lycoridem Cyri torret amor: Cyrus in asperam d-at Pholoen, Hor.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i gramm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Härleda, böja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (neml. om både flexion och derivation, i mots. till</text:span> impositio = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stamordets bildning):</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēclīnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjning, lutning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt sidan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afwikning:</text:span></text:span> corporis d-e vitare aliquid; atomorum, C. <text:line-break/>2. d. mundi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= lutning mot polerna)</text:span> = clima: Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undwikande:</text:span></text:span> periculi, laboris, C. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i gramm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">all </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Formbildning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (härledning och böjning),</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Declination</text:span></text:span> = flexio nominum, Diom.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēclīnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjning:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indēclīnābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oböjlig, oföränderlig:</text:span></text:span> animus, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indēclīnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförändrad, ståndaktig:</text:span></text:span> amicitia, Ov</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclīno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta, kasta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ett håll:</text:span> in unum latus i-ant omnes, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en här: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wika:</text:span></text:span> legiones i-ant, T. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om solen, dagen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjunka, luta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till nedgång:</text:span> i-at meridies, Hor.; dies in vesperam, Ct.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinnet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en mening, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wara böjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för:</text:span> sententia senatus ad pacem cum Pyrrho faciendam i-bat; intelliges, ecquid i-ent ad hoc meum consilium adjuvandum, C.; hos ut sequar, i-at animus; in hoc consilium maxime i-nt; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.,</text:span> L.; rei (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Hor.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lyckan, omständigheter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjunka, taga en olycklig wändning, försämras:</text:span></text:span> si fortuna belli i-at, omnibus periculum erit, L.; initia fere meliora sunt, finis i-at, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i synnerhe</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T2">reflex.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medialt; serskildt</text:span> pt. pf. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">comp.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höja, luta, sänka, wända åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett håll:</text:span> malos, L.; genua arenis, Ov.; caput in latus i-re; cervix utrolibet i-ta, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bringa att wika;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wika:</text:span></text:span> i-atur Romana acies, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om solen, dagen:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">reflex.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjunka, luta:</text:span></text:span> i-to ad pomeridianum tempus die, C.; sol se i., L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åt ett håll, om personliga och sakliga object):</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>quam vellem, te in Stoicos i-visses; i. aliquid ad suæ causæ commodum; culpam i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kasta)</text:span> in aliquem, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra böjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra wacklande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i öfwertygelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beweka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öfwertyga, -tala):</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wacklande, böjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> i. animos in sententiam; hæc animum i-ant, ut credam, L.; i-ri timore; primo impelli leviter judicem oportet, ut jam i-to reliqua incumbat oratio, C.; plebs ad plebem i-tior erat, L.; misericordia judicem i-at, Qu.; i-ta ad suspicionem mens, T.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förändra:</text:span></text:span> color in luteum i-tus, Pn.; partim adverbium est neque i-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(böjes),</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gifwa utslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en sak, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afgöra:</text:span></text:span> - te in otium referas, præcipue nunc jam i-tā victoriā, C.; fraus rem i-vit, L. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gifwa en rigtning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt det sämre, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bringa att sjunka;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sjunka, falla:</text:span></text:span> fortuna omnia i-bat, L.; fortuna se i-at, Cs.; fortuna i-ta et prope jacens, C.; res i-ta, L.; domus, Vg.<text:line-break/>f. vox i-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> flexa) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">drillande:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclīnābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt böjlig:</text:span></text:span> in pravum, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclīnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjning, lutning, kastning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ett håll: absol.:</text:span> C.; corporis, Qu.; mundi (= clima), Vitr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">händelsernas, omständigheternas </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wändning, omkastning:</text:span></text:span> minimis momentis maximæ i-es temporum fiunt; populi Romani vectigalia perlevi sæpe momento fortunæ, i-e temporis pendent; fit ad meliorem spem i., C.; causæ, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wändning, omkastning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tänkesätt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">böjelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn, ngt:</text:span> voluntatum repentina i.; i-e voluntatis propendere in aliquem, C.; utendum ea i-e ratus Cæsar; principum i. in hos, offensio in illos, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (höjning och sänkning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">omkastning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af röst, ton:</text:span> vocis, C.<text:line-break/>d. verbi i. = declinatio (quod vide): Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclīnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjningsform:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böja, luta framåt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mare in litus, Ov.; capita in aliquam partem p-antur, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bringa nära sitt afgörande;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medialt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sjunka:</text:span></text:span> re p-tā; rem p-tam adjuvare, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕclīnis</text:span> (-us, Vop.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bakåt lutande, lutad:</text:span></text:span> Ov., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕclīno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta, böja bakåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till hwila):</text:span> caput, C.; alces ad arbores se r-ant, Cs.; in gramine r-tus; nullum otium a labore me r-at, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>līo, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Muserna, historiens gudinna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clip . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clupeus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>listhĕnes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clītellæ,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klöf-, packsadel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på hästar, mulor, åsnor):</text:span> Pt., Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordspråk:</text:span> c-as bovi imponere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätta bocken till trädgårdsmästare),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clītellārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bär packsadel:</text:span> muli, Col., Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>līternum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ital. Stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lītor, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Arcadien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clītŏrĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lītumnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Umbrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lītus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clīvus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pl.</text:span> -a, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.,</text:span> Cato; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besl. med</text:span> clino?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sluttande wäg, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Backe, lid:</text:span></text:span> c. Capitolinus, C.; descendere per c-um; nituntur longo vestigia ponere c-o, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttning, lutning:</text:span></text:span> mensæ clivus (fit impari tertio pede), tollitur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(undanrödjes)</text:span> subditā testā; pennæ c-o crevisse videntur, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīvōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Backig:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clīvŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten backe:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acclīvis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acclīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som bär uppför, sluttande upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mot ett ställe):</text:span> pars viæ est a-is, C.; aditus leniter a-is, Cs.; tramite a-o, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acclīvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i abstract mening):</text:span> collis, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēclīvis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pl.</text:span> d-va, dubia l., Ov.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttande nedåt, stupande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> latitudo, Sa.; collis d. ad flumen; a summo æqualiter d., Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> mulier ætate d-i, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēclīvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> nedåt:</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīvis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīvus</text:span> (Pt., Varr., Sen.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nedåt sluttande:</text:span></text:span> via; per p-e, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om tider) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som närmar sig till, håller på att öfwergå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i -:</text:span> Junius in Julium est p-us, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt, beqwäm:</text:span></text:span> in p-i res est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(går lätt),</text:span> Pt., Ter.; cursus facilis et p.; p-e est dictu; facilia, p-ia, jucunda, C.; cetera omnia plana et p-ia, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjd, benägen, fallen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> a labore ad lubidinem, Ter.; ad morbos, C.; egestas sceleri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(leder lätt till),</text:span> Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīve</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīvi</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīvĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedåt, raskt, lätt:</text:span></text:span> C. (Madv. de Fin. 754).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōclīvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttning nedåt:</text:span></text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Benägenhet, anlag:</text:span></text:span> ad morbos, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕclīvis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluttande:</text:span></text:span> campus, Pal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cloāca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Pn. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> cluo = purgare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i det äldre språket): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cloak,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> underjordisk (murad) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afloppskanal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för watten och orenlighet (serskildt</text:span> C. Maxima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom, från forum till Tibern):</text:span> c. receptaculum purgamentorum urbis; c-am ducere, agere, L.; ex c-a arcem facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordspråk</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af en mygga en kamel),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cloācālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hörer till</text:span> c.: Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cloācŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>loācīna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.<text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>luācīna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillnamn för Venus:</text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clodico = Claudico, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Claudus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Clodius = Claudius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clodo = Claudo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Claudus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>loelius (Cluĭlius): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fornrom. (albanskt) slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clostrum = Claustrum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lōtho, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Parcerna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cluacina = Cloacina.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cludo = I. Claudo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cludus = Claudus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>luentius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clueo,</text:span> ēre, 2. (cluo, Pt., Aus.): v. arch.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Heta, nämnas, sägas; wara:</text:span></text:span> vir meus victor cluet; ita sit, ut nomen c., Pt.; unde ignis c. mortalibus divisus, Pac. ap. C.; (animalia) non minus quam homines inter se nota c-ent, Lucr. II. 351.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclŭtus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inclĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frejdad, berömd:</text:span></text:span> i-a justitia religioque ea tempestate Numæ erat; templum divitiis i-um, L.; gloria, Vg., Hor.; -issimus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cluilius = Cloelius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clūnis,</text:span> is (frequ. in pl.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gump, bakdel, länd:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.; pulcræ equorum, Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clūnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bak-:</text:span></text:span> pes, Av.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clūnĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clūnĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Cluo = Clueo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Cluo,</text:span> ĕre ”antiqui purgare dicebant”, Pn. XV. 36.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lŭpea, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clŭpeæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">udde och stad i Africa.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clŭpeus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clŭpeum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clĭpeus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clĭpeum</text:span> (Cly̆peus, -um): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rund sköld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af metall), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skifwa:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> specielt</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förswarswapen i krig (mots.</text:span> scutum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aflång sköld):</text:span> C., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ram, medaillon</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för bröstbilder (porträtt):</text:span> c. argenteum cum imagine Hasdrubalis, L. (origo plena virtutis, faciem reddi in scuto cujusque, qui usus fuerit illo, Pn. 5. 4).<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> caeli c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(solen),</text:span> Enn., Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags meteor:</text:span> c. flagrans, ardens, Sen., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clŭpeo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rusta med </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköld:</text:span></text:span> Pac.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clŭpeātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköldrustad, -wäpnad:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Pt., Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som befinner sig i ram, på medaillon:</text:span> imago, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Clūrīnum</text:span> pecus = simia, Pt. Truc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lūsium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clūsīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lūsius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den tillslutande, binamn för Janus:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>lŭvia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Samnium.<text:line-break/></text:span>Clŭviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ly̆mĕnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. Personnamn.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cly̆mĕnēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: C-a proles (Phaëthon).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Clyp . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clupeus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Clyster,</text:span> ēris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klystir-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lavements-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spruta, klystir:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ly̆tæmnestra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn</text:span> (uxor Agamemnonis).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ly̆tĭē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>næus (Gnæus),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>nēus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. prænomen</text:span> (Cn.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>nĭdus (Gnĭdus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Carien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cnĭdĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>nōsus (Gnōsus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Creta.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cnōsĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Co = Cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Con <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättningar framför vocaler och</text:span> h (coagulum, coëo, coitio, cooperio, cohæreo).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coact . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cogo, Ago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coævus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aevum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coagm . . .,<text:line-break/>Coagul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cogo, Ago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coaxo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta som grodor:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōcălus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">konung på Sicilien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coccum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skarlakan (-ssaft, -färg, -tyg):</text:span></text:span> c-o tingere, Hor.; funis c-o nexus, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccĭnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skarlakansfärgad:</text:span> Pn., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccĭna</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skarlakanskläder:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccĭnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klädd i skarlakan:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccȳ̆mēla</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en äpplesort:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coccyx</text:span>, ȳgis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gök:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cochlĕa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snäcka, snigel:</text:span></text:span> in c-am retortus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spiralformig),</text:span> Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skruf, skrufmor, spindel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en preß:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. genus ostii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(spiraltrappa?)</text:span></text:span> angustum et obscurum, Varr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattenpump:</text:span></text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cochlĕar</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cochlĕāre</text:span>, āris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sked, skedblad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom mått):</text:span> Col., Pn., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cochlĕārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sked:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rum, der (ätliga) sniglar hållas:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cochlis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en art ädelsten:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. columna c-is, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med spiraltrappa inuti, sådan som</text:span> Trajani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Antonini <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">colonner,</text:span> Curiosum &amp; Notitia urbis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ocles, ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enögd:</text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. tillnamn</text:span> (Horatius C.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coct . . .,<text:line-break/>Coculum,<text:line-break/>Cocus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coquo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōcȳtus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i underjorden.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cōcȳtĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coda = Cauda.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>odēta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fält på andra sidan om Tibern i Rom,</text:span> Su. Cs. 39 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Paul. Diac. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bewuxet med</text:span> frutices in modum codarum equinarum).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Codex, Codicill . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Caudex.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏdrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coelebs = Caelebs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coeles, -stis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Caelum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>oelēsy̆rĭa (Coelē Sy̆rĭa = κοίλη Συρία), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Syrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coelibatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Caelebs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coelicola,<text:line-break/>Coelifer,<text:line-break/>Coeligenus,<text:line-break/>Coelipotens,<text:line-break/>Coelitus,<text:line-break/>Coelum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Caelum.<text:line-break/>Coelimontium,<text:line-break/>Coelius = Cael . . .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coena,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> (caena, cena, antiq. caesna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> cesna): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måltid,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> neml. hufwudmåltiden på dagen, i sednare tider, d. w. s. ungefär från och med 2:dra seklet f. Chr., den sista måltiden, som började på eftermiddagen kl. 3 ungf., och wanligtwis warade till sängdags; i äldre tider war enl.</text:span> Festus c. = cibus meridianus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> prandium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som efterföljdes af en</text:span> vesperna: c. nuptialis, Pt.; dubia, Ter.; genialis, saliaris, auguralis, C.; magna, brevis, Hor.; subita, Sen.; abundantissima; c. recta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som</text:span> in natura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gifwes, mots.</text:span> sportula), Su.; ante, inter, post <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(före, under, efter),</text:span> Cato, C.; ad c-am abducere, C.; vocare, Ter.; ducere, Hor.; invitare, C.; ire, itare, C.; venire, Ter.; redire a c-a; condicere alicui (ad c-am), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lofwa sig bort);</text:span> imperare puero c-am; facere, obire c-am, C.; adhibere aliquem c-æ, Su.; c-am ducere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> producere ad - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sitta wid bordet till -),</text:span> Hor.; prima, secunda etc. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afdelningen af måltiden, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rätten),</text:span></text:span> Mt.; caput c-æ, Cic.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Matrum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> men sedermera</text:span> ”quia olim in superiore parte aedium coenitatum est”) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ofwanrum, rum i </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfre wåningen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl. bebodt af betjening l. uthyrdt åt fattigt folk:</text:span> C., L.; domesticorum c-a, Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till, syftar på</text:span> c.: spes, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coeno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hålla</text:span></text:span> (coena) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">måltid; spisa:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: apud aliquem, cum aliquo, in triclinio, bene, melius, frugaliter, libenter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med god smak),</text:span> turpiter, C.; c-vimus una, Hor.; foris, Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har spisat,</text:span> C.; c-atum est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der spisades),</text:span> L.; N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: aves, aprum, Hor.; c-atæ noctes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med måltid),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Matsal, -rum:</text:span></text:span> capax populi, Sen.; modica, Pn.; laqueata, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātōria</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måltidsdrägt:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenātŭrio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Desid.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wilja spisa:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ständigt spisa:</text:span></text:span> foris; apud aliquem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten måltid:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concoenātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spisande tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incoeno</text:span>, 1.: i-ante eo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">då han spisade derinne</text:span> (in spelunca), Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incoenātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej har spisat:</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incoenis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcoeno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spisa i hast:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coenosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coenum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coenum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (caenum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smuts, gyttja, träck:</text:span></text:span> C., Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> ex c-o plebejo consulatum extrahere, L.; hoc c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en person),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coenōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smutsig, gyttjig:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Coepio,</text:span> Pt),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coepi</text:span> (coēpi, Lucr.), (coepisse),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">coeptus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Verb. defect.,</text:span> 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Började</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (börjat), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">börjad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">handlingsverb (dock sällan med object af nomen, wanligare i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligast med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">infinit.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">activ eller passiv allt efter verbets egen form):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> poenitet c-isse; c-it agere; dicere; loqui; habere spem, C.; si quidquam hic turbarum c-eris, Ter.; proelio nostros lacessere c-erunt; lapides jaci c-ti sunt, Cs.; homines c-ere senatum criminando plebem exagitare; bellum c-tum est; res in senatu agitari c-ta est, Sa.; dixit, Romanos bellum c-turos esse; c-ta urbis magnitudo; agi deinde de concordia c-tum, L.; bellum c-tum. Vg.; opus, iter c-tum, Ov.; ignis c-tus, luce coepta (= orta), T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span> coepit = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Började tala:</text:span></text:span> silentio facto ita c., L.; sic c.; talia c., Vg.; ad hunc modum c., T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> T. coeptus:<text:line-break/>a. = factus, institutus: limes a Tiberio c-us; amphitheatrum apud Fidenas c-tum, T.<text:line-break/>b. = ortus: ignis, lux, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i neutral bemärkelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">infinit.</text:span>: c. esse Romæ; c-erunt rapinæ fieri, C.; - tum circumveniri innocentes, alia hujuscemodi fieri coepere, Sa.; amphora c-it institui: currente rotā cur urceus exit?, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">infinit.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja; utgå, härröra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från:</text:span> silentium, deditio c-it; his ex virtute nobilitas c-it, Sa.; pugna c-it, L.; obsidium; proditio c-it e domo Scævini, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coeptum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Företag, påbegynt werk:</text:span></text:span> audax, L., Vg.; c-is intervenit bellum, L.; annuere c-is, Vg.; desistere c-o, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coepto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ifwer): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom handlingsverb: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja, begynna, taga sig före, företaga, försöka;</text:span></text:span> quid hic c-as?, Ter.; c-at constringere, C.; primi seditionem c-verant; arma, insidias; coërcere c-bat; c-tam libertatem omisere, T.<text:line-break/>2. verbum neutrum: c-ante legionum motu, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coeptus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begynnelse:</text:span></text:span> primi appetendi c-us (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occoepi</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Verb. def.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Började:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coërc . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Arceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coero, arch. = Curo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coerul . . . = Caerul . . .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coetus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coëo, Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>oeus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn</text:span> (Titan).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōgĭto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> co-agito, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. fl.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm., i motsats till tala, handla</text:span> (dicere, agere): c. et providere et dicere in nullo corporum genere inest; eloqui copiose, acute c.; c. prudenter, agere considerate; agendi c-dique sollertia, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tänka efter, tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, öfwer ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwertänka, besinna, betänka:</text:span></text:span> sumere spatium ad c-dum; secum, cum animo suo c.; de negotiis, de animo, de amicitia; meditari aut aliquid aliud attentius c.; hæc c-ans soleo sæpe mirari; non c-ant, ea sibi accidere posse, C.; c-arat, hæc posse in itinere accidere, Cs.; fac c-es, in quantā calamitate sis, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka sig, föreställa sig, hafwa för sina tankar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förhoppningar):</text:span> c. Homeri faciem; c. tempus inimicitiarum; celeritas tanta, quanta c-i vix potest; hæc significant, nos etiam futura c-are; c. dictaturam; quæ potest esse in vita jucunditas, quum dies noctesque cogitandum sit, jam jamque esse moriendum?, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">taga i öfwerwägande, öfwerwäga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngt, som är att göra), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om ett företag, en plan, ett beslut):</text:span> injuria c-ata; consilia c-ata <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> calida = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ej öfwertänkta);</text:span> scelus, C.; multæ res eum hortabantur, quare sibi eam rem c-ndam putaret; non jam ut aliquid acquireret, sed ut incolumem exercitum reduceret, c-bat; ne quam occasionem rei bene gerendæ dimitteret, c-bat, Cs.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka, tänka på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hafwa i sinnet, för afsigt; afse, ärna, tillärna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tänka, ärna:</text:span></text:span> ad disturbandas nuptias, Ter.; de populi Romani pernicie; facinus c-atum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillärnad, i motsats till</text:span> perfectum); hoc jamdudum c-o; quæ c-rat, perfecit; nocere c-at; quid ad hæc dicere c-as?, C.; de bello eadem, quæ antea, c-bat; adoriri c-bat, Cs.; quid bellicosus Cantaber - c-et -; c-at uti, dare, Hor.; quid c-et Auster, sol tibi signa dabit, Vg. <text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wara sinnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngn:</text:span> Carthagini jam dudum male c-nti bellum denuntio; amabiliter in aliquem, C.; amice de aliquo, N. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tanke:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i theoretisk men.:</text:span> c-a eloqui, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afsigt, plan:</text:span></text:span> c-a perficere, C.; patefacere, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänkbar:</text:span></text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som går i tankar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tankfull:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtāte</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtāto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med eftertanke, öfwerläggning:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänkande, tanke:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänkande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom själsförmögenhet l. handling, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tanke, föreställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (phantasi):</text:span> homo c-is est particeps; c. in se vertitur; c-e complecti, comprehendere, fingere, percipere, præcipere aliquid; hæc c-e magis, quam re separari possunt; c-em a consuetudine abducere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i concret men. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tanke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (det som tänkes):</text:span> mandare literis c-es suas; omnes c-es suas in rem humilem contemptamque abjicere, C.; stulta, Cs.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänkande, begrundande, öfwertänkande:</text:span></text:span> tacita c-e a solitudine abstrahi; tempus ponere in acerrima c-e; subitam orationem commentatio c-oque facile vincit, C. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tanke = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopp, beräkning, afsigt:</text:span></text:span> inducere alicuius animum in spem c-emque meliorem; dubitatio significat c-em injuriæ; c., quantam illa res sit habitura utilitatem, C.; c. reparandæ classis, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōgĭtātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänkande:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excōgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttänka; upptänka, -finna:</text:span></text:span> acutus ad e-dum; admirabatur Scævolæ ingenium, qui e-sset, nasci prius oportere, quam mori; scelus fingere aut e., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excōgĭtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttänkt, utsökt:</text:span></text:span> C., Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excōgĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttänkande, utfunderande:</text:span></text:span> ea e-em habent non difficilem, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom</text:span> pars eloquentiæ = inventio, id.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excōgĭtātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: id.: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnexcōgĭtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Icke upptänkt:</text:span></text:span> novum et i-um antea remedium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incōgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka, hafwa i sinnet mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> fraudem socio (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incōgĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tanklös:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otänkbar:</text:span></text:span> Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incōgĭtans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tanklös:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incōgĭtantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tanklöshet:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incōgĭtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oöfwertänkt:</text:span></text:span> opus, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetänksam:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan att ha </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tänkt sig för, oförberedd:</text:span></text:span> dicere, Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcōgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förut påtänka, betänka:</text:span></text:span> facinus p-tum, L.; plura, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcōgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter och åter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besinna, begrunda:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cognat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nascor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Cognit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cognosco, Nosco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cognom . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nomen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cogo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cohibeo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Habeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏhors,</text:span> rtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> Chors, Cors) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fyrkantigt sluten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gård</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en</text:span> villa rustica: c. conjungitur ex pluribus tectis; circum c-em pecus coërcetur; c. exterior, interior, Varr.; c. pecudum, gallinarum, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(infanteri-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trupp, cohort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af Romarnes italiske bundsförwandter:</text:span> auxiliaria, Sa.; auxiliares c-es, L.; c-ium, turmarum, legionum tibicines, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sednare (ungf. från bundsförwandt-krigen): af romerska borgarehären:</text:span> c. legionaria, veterana, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. cohors prætoria = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fältherres lifwakt:</text:span> Cs., Sa.; p-æ, prætorianæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kejsarnes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lifwakt, garde:</text:span></text:span> novem p-æ c-es, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerhufwud enskilda, icke i legioner förenade infanteri-afdelningar, såsom:</text:span> c-es veteranæ, Sa., T.; c-es urbanæ (III), vigilum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wakttrupper i hufwudstaden,</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om främmande härar:</text:span> Hannibalis, Juv.<text:line-break/>3. equestris c., Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Suite, följe, skara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som omgifwer ngn, isynnerhet en furstlig person (medlem af kejsarefamiljen) l. en provins-höfding:</text:span> prætoris, C.; Cybebes, Catl.; c. (Tiberii in Asiam proficiscentis), Hor.; c. nobilium, Ct.; laboriosa Ulixis, Ov.; c. Drusi, T.; c. amicorum, Su.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skara, swärm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> nova febrium c., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhortālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wistas, uppfödes i hönsgården:</text:span> aves, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏhortĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten cohort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (trupp):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coitio, Coitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coëo, Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlăphus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knytnäfweslag:</text:span></text:span> alicui infringere c-um, Ter.; incutere alicui, Juv.; ducere, Qu.; c-is percutere, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏlax, ăcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Smickraren, titel på en comoedi af Menander:</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>olchus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">S.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Colcher, colchisk, folkslagsnamn (wid</text:span> Pontus Euxinus).<text:line-break/>Colchĭăcus,<text:line-break/>Colchĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>olchis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>2. Colchis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Colchernes land.</text:span><text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">colchisk qwinna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōlēpium</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (Petr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōlīphium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gladiatorskost:</text:span></text:span> comedere c., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coleus = Culeus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colina = Culina.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colis = Caulis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Collare, -laris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Collum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collatatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ollātia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.<text:line-break/></text:span>Collātīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collatio,<text:line-break/>Collatitius,<text:line-break/>Collativus,<text:line-break/>Collator,<text:line-break/>Collatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Confero, Fero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collect . . ., Colleg . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕgo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colliciæ,<text:line-break/>Colliciaris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liqueo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colliculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Collis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colligatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colligo (-āre), Ligo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colligo (-ĕre) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕgo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collimit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Limes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Collis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colliquiæ = Colliciæ.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> cello): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kulle, höjd:</text:span></text:span> nitidissimus et viridissimus, C.; saluberrimus, L.; altus, supinus, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om Roms 7 kullar, enkannerligen</text:span> Viminalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Quirinalis.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäxer, finnes på</text:span> c.: herba, Ppt.; vinea, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i Rom:</text:span> regio c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som omfattade de nord-östlige kullarne);</text:span> porta c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på</text:span> Quirinalis), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collisio,<text:line-break/>Collisus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Collido, Lædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collocutio,<text:line-break/>Colloquium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colloquor, Loquor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collubus = Collybus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">-us</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Pt., Cato): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hals:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> 1. (menniskors och djurs):</text:span> procerum et tenue c. (Ciceronis adolescentis); secare c. ali cui; committere c. alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta sig halshugga),</text:span> C.; c-o dare brachia circum, Vg.; colla alicujus tenere blandis lacertis, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på döda föremål:</text:span> amphoræ, Cato; papaveris, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: offula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som är af halsstycke?),</text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collāre</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halsband, -boja:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcollo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">af halsen:</text:span></text:span> in collo est: decolles cave, Cæc. ap. Non.; apud veter es (decollo) decipio significat, ut Lucilius: quibus <text:soft-page-break/>fructibus me decollavi, Diom. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid</text:span> decōlo).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halshugga:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succollo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyfta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">på halsen, skuldrorna:</text:span></text:span> apes regem, Varr.; s-atus et imperator salutatus est, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Collusio,<text:line-break/>Collusor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colludo, Ludo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Collustro,</text:span> 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> illustro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Belysa, öfwerstråla, upplysa:</text:span></text:span> sol omnia luce sua; luna solis lumine c-atur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Collustro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lustrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colluvies,<text:line-break/>Colluvio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colluo, Luo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Colly̆bus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> (Collubus): v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wexel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wexlande):</text:span> deductio pro c-o; detrimentum in c-o, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collȳra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en art </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bakwerk:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collȳrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: jus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som ätes dertill):</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collȳrium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ögonsalfwa:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlo,</text:span> cŏlui, cultum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odla; wårda; sköta; idka; hedra; dyrka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> neml.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om jord och deß alster: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odla, bruka, häfda, sköta:</text:span></text:span> agrum, C., Sa., Cs.; studium agri c-ndi; terræ pars habitabilis et culta; vitem, prædia, C.; rura, Cs.; arbora, Hor.; hortos, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med förswagad betydelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bebo:</text:span></text:span> urbem, C.; Casperiam terram, Vg.; cygnus fluminum ripas, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo:</text:span></text:span> circa ripam Rhodani, L.; Germani cis Rhenum c-ntes, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda, sörja för, hafwa omsorg om; söka befrämja, förädla, gagna:</text:span></text:span> Jupiter terras, C. poēt.; Romulus et Liber - - dum terras hominumque c-unt genus, Hor.; Juno terris magis omnibus Carthaginem, Vg.; universam generis humani consociationem c. debemus, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om kroppen såsom obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköta, putsa, smycka:</text:span></text:span> corpora, Ov.; brachia auro, Ct. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfälligt iakttaga, öfwa, idka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om lefnadssätt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föra:</text:span></text:span> cærimonias summa curā; religionum c-ns; officium c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> negligere); amicitiam, justitiam, liberalitatem, studia, artes; hoc quoque - orationis genus c-ndum est, C.; bonos mores, Sa.; hanc vitam c-uere veteres Sabini, Vg.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wisa uppmärksamhet, aktning, wördnad; hedra; söka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gunst:</text:span></text:span> opes opportunæ sunt, ut colare; coli et observari temporis causa; amici inter se colunt et diligunt; aliquem tamquam superiorem c.; c-ndus est ita quisque maxime, ut virtutibus maxime ornatus erit; parentis loco c. aliquem, C.; donis, L.; pater ita nos instituit, ne quem c-remus, nisi populum Romanum, Sa.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dyrka; helighålla:</text:span></text:span> deos, Herculem; ex patriis ritibus optima; Apollinem religione summa, C.; Mercurium, templum, Cs.; culti semper et colendi (dii), Hor.; penates, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odlad:</text:span></text:span> ager c-issimus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smyckad:</text:span></text:span> filia c-ior, Mt. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bildad:</text:span></text:span> animi, C.; ingenia c-iora, Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culta</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">odlad jord, mark, odling (concr.):</text:span> Lucr., Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdadt, prydligt:</text:span></text:span> dicere, Qu.; Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlōnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlōna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jord-, åkerbrukare:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> majores nostri ita laudare solebant - bonum agricolam, b. c-um, Cato; optimus c., C.; alia pastoris scientia, alia c-i, Varr.; arva coēgi, ut quamvis avido parerent c-o, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brukare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af andras jord, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">landtbonde, arrendator:</text:span></text:span> cum publicanis ita agere, ut cum c-is nostris debemus; a c-o, qui habuit conductum fundum, rationes accepit, C.; sive reges sive inopes erimus c-i; servi, liberti, c-i (Massiliensium), Cs.; fortis mercede c., Hor.; apud Germanos frumenti modum dominus aut pecoris aut vestis ut c-o injungit, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nybyggare, colonist:</text:span></text:span> deducere c-os in colonias; assignare agros c-is; Pompejani et c-i, C.; Sullani, Sa.; Carthaginem Tyrii tenuere c-i, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlōnia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Egor, mark,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ngn odlar:</text:span> vilicus c-æ suæ terminos egredi non debet, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coloni,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i betyd. såwäl af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nybygge,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nybyggarne,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som skickades till att bebo en ort:</text:span> c-am deducere in locum, C., Sa., L.; constituere in loco; occupare locum c-is; mittere c-as, homines in c-as; in c-as exire, proficisci; c. civium Romanorum; Latina; florens, C.; c-æ Lacedæmoniorum, N.; multi homines ex c-is et municipiis, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlōnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som rör, tillhör</text:span> colonus, -ia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bet.</text:span> a: leges c-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för en jordbrukare),</text:span> Varr.; oves c-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordinära),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är från ett nybygge, från colonierna:</text:span> cohortes, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odlande, brukande:</text:span></text:span> agri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odlare, landtman:</text:span></text:span> agrorum, L.; agelli virentis, Hor.; vitis, C.; pecora c-esque in agris esse, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bebyggare, innebyggare, som bebor:</text:span></text:span> locus frequens c-bus, ut inter montanos, L.; mater cultrix Cybelæ, Vg. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hyllar, håller sig till ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anhängare:</text:span></text:span> populus fautor c-orque bonorum; unicus c. Romanæ amicitiæ, L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som öfwar, idkar, egnar sig åt:</text:span> veritatis, C.; agri magis, quam belli, Sa.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dyrkare:</text:span></text:span> parcus et infrequens deorum, Hor.; = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prest:</text:span> c. matris deûm, Su.; Augusti, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odling:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> agrorum, fundi, vitium, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> c. animi philosophia, C.; nemo adeo ferus est, ut non <text:soft-page-break/>mitescere possit, si modo c-æ patientem commodet aurem, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. c. potentis amici <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppwaktande),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jordens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Odling:</text:span></text:span> agri, agrorum; regiones propter vim frigoris omni c-u carentes; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">plur.:</text:span> omnes c-us fructusque Cereris interierunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wård, skötsel, ans,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lefnadssätt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (yttre) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hyfsning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uppfostran):</text:span> corporis victus c-que <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppehälle och wård)</text:span> ad valetudinem referatur, non ad voluptatem; victus cultusque bestiarum; vestitus, victus, c. vitæ; multos tenuis c. delectat; a fera agrestique vita ad hunc humanum civilemque c-m deducti sumus, C.; Belgæ a c-u et humanitate provinciæ longissime absunt; c. et victus, Cs.; regio c-u vitam agere, Sa.; liberali, humili c-u habere, educare aliquem, Sa., L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klädnad, skrud, utstyrsel, prydnad:</text:span></text:span> Jugurtha miserabili c-u Romam venit; plebes, cui omnes copiæ in quotidiano usu c-uque corporis erant; Thalæ erant Jugurthæ multi thesauri filiorumque ejus c-us, Sa.; modicus, C.; patrius, regius, domesticus, quotidianus, N.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyx, utswäfning:</text:span></text:span> libido, stupra, ganeæ ceterique cultus, Sa.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">själens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bildning:</text:span></text:span> c. animi, C.; recti c. pectora roborant, Hor.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hyllning, uppmärksamhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mot person):</text:span> diligentem tribuere alicui, C.; meus, T.<text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dyrkan:</text:span></text:span> deorum, C.<text:line-break/>8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Idkande:</text:span></text:span> literarum, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŏlo</text:span> (cŏlui), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo inwid, i närheten af:</text:span></text:span> Histrum fluvium, Næv. ap. C.; illum locum, C.; viam, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som bor inwid -, granne:</text:span></text:span> Cereris, C.; ejus loci; Philippus gravis a. Aetolis, L.; Padi, Pn.; ripæ, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumcŏlo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo omkring:</text:span></text:span> sinum maris; paludem, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŏlo</text:span>, cŏlui, cult., 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppodla, bearbeta:</text:span></text:span> vineam, Pn.; rura, Col.; lanam, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andlig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förädla, bilda, utbilda:</text:span></text:span> dare se philosophiæ e-endum; animus doctrinā e-tus; vita artibus e-ta; victus hominum Atheniensium beneficio e-tus, C.; inventas vitam e-uere per artes, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Försköna, smycka, pryda:</text:span></text:span> Augustus urbem e-uit adeo, ut - -, Su.; parietes marmoribus, Pn.; orationem, T.; aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hedra),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wörda, hedra; dyrka:</text:span></text:span> aliquem, Ov.; deos, Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŏlo</text:span>, cŏlui, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo:</text:span></text:span> cis Rhenum, Cs.; alicubi, Sa.; inter mare Alpesque, L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bebo:</text:span></text:span> locum, C.; Asiam, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Innewånare, -byggare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som bebor ett ställe):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor:</text:span> Sophocles i. illius loci (Coloni), C.; eum locum i-æ Catabathmon appellant, Sa.; quācunque iter fecit (Hannibal), cum i-is conflixit; i-æ insulæ Lemni, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur m. m.:</text:span> nantes bestiæ maris, C.; Aquilo, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bosatt främling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots. så wäl</text:span> civis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som</text:span> peregrinus; <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sambo):</text:span> peregrini et i-æ officium est non esse in aliena republica curiosum; cives et i-æ Syracusani; cives Romani vestri (Siculorum) i-æ; Pythagorei paene i-æ nostri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ouppodlad, oodlad, ouppröjd, obebodd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> seremus tanquam in i-o et derelicto solo; via i-a et silvestris; pars terræ i-a, C.; loca, Sa.; i-æ pacantur vomere silvæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. (obearbetad):</text:span> nulla pars philosophiæ i-a ac deserta est, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Osnygg, owårdad, ohyfsad:</text:span></text:span> loci facies i-a, tenebris, odore foeda (alii: i-u), Sa.; homo, L.; canities, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ohyfsad, obildad, rå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i moraliskt, intellectuelt, æsthetiskt hänseende):</text:span> vir horridus et i.; oratio; vita, C.; indocti i-ique vitam transeunt; genus (hominum); mores, Sa.; versus, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inculte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utan wård och ans, obildadt, ohyfsadt:</text:span></text:span> dicere, vivere, C.; agitare, agere (= vivere), Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incultus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanwård, -skötsel, bristande wård</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adj.</text:span> incultus 2.): ingenium luxu et i-u torpescere sinunt, Sa.; honores (deorum) - per i-um - deserti, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percŏlo</text:span>, cŏlui, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfälligt utföra, smycka:</text:span></text:span> inchoata, Pn. ep.; non comperta eloquentiā, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wisa aktning, wördnad, artighet, hyllning:</text:span></text:span> patrem, Pt.; Agrippinam ejusque liberos, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket smyckad, prydlig:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcŏlo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I förwäg, i förtid:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppodla, -öfwa:</text:span></text:span> animum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hylla:</text:span></text:span> nova et ancipitia, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Serdeles prydlig:</text:span></text:span> genus eloquentiæ, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcŏlo</text:span>, cŏlui, cult., 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter odla, bruka, bearbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åter göra fruktbärande):</text:span> desertam terram, intermissa metalla r., L.; ut terra variis seminibus, sic ingenia nunc hac, nunc illā meditatione r-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfriskas),</text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besöka åter:</text:span></text:span> Phdr. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter idka, upplifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett studium, ett minne), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">åter genomgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i minnet l. tankarne), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">besinna, erinra sig:</text:span></text:span> inter se studia, artes; secum aliquid, C.; hæc quum r-o, Pt.; animas ad lumen ituras (Anchises) lustrabat studio r-ns, Vg.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter bringa till heder, återställa, hedra:</text:span></text:span> dignitatem alicujus, C.; imagines Galbæ; aliquem sacerdotio, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cōlo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlŏcāsia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŏcāsia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indisk wäxt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwars frukt är den ægyptiska bönan):</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōlon,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lem):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stycke, afdelning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en period l. vers (colon):</text:span> (membra, quæ κῶλα Græci vocant, C.), Qu., Don. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en tarm:</text:span> Don.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Colona <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cŏlo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏlōnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Troas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colonia,<text:line-break/>Colonicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colonus, Cŏlo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏlōnos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Demos af Attica.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cŏlōnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏlŏphon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i mindre Asien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cŏlŏphōnĭăcus,<text:line-break/>Cŏlŏphōnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlor</text:span> (Colos), ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> argenti, Hor.; nox rebus aufert c-em, Vg.; accipere c-em; inducere rei c-em, Pn.; c. albus, viridis, varius, vivus, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ansigtsfärg, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hy:</text:span></text:span> c. verus, non fuco illitus, Ter.; c-is bonitas exercitationibus tuenda est; venustatis non fuco illitus, sed sanguine diffusus c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild),</text:span> C.; heu, formose puer, nimium ne crede c-i, Vg.; mutare c-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skifta färg);</text:span> c. puniceæ flore prior rosæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. i bildliga uttryck (om ytan, utseendet af ngt): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färg:</text:span></text:span> ornatur oratio suco et c-e suo; oratio omnibus picta c-bus; urbanitatis c.; non solum sucum et sanguinem, sed etiam c-em civitatis amisimus, C.; quisquis erit vitæ c., scribam, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om föredragets färg = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ton, stil, character, grundstämning:</text:span></text:span> habitus orationis et quasi c., C.; operumque c-es servare, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som gifwes åt en sak, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skengrund, ursäkt:</text:span></text:span> dic aliquem, sodes, dic, Quintiliane, c-em, Juv.; sola c-em habet poenitentia; res non recipit c-em, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> arcus c-tus, C.<text:line-break/>b. c-ari = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bli solbränd:</text:span></text:span> si in sole ambulo, naturā fit, ut c-er, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> illorum librorum tactu quasi c-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tager färg)</text:span> oratio urbanitate c-ta; oratio ipsa se c-et et roboret, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭcŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twåfärgad:</text:span></text:span> baca, Ov.; ovum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ensfärgad:</text:span></text:span> cum aliquo, Vg.; alicui, Ov., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som mistat sin rätta färg, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Urblekt; wanställd:</text:span></text:span> sanguis, C. poēt.; Indus, Ov.; species æris, Pn.; ætas, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcŏlōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beröfwa deß (rätta) färg, gifwa en owanlig färg; wanfärga; wanställa:</text:span></text:span> cædes mare d-vere, Hor.; corpus livore d-atum, C.; uva d-atur, Col.; fama, Capit.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcŏlōrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">onaturlig förändring af färg:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Olik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. sins emellan till </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">färg, hy:</text:span></text:span> sententiæ judicum notabantur d-bus signis, C.; matrona meretrici, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brokig:</text:span></text:span> aves d-es, Varr.; rerum d. usus, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ūnĭcŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enfärgad:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Colos = Color.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏlossæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phrygien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cŏlossīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlossus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jättestatue</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (statue i jättestorlek), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">coloß:</text:span></text:span> c. CXX pedum Neronis effigie, Su.; sidereus c., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlossēus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlossĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Colossal, jättestor:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlostra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlostrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råmjölk:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlostrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjuk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af sådan:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlostrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjukdom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deraf:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōlōtes,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ödla:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlŭber,</text:span> bri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŭbra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Orm: (watten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-,</text:span> Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tomt-,</text:span></text:span> Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hugg-,</text:span></text:span> Hor.). <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŭbrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besatt med ormar:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Luc. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŭbrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ormartad:</text:span></text:span> ingenium, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōlum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sil</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (durkslag):</text:span> junceum, sparteum, aēneum, Cato, Vg., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sila, rena:</text:span></text:span> mel, ceram, aquam, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcōlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rinna ned, bildl. =) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slå fel:</text:span></text:span> spes, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percōlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sila igenom:</text:span></text:span> serum in junceis fiscellis, saccis; humor per terras p-tur, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlumbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dufhane; dufwa</text:span></text:span> (femininum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligt såsom</text:span> epicœnum): albulus, Catl.; vetuli notique, Hor.; timida, Vg.; domestica, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumbar</text:span>, āris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dufslag):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stock</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som bars kring halsen):</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för åra i ett skepp:</text:span> Fs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumbārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dufwaktare, -skötare:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumbārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dufslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (och hwad dermed har likhet):</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumbīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af dufslägt; duflik:</text:span></text:span> pulli, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumbor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som dufwor kyssas, näbbas:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Columella,<text:line-break/>Columellaris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Columna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlŭmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Och<text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Culmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm.: ngt, som skjuter upp, uppbär ngt):</text:span> <text:line-break/>I. (columen):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjelke,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som stöder sparrwerket i en takresning:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöd:</text:span></text:span> familiæ, Ter.; reipublicæ, C.; rerum mearum, Hor.; Macedoniæ sidus et c., Ct. <text:line-break/>II. (columen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> culmen):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Takås, kam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett tak, en mur o. s. w.:</text:span> (columbarium) agreste in columinibus vilarum, Varr.; maceriæ columen, Cato; Jovis species ad excelsum columen posita, C. poēt.; culmen ædis Jovis, L.; tuguri, vilarum, domorum, tecti culmina, Vg.; fulta c-a, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höjdpunkten, höjden, toppen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hufwudet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">det öfwersta, högsta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt, i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> sidus venit in columen [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">höjdpunkten af himmelen (zenith</text:span>)], Col.; c. amicorum Antonii Varius, C.; - culmen hominis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hjessan),</text:span> L.; Alpium, Cs.; fortunæ, L.; ruit a culmine Troja, Vg.; rerum pretii c., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlumna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rundpelare, colonn:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom stöd:</text:span> c-æ templa et porticus sustinent; marmorea, C.; sublimibus alta c-is regia solis, Ov.; breves, Albanæ, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fristående:</text:span> Mænia, rostrata, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om klippor, bergsspetsar:</text:span> c-æ Herculis, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">luftfenomen, meteorer:</text:span> vocatur et c., quum spissatus humor rigensque ipse se sustinet, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŭmella</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Colonn:</text:span></text:span> Cato; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">grafwård:</text:span></text:span> eminens, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stöd:</text:span></text:span> Lucili c., Mt. cit. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen rom. cognom.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlŭmellāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppstående:</text:span> dentes, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumnārii</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl. m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som uppehåller sig under pelargångar:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumnārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till portikers underhåll:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som uppbäres af colonner:</text:span> Pt.; Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlumnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppbyggande på eller med colonner:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intercŏlumnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mellanrum mellan colonnerna:</text:span></text:span> C., Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏlurnus</text:span> = Corulnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som är af hassel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> Corylus), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlūrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">storcirkel i en spher:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlus,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">Abl.</text:span> colo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> colu, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Acc. pl.</text:span> colos, colus; <text:span text:style-name="T2">masc.</text:span>: Catl., Ppt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rock, spinnrock:</text:span></text:span> veni ad me cum c-u tua et lana, C.; c-o vitam tolerare, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlūtĕa,</text:span> ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags frukt:</text:span> Pt. Ps. 87.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏlymbas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. simmande): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inlagd:</text:span></text:span> olivæ, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Com</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">præpositionen</text:span> cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättningar framför läppljud</text:span> (b, p, m) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och stundom framför vocal.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på menniskas hufwud (wanl. såsom en nedhängande l. böljande massa; ej i allm. hårwäxt) i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">collect. och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>: madenti c-ā, composito capillo; intonsa, C.; promissæ et rutilatæ, L.; longa, flava, spissa; c-am cingere lauro; religare; renodare, Hor.; pectere, Ov.; formare, Su.; in gradus frangere, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Man, ull:</text:span></text:span> agni aurea, C.; leonis, Gell.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på wäxter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löf; trådar:</text:span></text:span> nemorum c-æ, Hor.; palmæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. faces quatiunt c-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strålar),</text:span> Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏmans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har långt hår, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långhårig, -manig:</text:span></text:span> galeæ cristæ c-es; colla equorum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löfrik:</text:span></text:span> narcissus, Vg.; silva, Vf.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Strålrik:</text:span></text:span> stella, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏmātōrius</text:span>, A.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som brukas i håret:</text:span> acus, Petr.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår-, löfrik:</text:span></text:span> Gallia, Anton. ap. C.; silva, Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårrik:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏmŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Coma a.: Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comagene,<text:line-break/>Comagenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Comm . . .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏmāna, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">asiatiskt stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comans <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmarchus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Byfogde:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comatorius,<text:line-break/>Comatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comburo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Uro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōmē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Carien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Comum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏmētes,</text:span> ae, (<text:span text:style-name="T1">-ta</text:span>, ae), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. som har långt hår): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comet (swansstjerna):</text:span></text:span> C.; sidus c-es, T.; stella, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som hör till, passar för lustspelet, som sysselsätter sig med, föreställes, uppträder deri:</text:span> poēta; mos; adolescens; senex; levitates, C.; res c-a non vult exponi tragicis versibus, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comisk författare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comisk skådespelare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på comoediens sätt (i hwardagston):</text:span> tragicas res pæne c., tristes remisse tractare, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmĭnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Commĭnus</text:span> (cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> manus?), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I handgemäng, (i strid) på nära håll, i stående strid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> eminus): eminus hasta, c. gladio uti; pugnare, agere, accedere c. ad aliquem, C.; sequi, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öga mot öga, gent emot, framför, genaste wägen:</text:span></text:span> ursam adspicere c., Ov.; viso c. armatorum agmine, T.; c. petere aliquid, T., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sätt, tal, handling) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wänlig, fryntlig, gladlynt, godlynt, godmodig:</text:span></text:span> homines c-es, benigni, faciles, suaves; quis Laelio (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>) c-ior?; c. et humanus erga aliquem, C.; patres, L.; in alqm c., Hor.; oculis c-bus allicere amorem, Ov.; sermo et congressus, T.; c-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lustig)</text:span> garrire libellos Davo eludente Chremeta, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wänlighet, fryntlighet, godlynthet, godmodighet:</text:span></text:span> in obsequio c. adsit, assentatio amoveatur; nullam c-em habuit sermonis; a severitate quid tam distat, quam c.?; gravitati aspergere c-em, gravitatem condire c-e; c. et humanitas; facilitas et c., C.; c-e, per c-em rem perdere, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wänligt, fryntligt, godmodigt, trefligt:</text:span></text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>accipere aliquem, Pt.; adjuvare, Ter.; erranti c. monstrare viam, Enn. ap. C.; c. appellare; tum Scævola c., ut solebat: non luctabor, inquit, amplius, C.; c. invitare, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percōmis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ganska wänlig, fryntlig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmissor,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> (v. gr. κωμάζειν): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringswärma, -tåga efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">till ett dryckeslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (under musik o. s. w.); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fira, hålla ett dryckeslag:</text:span></text:span> c-atum ibo ad Philolachetem, ubi nos - lepide accipiet: ecquid tibi videor madere?, Pt. (Most. 305 ff.); L.; c-atum intromitti ad aliquem, Ter.; epulantes cum carmine triumphali et solennibus jocis, c-ntum modo, currum (dictatoris) secuti sunt, L. III. 29; c. in domum alicujus, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmissābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringswärmande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett tåg af druckne:</text:span> Alexander per Indiam c. temulento agmine incessit, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmissātio</text:span>, onis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringswärmande, tåg af dryckesbröder, dryckeslag:</text:span></text:span> c-es, convivia, cantus, symphoniæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Cat. II. 5); tempestas c-is, C.; ad mediam noctem extendere c-em, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmissātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringswärmare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bland dryckesbröder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">dryckesbroder:</text:span></text:span> Ter., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comitas,<text:line-break/>Comiter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Comis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> membrum incisum): Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ommāgēnē (Cŏmag.), es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nordöstra delen af Syrien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Commāgēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Commend . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mando (āre).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Commensus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Metior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comment . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Commercium,<text:line-break/>Commercor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Merx.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Commilitium,<text:line-break/>Commilito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Miles.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comminiscor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comminus = Cominus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Commiss . . .,<text:line-break/>Commod . . .,<text:line-break/>Commot . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mitto, Modus, Moveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Communic . . .,<text:line-break/>Communio (ōnis),<text:line-break/>Communis,<text:line-break/>Communitas,<text:line-break/>Communiter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Munia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmo,</text:span> compsi, comptum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansätta, -foga:</text:span></text:span> animi natura quibus rebus c-atur, docui, <text:soft-page-break/>Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ordna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> håret, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kamma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hår, hufwud, ngn):</text:span> caput, Pt.; mulieres dum c-untur -, Ter.; capillos, C.; c-ti crines adulteri, Hor.; c-ta puella comas, Ov.; aliquem aurato pectine, Sil.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Putsa, pryda:</text:span></text:span> corpora; orationem, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Comptus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Putsad, wårdad, polerad, sirlig:</text:span></text:span> c-a et mitis oratio senis, C.; orator, Qu.; sermo c-ior, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span>: -ius: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdadt, prydligt:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Comptus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanfogning:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårprydnad, frisur:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incomptus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Okammad:</text:span></text:span> capilli, coma, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owårdad:</text:span></text:span> oratio, Qu.; versus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incompte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōmœdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som spelar comoedi:</text:span> natio c-a est (Græcorum), Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmoedus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentlig comisk skådespelare:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmoedĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Comoedi, lustspel:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom diktart:</text:span> c. est imitatio vitæ, speculum consuetudinis, imago veritatis; jocis referta est antiqua Atticorum c., C.; c. poēma esset necne, quæsivere quidam; Eupolis atque - alii, quorum c. prisca virorum est, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom enskildt stycke:</text:span> c-am facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(författa),</text:span> Ter.; Atticorum c-æ, C.; c-am docere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inöfwa);</text:span> agere; dare ædilibus, Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmoedĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: ars, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōmoedĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom det sker i comoedien:</text:span> astat dulice et c., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compactilis,<text:line-break/>Compactio,<text:line-break/>Compactura,<text:line-break/>Compactus,<text:line-break/>Compages <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och<text:line-break/></text:span>Compago <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compingo, Pango, Pago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compactum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compaciscor, Pago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comparabilis,<text:line-break/>Comparate,<text:line-break/>Comparatio,<text:line-break/>Comparative,<text:line-break/>Comparativus,<text:line-break/>Comparo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compar, Par; Comparatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Comparo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen under</text:span> II. Paro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compeciscor,<text:line-break/>Compectum = Compac . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compedio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Compello,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af samma stamord, som</text:span> appello, interpello):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltala, tala till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> nominatim, C.; nomine, L.; voce, <text:soft-page-break/>multo honore, verbis amicis, Vg.; blande, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårdt, tillrättawisande, skymfligt tilltala; snäsa, skälla ned, ut; skälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn för ngt:</text:span> pater aliquem; aliquem edicto; mimus Attium poētam c-vit in scena, C.; aliquem segnem, L.; aliquem fratricidam et impium, N.; magna voce (aliquem) cuculum; inultum c-ri, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lagligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltala, åtala:</text:span></text:span> minatur - se judicem, qui non affuerit, c-turum; c-ri me lege voluerunt, C.; crimine aliquem, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compellātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltal:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förebråelse; snäsa, smädelse:</text:span></text:span> non tulit c-es meas; non sentit c-em suam commendationem esse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compend . . ., Compens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pendo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comperco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Parco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comperend . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Perendie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comperio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> (Perior).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Compes,</text:span> ĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> pes? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. beslägtadt med</text:span> expedio, impedio, πέδη?; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Boja, fjettra,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynnerhet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fot-boja, -black:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> vincire aliquem aureis c-bus, Ct.; minitari alicui c-es, Val.; crura dura c-ede, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck:</text:span> lineam c-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om nätet:</text:span> alii: c-am), Varr.; qui (animi) in c-bus corporis semper fuerunt, etiam, quum soluti sunt, tardius ingrediuntur, C.; Hebrus nivali c-e vinctus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compĕdio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fjettra; hop-, ombinda:</text:span></text:span> servi c-iti, Cato; pedes corrigiis c-io <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omsnörar),</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Compesco,</text:span> escui, s. s., 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> dispesco; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besl. med</text:span> compes, compedio, impedio?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fjettra, tygla:</text:span></text:span> compedibus, catenis, Ov.; equum freno, Tib.; catenā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hålla inom skrankorna, tukta, inskränka, lägga band på:</text:span></text:span> quæ mare c-ant causæ (quærere); luxuriantia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i stilen)</text:span> c-re, Hor.; ramos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(qwista),</text:span> Vg.; linguam, Pt. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stäfja, hämma:</text:span></text:span> clamorem, Hor.; furorem, tristitiam, Ov.; famem, Sen.; incendia, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compet . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Peto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Compīlo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kanske besl. med</text:span> pilus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hår, eg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plocka, plocka bar;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> jfr</text:span> pilo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plundra, roffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till sig:</text:span> quidquid domi est, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplundra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (person, hus, land o. s. w.):</text:span> malo c-ri, quam vēnire; exercitum; provinciam; fana; totum oppidum ostiatim, C.; templa omnibus ornamentis, L.; scrinia Crispini, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compīlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanroffande:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compingo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pango, Pago.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Compĭtum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gatmöte, wägskilnad; korswäg</text:span></text:span> (c. est, ubi viæ competunt, Varr.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på hwilka platser i stad och på land folksamlingar, folknöjen, auctioner höllos och (wid</text:span> compitalia) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gudstjenst firades wid</text:span> aræ, fana: vilicus rem divinam facito compitalibus in c-is, Cato; auctionari in c-is, C.; ad compitum Anagninum in luco Dianæ; per <text:soft-page-break/>vias et c-a rogationem populo suadere, L.; circum pagos et c-a præmia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(segerpris i lekar)</text:span> ponere, Vg.; quis circum pagos et c. c-a pugnax magna coronari contemnat Olympia?, Hor.; ora Hecates in c-is; Lares c-a servant, Ov.; porco lustrari c-a, Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Lares c-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwilkas bilder stå i</text:span> compitis), Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compĭtālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fest, som firades åt Larerna</text:span> in compitis: Cato, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Compĭtālĭcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som anställes</text:span> in compitis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i gatmötena:</text:span> ludi, C.<text:line-break/>2. hæc reservemus ambulationibus c-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under festen</text:span> compitalia), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Complementum, Complet . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compleo, (Pleo).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Complex . . ., Complodo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Plecto, Plaudo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compluvium,<text:line-break/>Compluviatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pluo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Potis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Composit . . ., Compostura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Compono, Pono.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compransor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prandeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comprehens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prehendo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compress . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Comprimo, Premo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ompsa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i södra Italien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Compsānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compte,<text:line-break/>Comptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Como.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Compuls . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pello.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Comula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōmum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i öfre Italien.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cōmensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Con</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">præpositionen</text:span> cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättning framför gom- och tungljud.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conam . . ., Conat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concallesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Callum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>oncănus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hispaniskt folkslagsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concentio,<text:line-break/>Concentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Concino, Cano.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Concipio, Capio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concerpo, Concert . . ., Concess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Carpo, Cerno, Cedo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Concha,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mußla, snäcka, snäckskal:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c-as legere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(plocka);</text:span> pina duabus grandibus patula c-is, C.; concharum color, Lucr.; vilis, Hor.; marinæ, tenues, cavæ c-æ, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snäcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom Tritons blåsinstrument:</text:span> Vg., Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">snäcka såsom husgerådsartikel:</text:span> c. salis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(saltkar);</text:span> c. unguenti, Hor.; bibitur c-ā, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Purpurfärg:</text:span></text:span> tinctus c-ā Sidonide, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perla:</text:span></text:span> lucida ex mari rubro, Tib. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mußleformig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchĕus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af, från snäcka:</text:span> baca <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(perla),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchīta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mußlesamlare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchis</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skalböna:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchȳlium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snäcka, ostron:</text:span></text:span> ostreæ et c., C.; coenamus aves, c-a, pisces, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Purpursnäcka, -färg, -kläder:</text:span></text:span> color c-i, Lucr.; c-o tinctus, C.; c. poscere, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conchȳliātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Purpurfärgad:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Purpurklädd:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concĭdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cado.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concīdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Concĭlium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> Concieo?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansättning, samling; samfund, sällskap; förening:</text:span></text:span> principiorum, corporum, materiæ, Lucr.; in pastorum c. se recepit; impiis iter est seclusum a c-o deorum; virtutum c., C.; amicorum, N.; hoc mihi tecum c. manebit, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i politisk l. officiel men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammankomst, möte, församling:</text:span></text:span> ducum; vocare, admitti in c., C.; principum Galliæ c.; c. convocare, dimittere, cogere, indicere; in communi Belgarum c-o, Cs.; c. Latinorum, populorum Etruriæ, plebis, L.; patrum, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förening, samfund, förbund:</text:span></text:span> c-a coetusque hominum jure sociati, quæ civitates appellantur, C.; Achaicum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭlio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopföra, förena:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> atomi c-antur, Lucr.; oratio c-at homines inter se; natura vi rationis hominem c-at homini ad orationis et vitæ societatem, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förena, sammanföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till äktenskap l. oloflig älskog:</text:span> alicui, ad aliquem, Pt., Su. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn, för sig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra till wän</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn (med sig):</text:span> lenitate c-amur iis, qui audiunt; c. eorum animos, qui audiunt; animos ad benevolentiam dignitate vitæ; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i philosophisk stil:</text:span> animal, simul ac natum est, sibi ipsum c-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> alienatur) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ansluter sig till,</text:span> C.; animos militum sibi, civitates Cæsari c-re, Cs.; reges, talem virum sibi, N.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stifta, sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förening):</text:span> pacem, Cs., N.; nuptias, Js. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winna, förwärfwa, -skaffa, bereda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ådraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig l. ngn annan:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> sibi amorem ab aliquo; amor c-atur, si -; hoc ei gloriam c-vit; servitutem patriæ, C.; regnum alicui; dignitatem sibi, Cs.; otium civitatibus Timoleon; fortuna id Cæsari c-vit, quod nemo quivit <text:soft-page-break/>consequi; sui cuique mores fortunam c-ant, N.; odium sibi, Qu.; tu mihi regnum, sceptra (Jovemque) c-as, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Köpa:</text:span></text:span> pulcre, recte aliquid, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concĭliābulum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mötes-, tingsställe, ting:</text:span></text:span> ambitione ducti novi homines nundinas et c-a obire solebant, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förening:</text:span></text:span> totius hominis c-em colere, tueri, servare, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anslutning; winnande, tillwinnande:</text:span></text:span> prima hominis c. est ad ea, quæ - -; c-is causa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att winna sinnena)</text:span> leniter dicere, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwärfwande, -skaffande:</text:span></text:span> gratiæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som stiftar, tillwägabringar förening:</text:span></text:span> opinio virtutis amicitiæ c-ix, C.; nuptiarum c-or, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i dålig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopplare, -erska:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātrīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wärfwar för ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mäklerska, wärfwerska:</text:span></text:span> blanda c., nobilitas, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koppleri:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātus</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Abl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concĭliātu</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förening:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconcĭlio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Locka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till sig, i snara):</text:span> eum, qui tibi mandatus est, Pt. Trin. 1. 2. 99.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afhända:</text:span></text:span> mihi copias omnes, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interconcĭlio</text:span>, 1. = Concilio, d. 1. ap. Qu. XII. 10. 59.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕconcĭlio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter winna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för sig l. en annan; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">försona, förlika:</text:span></text:span> inimicos in gratiam; me cum Cæsare; ordinem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klaß),</text:span> C.; militum animos imperatori, L.; milites; Parum insulam oratione, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter stifta; återställa, återwinna:</text:span></text:span> gratiam; existimationem judiciorum amissam, C.; apes, Varr.; pacem, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕconcĭliātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Försoning, -likning:</text:span></text:span> matris, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Återställande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af fred, enighet):</text:span> gratiæ, concordiæ, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕconcĭliātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: pacis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medlare),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Concinnus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -nior: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Nonius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Cinnus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blandad dryck):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälfogad, wälbildad, wälformad; sirlig, täck:</text:span></text:span> facies, Pt.; oratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rundad, symmetrisk framställning);</text:span> venustæ et c-æ sententiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sirliga, wäl swarfwade antitheser),</text:span> C.; versus c-ior; c-a Samos, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Passande, behaglig, angenäm:</text:span></text:span> ut tibi c-um est, Pt.; aptus et c. ad rem reditus, C.; c. amicis, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinne</text:span>, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinnĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Symmetriskt, rundadt, sirligt, smakfullt:</text:span></text:span> distribuere, dicere, scribere, C.; vestitus, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinnĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Symmetri; konstmässig byggnad, sammanställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i hwilken ord och membra symmetriskt motswara hwarandra):</text:span> verborum, sententiarum; collocationis partes sunt compositio, c., numerus, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sirlighet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> symmetri i allm.:</text:span> Sen., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinnĭtudo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sirlighet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansätta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> behörigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blanda; forma, laga, bereda:</text:span></text:span> vinum, Cato; trapetum; aream; lutum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till takstenar);</text:span> pallam, Pt.; munusculum alicui, C. ep.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åstadkomma, förorsaka; göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn till ngt:</text:span> fervorem, Lucr.; negotium alicui, Sen.; aliquem insanum, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansättning, beredning:</text:span></text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concinnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som ordnar, utsirar:</text:span></text:span> capillorum, Col.; orationis, Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconcinnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Opassande, smaklös, otreflig:</text:span></text:span> in aliquo genere i. aut multus, C.; asperitas i. gravisque, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕconcinno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (reparera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bota:</text:span></text:span> pallam, Pt.; ædes, C.; detrimentum, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concino <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cano.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(verb.)</text:span> = Concieo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(subst.),</text:span> Concion . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Concĭpĭlo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmodl. af</text:span> concipio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gripa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concipio, Concis . . ., Concit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Capio, Cædo, Cieo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conciuncula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conclave <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clavis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concludo,<text:line-break/>Conclus . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concord . . .,<text:line-break/>Concors <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concret . . .,<text:line-break/>Concub . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cresco, Cubo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conculco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Calco, Calx.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concumbo,<text:line-break/>Concupisco,<text:line-break/>Concurs . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo, Cupio, Curro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Concuss . . .,<text:line-break/>Concutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quatio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Condălium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ring:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(titel på en comoedi af</text:span> Pt.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condemn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Damnum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dīco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Condio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Condio,</text:span> 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krydda, sylta, lägga in</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (serskildt frukter i kryddor, olja, </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ättika), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">laga:</text:span></text:span> oleas, Cato; caules in aceto, Pn.; herbas, jus, C.; jus male c-tum, Hor.; mortuorum corpora c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">balsamera,</text:span> C.; corpus (Poppææ) differtum odoribus c-tur, ut mos externorum regum, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krydda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">försätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förljufwa, -mildra, -höja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (smaken) intrycket af ngt:</text:span> vitia naturæ studio malitiæ; tristitiam temporum hilaritate; gravitatem comitate, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pt. pass.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -tior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kryddad, smakfull:</text:span></text:span> c-iora hæc facit - aucupium atque venatio; oratio, orator lepore c-ior, C.; oratio nimium c-a, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krydda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> c-is condire coenam, Pt.; fames cibi c.; facetiæ sermonum c-a, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condīmentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som brukas till kryddning:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condītio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condītūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condītus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inläggning, -syltning, kryddning:</text:span></text:span> frugum c-io, C.; olivarum c-ura, uvarum c-us, vini c-io, Col.; cibi c-ura, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condĭtio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Condo, Do; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span> = Condicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dīco;<text:line-break/>Condītio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Condio; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Condĭt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Do <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Condīt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Condio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condolesco,<text:line-break/>Condormisco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Doleo, Dormio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conducibilis,<text:line-break/>Conduct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conduco, Duco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Condŭlus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condy̆lus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fingerknoge:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Condo, Do.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Condy̆lōma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tagg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absceß,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Condylus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Condulus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conela <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunila.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confarreo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Far.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conficio, Facio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confercio,<text:line-break/>Confert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Farcio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Confiteor, Fateor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Confestim,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> Festino): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genast, omedelbart, ofördröjligen:</text:span></text:span> quæ gestum negotium c. aut ex intervallo sequuntur; rem c. gerendam arbitror, C.; cohortes c. se subsequi jussit, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conficio,<text:line-break/>Confinium,<text:line-break/>Confisio,<text:line-break/>Confiteor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facio, Finis, Fido, Fateor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conflict . . .,<text:line-break/>Confrag . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Confringo,<text:line-break/>Confugium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fligo, Frango, Fugio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confus . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Confundo, Fundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Confuturum (Pt. Mil. Glor. 941) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conger,</text:span> gri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hafsål:</text:span></text:span> Ter., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Congeries,<text:line-break/>Congest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Congero, Gero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Congius,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mått för flytande waror</text:span> (1/8 amphora, 6 sextarii): olei, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congiālis</text:span>, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congiārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör l. håller en</text:span> congius: vinum, Cato; fidelia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Congiārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Traktering, spendering, skänk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till folket l. soldaterna, ursprungligen bestående af win, olja d. d., sedermera af penningar:</text:span> c-o lenire multitudinem; donari c-o, C.; dare populo, Pn.; militi, Ct.; populo c-um, militi donativum proposuit, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Congredior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och<text:line-break/></text:span>Congress . . .,<text:line-break/>Congreg . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior, Grex.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Congru . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gruo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conject . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conjicio, Jacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conifer,<text:line-break/>Coniger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conjicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conila <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunila.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Conisco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stångas</text:span></text:span> (vox plane incerta: Cic. ap. Qu. VIII. 3. 21 legitur jam corusco, quod vide.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conjug . . .,<text:line-break/>Conjunx <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/>Conjux <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugo, Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conjunct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jungo, Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Connex . . .,<text:line-break/>Connub . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Necto, Nubo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏnon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōnōpēum,</text:span> i,<text:line-break/>Cōnōpĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr. (κώνωψ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mygga): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sparlakanssäng</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-bädd, bädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med förhäng mot myggor (canapee):</text:span> foetæ nostræ in c-is jacent, Varr.; infans in testudineo c-o, Juv.; turpe c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom tillhörande ægyptisk weklighet),</text:span> Hor., Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōnor,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga ansats, laga sig till, sträfwa; bjuda till; försöka, taga sig före, företaga:</text:span></text:span> mulieres dum moliuntur, dum c-antur, annus est; ego obviam c-bar tibi; egone ista c-er?, Ter.; <text:soft-page-break/>manibus, pedibus c-bor, dum tibi prosim; nunquam hæc dicere c-bitur; c-ntem deterruit pudor; opus magnum et arduum, C.; priusquam quidquam c-retur, Divitiacum ad se vocari jussit; nihilo minus id, quod constituerant, facere c-antur; c-ati, si perrumpere possent, Cs.; indicem persequi c-atur, Sa.; multa, N.; ter conatus ibi collo dare brachia circum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnāta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl. n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Företag, försök:</text:span></text:span> c-a perficere, Cs., N.; c-is obviam ire; c-a exsequi, L.; c-a peragere, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">-mentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: Pn.): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">redskap, hwarmed man tager ansats; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för gående:</text:span> nervos c-e adjuvare, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ansats, ansträngning, fart:</text:span></text:span> sumere c. (eundi, saliendi) ab aliqua re, Lucr., Ov.; mittere aliquid magno c-e, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bemödande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ansats, ansträngning, drift</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> multis sæpe c-bus captis, L. III. 5, 6; magno c. magnas nugas dicere, Ter.; majore c-u agere aliquid; naturā belua c-um habet ad pastus capessendos, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utbrott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af en affect); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">företag, anslag:</text:span></text:span> sedare c-um iracundiæ; c-u desistere; perditos Gracchi c-us Scipio vindicavit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conquest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conqueror, Queror.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conquĭnisco,</text:span> quexi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Huka sig tillsammans, ned:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conquiro,<text:line-break/>Conquisit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quæro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conscendo,<text:line-break/>Conscensio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scando.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conscius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conscript . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Conscribo, Scribo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consecratio,<text:line-break/>Consecro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sacer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consectarius,<text:line-break/>Consectatio,<text:line-break/>Consectatrix,<text:line-break/>Consector,<text:line-break/>Consecutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sequor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consens . . .,<text:line-break/>Consentaneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sentio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consentes</text:span> Dii, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varr. ap. Arnob. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de gudar, som utgöra Jupiters rådsförsamling,</text:span> consiliarii Jovis (Varr. de r. r. I. 1; Augustinus de civitate Dei IV. 23).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>onsentia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i södra Italien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Consentīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consero, II. Sero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consido, Sedeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consīdĕro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> desidero?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Betrakta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ögonen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beskåda:</text:span></text:span> candelabrum etiam atque etiam; aliquid diligentius, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga i skärskådande, granska, bedöma, betänka, besinna, öfwerwäga:</text:span></text:span> pictores - et vero etiam poētæ suum quisque opus a vulgo c-ri vult; una quæque pars ex se et suā naturā c-atur; aliquid, de aliqua re; aliquid secum, cum animo suo; in hoc c-ndo animi in contrarias sententias distrahuntur; c., quid sit agendum; si c. volumus - quæ sit in natura hominis excellentia; c-dum est, ne aut temere desperemus aut nimis confidamus, C.; aliquid secum, in animo, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälbetänkt, förståndig:</text:span></text:span> judicium, consilium c-um, c-ius; verbum c-issimum; c-i hominis est -, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Betänksamt, wälbetänkt:</text:span></text:span> agere, facere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕranter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: id.: Val. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕrantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Betänksamhet:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Betraktande:</text:span></text:span> naturæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consīdĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sceptiker:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsīdĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetänksam, tanklös:</text:span></text:span> nos sumus i-i; cupiditas, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsīdĕrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetänksamt:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsīdĕrantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetänksamhet:</text:span></text:span> C. (dub. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consili . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consulo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consero, I. Sero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consobrinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Soror.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consort . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consors, Sors.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conspect . . .,<text:line-break/>Conspic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Specio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conspergo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Spargo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Constans,<text:line-break/>Constant . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consto, Sto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consterno,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sammanhanget med</text:span> Sterno, Consterno, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är owißt):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra skygg, sätta i koller:</text:span></text:span> equos, L.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skygga:</text:span></text:span> Sa., L., Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor såsom object:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppskaka, -jaga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skrämma;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i förwirring rusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från l. till ngt:</text:span> Coriolanus velut amens a sede c-tus - amplexum obtulit matri; ad arma, in fugam c-ri, L.; c-ti confugiunt, Cs.; fugā foedā c-ri, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beröfwa sans, besinning; slå med förskräckelse, förwillelse; förwilda, -wirra:</text:span></text:span> animo c-ri, Cs.; animos c-re, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consternātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hästars </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skyggande:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blind förskräckelse, blindt raseri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynnerhet om folkmassor (härar l. upproriska hopar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tumult</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uppror):</text:span> ira c-ioque subita (militum); muliebris (legem Oppiam abrogari poscentium), L.; tantum c-is concivit, ut -; c. (militum nocturna); c-e insanire, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Constituo,<text:line-break/>Constitut . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Statuo, Sto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Constratum,<text:line-break/>Constrict . . .,<text:line-break/>Constructio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sterno, Stringo, Struo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consualia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consuefacio,<text:line-break/>Consuet . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consuesco, Suesco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consul,</text:span> ŭlis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Consul,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> benämning för de 2 högste årlige embetsmännen i Rom såsom fristat och nominelt äfwen under kejsarne:</text:span> (c. est, qui consulit populo, C.; c. nominatur, quia consulit populum et senatum, Varr.): c-em facere aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wälja),</text:span> reficere; c-es facti, creati sunt - -; c. (ordinarius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mots.)</text:span> suffectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= inwald i stället för en under året afgången),</text:span> C.; c-em declarari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= förklaras för, utnämnas af den wid walet præsiderande embetsmannen),</text:span> C., Sa., Cs.; C. Murænam consulem c-ul renuntiavi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låtit utropa såsom consul af härolden);</text:span> c. iterum, tertium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för andra, tredje gången);</text:span> L. Cæsare, C. Figulo consulibus (Coss.) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under (deras) consulat,</text:span> C.; Galeria tribus Q. Fulvium c-em dixerat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hade röstat på honom till -),</text:span> L.; c. meus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= den, under hwilken jag är född),</text:span> Hor.; multos c-es numerare (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">många år, alldenstund åren betecknades med consulernes namn),</text:span> Sen. - Consul = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">exconsul med prolongeradt imperium,</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consŭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör consul, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consuls-, consularisk:</text:span></text:span> ætas (43 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">år);</text:span> imperium; auctoritas; officium; locus; familia; homo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som warit consul),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consŭlāris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consular,</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">person, som warit consul (exconsul) eller som har consularisk rang:</text:span> C., Sa., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consŭlārĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som det höfwes en consul:</text:span></text:span> vita acta c., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consŭlātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consuls embete, consulat:</text:span></text:span> c-um petere, obtinere, adipisci, consequi, capere, suscipere, inire, gerere, sustinere, obire; abire c-u, abdicare se c-u, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōconsul</text:span>, ŭlis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen såsom twå ord</text:span> pro c-e): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Proconsul</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= exconsul, som året eller åren efter sitt consulat styr en provins):</text:span> C., L., Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōconsulāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: som är i consuls, consulatets ställe:</text:span> p. imago <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om militärtribunatet),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Proconsuls, proconsularisk:</text:span></text:span> jus, imperium, vir, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōconsulātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Proconsuls embete, ståthållareskap:</text:span></text:span> Sa., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Consŭlo,</text:span> lui, ltum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådslå, rådgöra, -lägga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">pläga, öfwerlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sinsemellan, med ngn, för sig sjelf):</text:span> Galli, quid agant, c-unt, Cs.; in longitudinem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för framtiden),</text:span> Ter.; de Rhodiis c-tum est; priusquam incipias, c-ulto: postquam c-eris, mature facto opus est, Sa.; cum suis, L.; in commune, in medium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för det allmännas sak, gemensamt);</text:span> c., Ter., L., T.; quantum tu virtute exsuperas, tanto impensius me c-re æquum est, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fatta råd, besluta</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid, de aliqua re</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligast med utwidgad betydelse:</text:span> c. <text:span text:style-name="T2">de aliqua re, in aliquem</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förfara, gå till wäga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afseende på ngt, emot ngn:</text:span> pessime istuc in te c-is, Ter.; aliquid c-i et prospici poterit; aliter mihi de illis, ac de me ipso c-dum est, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> consultum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedanför);</text:span> de vita ac tergo civium regio more; de uxore honeste, Sa.; a patribus abstinebatur: in humiliores libidinose crudeliterque (a decemviris) c-batur; de perfugis; in deditos crudeliter, L.<text:line-break/>3. boni, optimi c. aliquid = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäl anse, wäl upptaga:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Pn., Qu.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="T2">de aliquo,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oftare</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui, alicui rei</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lägga, fatta råd för) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sörja för, se till godo, wårda sig, wara mån om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> - (skydda); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">se, göra afseende på:</text:span></text:span> alicui, Ter.; de salute suorum c., communem relinquere; parti civium c., partem negligere; saluti patriæ, paci, temporibus; famæ, pudori suo; iis, quos vi deviceris, c-dum est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skydda, skona),</text:span> C.; civitati, vitæ suæ, fortunis suis, sibi, religioni, Cs.; miseris civibus; sibi regnoque; magis iræ quam famæ, Sa.; rebus suis; male patriæ, Vg.; civium fortunis, L.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådfråga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fråga till råds; anmoda att yttra sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> aliquem per literas, C.; populum, Varr., C., L.; haruspicem, C.; senatum de foedere, de provinciis, Sa.; deos sortibus de re, Cs.; deum auguriis c-bat, quæ prodigia suscipienda essent, L.; oracula Phoebi, Vg.<text:line-break/>6. consulere aliquid = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fråga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter ngns mening om ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inhemta yttrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> rem consultam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försedd med rättslärdes yttrande)</text:span> deferre ad aliquem, C.; si jus c-res, peritissimus erat; rem consules ad senatum referunt, delatam c-re non licuit, L.; rem nulli obscuram - c-is, o bone rex, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. rådfrågad): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förfaren, skicklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. och wanl. i lag och rätt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lagklok:</text:span></text:span> juris; juris et justitiæ; c-orum alter disertissimus, disertorum alter c-issimus; juris- <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> jureconsultus, C.; juris et eloquentiæ, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådslut, rådslag, beslut;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt om senatens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">betänkande, beslut:</text:span></text:span> facta et c-a fortium et sapientium, C.; senatus c. factum est, ut -, C., L.; c. collegæ, L.; patrum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consulte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälbetänkt, klokt:</text:span></text:span> cavere, Pt.; rem gerere, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med flit:</text:span></text:span> Sp.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consulto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerlagdt, med flit:</text:span></text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oöfwerlagd; obetänksam:</text:span></text:span> largitio, L.; homo, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej rådfrågad, oåtspord:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej fått rådfråga sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådlös:</text:span></text:span> i-i abeunt sedemque odere Sibyllæ, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsulte</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inconsulto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetänksam:</text:span></text:span> i-e largiendo patrimonium profundere; se i-o in periculum mittere, C.; i-ius, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭlium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som hålles l. rådplägar) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådgörande, -plägning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (pröfning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerläggning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynn. offentlig); meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rådläggande församling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">myndighet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> specielt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">senaten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (statsrådet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krigsråd; domarenämnd:</text:span></text:span> vestrum est c., quid sit faciendum; in c. adhibere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillkalla)</text:span> aliquem; conferre c. cum aliquo; in c. mittere; summum, <text:soft-page-break/>publicum c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om senaten);</text:span> (dixit consul Philippus) videndum esse sibi aliud c.: illo senatu se rempublicam gerere non posse; dimittere c.; aderam in c-o consulibus, C.; præsenti c-o, pro c-o locutus est; ex decreto c-i imperat; c. habere de aliqua re; bonus c-o, Sa.; c-i est res <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medgifwer öfwerläggning);</text:span> habere c.; c-o, ad c. adhibere; in c-o pronunciare aliquid, Cs.; si essent in republica magistratus, nullum futurum fuisse Romæ nisi publicum c., (fremunt patres), L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beräkning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (klokhetsåtgerd); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afsigt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom handling):</text:span> ea non posita sunt in nostris c-is, sed in fortunæ temeritate; quantum humanis c-is provideri poterat; facere aliquid c-o, sine c-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med, utan afsigt),</text:span> C.; Servius non rupit fati necessitatem humanis c-is; mentem peccare, non corpus: unde c. abfuerit, culpam abesse, L.; quid æternis minorem c-is animum fatigas?, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som gifwes:</text:span> fidele c. dare deliberanti; libere dare c.; egere, parere c-o; petere c. ab aliquo; probare, repudiare, rejicere, respuere c. alicujus: uti c-o alicujus; juvare aliquem c-o, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som fattas l. finnes, (beråd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beslut, plan, tanke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (påfund, fint), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afsigt, beräkning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åsigt, såwidt de syfta till förwerkligande):</text:span> c. capere, inire de re, ex tempore capere; in suscepto c-o permanere; c. cepit - evertere fortunas alicujus; ut exirem; omne c. ad suam naturam revocare; c. ejus casus aliqui peremit; mutare c.; in omnibus c-is factisque considerandum est - -; illud Solonis c., quo primum instituit Areopagitas; bono, privato c-o facere aliquid; publicum c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offentligt beslut);</text:span> id non divino c-o, sed ipsa vi rerum factum est; c-a in republica <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(politiska åsigter och planer);</text:span> c. imperatorium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strategisk fint);</text:span> administer c-orum alicujus; facere aliquid eo c-o, ut - -, C.; communi c-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enligt gemensamt beslut);</text:span> clandestina c-a; Galli belli renovandi c. ceperunt; Helvetii domos suas reliquerant eo c-o, ut toti Galliæ bellum inferrent; ostendit, quid sui c-i sit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad hans plan war),</text:span> Cs.; c. novum, nefarium, pravum; c. patrare; aperire alicui, Sa.; unius viri c-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfinning)</text:span> rei addita fides, L.; c-a in melius referre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fatta bättre, wänligare tankar);</text:span> vertere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omintetgöra)</text:span> alicujus c-a; quod c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utwäg)</text:span> aut quæ jam fortuna dabatur?, Vg. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(närmande sig till egenskapsord): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beräknande wishet, klokhet, rådighet, rådwishet, förstånd, besinning:</text:span></text:span> c-o linguāque princeps; parvi sunt foris arma, nisi sit c. domi; ineunte ætate maxima est imbecillitas c-i; Romulus pastores congregavit, - non eloquentiā, sed c-o et sapientiā singulari; magnus animo et c-o prudentiāque fidens; præsenti animo c-oque uti; exercendum est corpus, ut c-o rationique oboedire possit, C.; convenerunt omnes, in quibus aliquid c-i aut dignitatis fuit; vir magni c-i, Cs.; c-o egere, Sa.; c-i plenus, N.; vis c-i expers mole ruit sua, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭliārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådplägande; rådande:</text:span></text:span> senatus; amicus, Pt.; fulmen, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭliārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådgifware:</text:span></text:span> regis, meus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Medlem, inwigd i ngns råd:</text:span></text:span> augur Jovi c. datus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭlior</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådlägga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">slå:</text:span></text:span> difficilis ad c-ndum res, C.; hæc c-ntibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(då de rådlade derom)</text:span> nuntiatur, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råda:</text:span></text:span> bonis amice, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭliātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consĭliātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådgifware, -erska:</text:span></text:span> Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consulto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådslå; lägga råd, rådföra sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerlägga, -wäga:</text:span></text:span> aut anquirunt aut c-ant, ad vitæ usum conducat necne id, de quo deliberant; de officio deliberare et c., C.; de rebus dubiis, Sa.; de bello, de exitu rei, Cs.; de sua salute; ad hæc c-nda procurandaque omnis multitudo a bello et armis conversa est, L.; tuum erit c-re, utrum prævaleat, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sörja för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med råd), (styra):</text:span> delecti (patres) reipublicæ c-bant, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådfråga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> aliquem, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådplägning, öfwerläggning:</text:span></text:span> nulla tibi jam est c., Ter.; res venit in c-em; de ejus c-e et deliberatione quæritur, qui rem celaturus non sit, si id injustum putet, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rhetoriken</text:span> = quæstio infinita = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allmän undersökning, fråga:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådfrågande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (serskildt af en rättslärd); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förfrågan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hos en myndighet):</text:span> respondere alicujus c-i; causa c-is, C.; res digna c-e principis, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som rådfrågar:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: hostia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarmed man frågar, rådfrågar gudarne):</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådsökande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (consulent, hos en jurist):</text:span> c-bus suis respondere, C.; c-or ostia pulsat, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådgifware, anstiftare:</text:span></text:span> malum consilium c-i pessimum, Varr.; cupido et ira pessimi c-es, Sa.; sua exempla reciderunt in c-es, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Consultrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som sörjer för -:</text:span> natura utilitatum c., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consumm . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Summa, Summus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consumpt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consumo, Sumo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Consurrectio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Consurgo, Surgo, Rego.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>onsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gudomlighet.</text:span><text:line-break/>Consuālia, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: Consi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fest.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contabundus = Cunct . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunctor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contag . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contingo, Tango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contāmĭno,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enligt wanliga antagandet af</text:span> Tango (Contagmino); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Examino <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och med hänseende till betydelsen</text:span> Contagio): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopflicka, -skarfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af beståndsdelar från olika håll, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hopblanda, blanda:</text:span></text:span> fabulam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af flera grekiska);</text:span> gaudium ægritudine, Ter.; Lucr.: gentes, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besudla, -fläcka, -smitta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i yttre och (wanl.) i moralisk men.:</text:span> Saturnini sanguine se non - c-arunt, sed honestarunt; se scelere, humanis vitiis; veritatem mendacio, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contāmĭnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oren, besudlad, -fläckad; wanryktad:</text:span></text:span> manibus c-is attrectare aliquid; spiritus c.; sceleribus et flagitiis c-ssimus; judicia unius vitio ac turpitudine c-a, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contatio = Cunctatio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunctor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Contechnor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Techna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contempl . . .,<text:line-break/>Contempt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Templum, Temno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nöjd) se</text:span> Contineo, Teneo; Content . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Contendo, Tendo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Conticesco,<text:line-break/>Conticinium,<text:line-break/>Conticisco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Taceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contign . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tignum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contiguus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contingo, Tango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Continens,<text:line-break/>Continenter,<text:line-break/>Continentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contineo, Teneo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contingo (-tĭgi) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Continu . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contineo, Teneo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contio</text:span> (Concio), ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> conventio?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Församling, folkförsamling, möte, stämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i abstract och concret mening = de församlade):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentlig, af medborgare eller af soldater</text:span> (c. est conventus a magistratu aut sacerdote publico per præconem convocatus, Paul. Diac.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott öfwerläggande l. afhörande, ej beslutande:</text:span> disceptationes c-um; c., quæ constat ex imperitissimis, tamen judicare solet, quid intersit inter gravem et levem civem, C.; advocare c-em, C., Sa., L.; c-em populi (C., Sa., L.), militum (Cs.) vocare; convocare in c-em, C., L.; venire, prodire, escendere, ascendere in c-em (i. e. in rostra), C.; pro c-e (populi aut militum) laudare aliquem, ornare, C., Sa., L.; clamor c-is, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Församling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> laudationes fere scribuntur ad c-em funebrem, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tal, föredrag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inför en församling:</text:span> c-bus populum tenere; in c-bus et in sententiis dicendis ad persuadendum tua plurimum valet oratio; legi tuam c-em, C.; habere c-em, C., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiōnālis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiōnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förekommer på ett folkmöte, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mötes</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> clamor c-lis; populus c-rius, C.; senex c-lis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(folkmötes-kund),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiōnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samlas till, biwista ett möte:</text:span></text:span> singuli vos universos c-ntes timent, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en församling, menighet:</text:span> de aliqua re; ex turri alta; velut ex superiori loco c-ri, ut homines mortem timere desinant, C.; apud milites, Cs.; ad populum, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiōnābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hållande tal, talande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från</text:span> rostra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> tribunal): velut c., L., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiōnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Folktalare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">demagog:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obetydligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Möte, tal:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contor = Cunctor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Contort . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contorqueo, Torqueo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contrā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett obrukligt</text:span> conter, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildadt af</text:span> cum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liksom</text:span> inter, intra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> in), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Emot:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gent emot, emot, på motsatta sidan, ansigte mot ansigte:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: petebam, ut c. intueri (Romulum) fas esset, L.; ulmus erat c.; Pyramus et Thisbe - suæ quisque parti (parietis) dedere oscula non pervenientia c., Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: c. portum, C.; c. meridiem; Britannia c. Galliam posita est, Cs.; Italiam c. Tiberinaque ostia, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Emot, i utbyte emot, tillbaka, till swar:</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: cedo mihi tres homines istis moribus aurichalco contra; ego eam c. amo, Pt.; quom hic nugatur, mihi c. nugari libet, Ter.; c. ferire, Sa.; Aeolus hæc c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till swar),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twärtemot, twärtom, deremot, i strid med, på motsatt sätt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: quæ probabilia videntur, sequi, quæ c., improbare; aliud probabile est, aliud c.; c. fit a plerisque; ut hic miseri, sic c. illi beati; c. putare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa motsatt åsigt);</text:span> c. liceri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bjuda twärtemot = bjuda lågt, då en annan bjuder högt);</text:span> c. quam fas erat; c. atque oportet; aut opes (eorum) metuunt aut c. ab iis aliquid exspectant; c-aque, sed c., at c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och, men twärtom, deremot),</text:span> C.; quod c. est; c. ac ratus erat; - at c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i motsats till forntiden)</text:span> quis est his moribus, quin divitiis et sumptibus, non probitate - cum majoribus suis contendat?, Sa.; facilem esse rem - si modo unum omnes sentiant: c. in dissensione nullam se salutem perspicere, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: c. naturam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> secundum naturam); c. officium est studiis a rebus gerendis abduci, C.; c. spem, opinionem; c. timorem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(twärtemot hwad han fruktade);</text:span> c. decus regium miserabili cultu Romam venit, Sa.; c. ea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deremot),</text:span> N., Cs., Sa.; c. exspectationem, Cs.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Emot,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i fiendtlig rigtning l. ställning, för att motstå l. anfalla, bekämpa, wederlägga o. s. w.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: arma c. ferre; c. pugnare; venient catervæ c. dicentium philosophorum; ne in mentem quidem quidquam c. venit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att inwända deremot),</text:span> C.; c. consistere, venire, Cs.; obsistere c., Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: c. patriam arma ferre; præsidia c. feras; his adjutor c. rempublicam repertus est nemo; Scipio patronus justitiæ fuit c. orationem Phili; pro tabulis, c. t-as dicere; c. omnia disputatur ab Academicis; c. animi immortalitatem disserere, C.; c. populum Romanum tertia pars Galliæ conjuravit, Cs.; c. pericula firmissimus; Jugurtha amissa Thala nihil satis firmum c. Metellum putat; c. hæc festinare oppidani; Jugurtha accepit, claros homines c. se venire, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Motsatt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet:</text:span> c-us regione; in c-as partes abire; c-o motu, ac caelum, C.; collis huic c.; tigna iis, Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till begrepp, beskaffenhet, syftning, innehåll:</text:span> frigus c. calori, mors vitæ, humor ignibus; virtutis vitiositas; in c-am partem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för motsatta sidan l. meningen)</text:span> afferre aliquid; in c-as partes disputare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för och emot),</text:span> C.; e c-o = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twärtemot,</text:span> C., Cs.; orationes inter se c-æ, C.; c-a fatis fata rependere, Vg.; Democritus semper ridebat, flebat c. auctor, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stridande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fiendtlig, motig, widrig:</text:span></text:span> virtuti nulla utilitas c-a est; omnis voluptas honestati c., C.; litora (sint precor) litoribus c-a, fluctibus undæ, Vg.; flamina c-a classi, Ov.; Avernus avibus, Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Antithes:</text:span></text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contrārie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Motswarande, i motswarighet:</text:span></text:span> verba verbis c. relata, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Motsatt:</text:span></text:span> scriptum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contro</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dativ-form, motswarande</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> contra, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott i sammansättningar,</text:span> controversia etc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contract . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contraho, Traho.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contrar . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contrect . . .,<text:line-break/>Contristo,<text:line-break/>Contritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Traho, Tristis, Tero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Controvers . . .,<text:line-break/>Contubern . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Verto, Taberna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contuitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contueor, Tueor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contŭmax,</text:span> ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(troligast af roten i</text:span> Temno, Contemno):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trotsig, stursk, spotsk; gen-, motsträfwig, -spänstig; tredsk:</text:span></text:span> in alios c.; in superiores c., in æquos fastidiosus, in inferiores crudelis, C.; animus, preces, T.; populus regibus, Sen.; bos, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ståndaktig:</text:span></text:span> c. adversus tormenta servorum fides, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Styf, spröd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om liflösa föremål:</text:span> fractu c., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contŭmācia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trots, trotsighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i klandrande mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sturskhet, spotskhet, gensträfwighet, motspänstighet:</text:span></text:span> singularis insolentia, superbia, c.; responsi c., C.; Flavius - c-ā adversus contemnentes certavit; eadem c. in vultu (Appii Claudii rei), L.; bovis, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trots</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ädel men.:</text:span> Socrates (reus) adhibuit liberam c-am, a magnitudine animi ductam, non a superbia, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contŭmācĭter</text:span>, cius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spotskt, trotsigt, sturskt, med gensträfwighet:</text:span></text:span> vexare, scribere, C.; milites omnia c. agebant, L.; Dolopes - quod c-ius se gesserant - urbe insulāque (Scyro) ejecit, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percontŭmax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket trotsig:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contŭmēlia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af roten i</text:span> Temno?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förnärmelse, -smädelse, skymf, hån:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i handling (smälek, kränkning):</text:span> c-am facere; in se accipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lida),</text:span> Ter.; facile patior injuriam, si est vacua a c-ā, Pacuv., c-is insequi, lacerare, vexare, operire, onerare aliquem; c-as alicujus pati, C.; vetus: c-as perferre, accipere; in suam c-am accipere, vertere aliquid; populi R-i beneficium extorquetur alicui per c-am; cum c-a perfugam appellari ab aliquo, Cs.; c-ā incitatus, accensus; c-am imponere alicui, Sa.; c-am edere in aliquem, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ord: (skymford, försmädelse, hånlig utlåtelse):</text:span> audire, dicere, Pt.; magnā cum c-ā verborum ad pugnam evocare; gravissimæ verborum c-æ, Cs.; c-am jacere in aliquem; aculei c-arum; inter fratres intorquentur gravissimæ c-æ, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wåld, mißhandling:</text:span></text:span> navis quamvis c-am perfert, Cs.; c-is os offerre, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contŭmēliōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förnärmande, ärerörig, hånlig, skymflig:</text:span></text:span> in socios, in edictis; literæ, oratio, voces, C.; in aliquem; dicta, Sa.; voces, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Contŭmēliōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med skymf, hån; på ett förnärmande sätt:</text:span></text:span> dimittere aliquem; lædere, maledicere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Contus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stång, stake):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Roderstång:</text:span></text:span> remi c-ique, Pn., T.; c-o ratem subigere, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom wapen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lans:</text:span></text:span> acutā cuspide c., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Contusio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contundo, Tundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Convaso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vas (vasis).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Convect . . .,<text:line-break/>Conven . . .,<text:line-break/>Convers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Veho, Venio, Verto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Convex . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Veho.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convīcium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stoj, stojande rop</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af många röster, isynnerhet för att uttrycka owilja l. nedtysta), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hyßjande:</text:span></text:span> facere c. ante ædes, Pt.; c. convivii; urgeri, explodi omnium c-o; jactatus est populi, senatus clamore c-oque, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">djurs </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skri:</text:span></text:span> ranarum, Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owett; hårda, onda ord; snäsa, oförsynt tillrättawisning, smädelse:</text:span></text:span> sustinere scurræ c-a; Cato rostra advolat, c. facit consuli; qua objurgatione aut potius quo c-o coner eos ab errore avellere?; aurium c-o mihi extorta veritas est, C.; regerere c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa igen),</text:span> Hor.; fundere c-a, Ov.; c-is incessere, proscindere, Su., Pn.; a c-is et probris ad tela transire, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Convīcior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gifwa onda ord, wara owettig, smäda:</text:span></text:span> Varr.; c-ri potius, quam vere accusare, L.; alicui, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Convīciātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smädare:</text:span></text:span> maledicus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Convictio,<text:line-break/>Convictor,<text:line-break/>Convictus (-us),<text:line-break/>Conviv . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vivo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kegla, kon,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. hwad som har form deraf (såsom hjelm, hjelmbuske, cypreß-, pinieäpple):</text:span> forma c-i formosior quam sphæræ, C.; galeæ insignis c. cristæque comantes, Vg.; tegmina capitum picto nutantia c-o, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konbärande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med konformig frukt:</text:span> cyparissi, Vg.; pinus, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōnĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.: Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Convulsio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Convello, Vello.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coos = Cos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōpa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> caupo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skänk-jungfru, krögare-madam:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōpæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cōpāis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sjö.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cōperio = Cooperio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Operio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏphĭnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korg:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Copia,<text:line-break/>Copiolæ,<text:line-break/>Copior,<text:line-break/>Copiosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cōpis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōpis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ops, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som är i besittning, har tillgång till ngt:</text:span> dies prosper et c., Pacuv.; facere aliquem copem (= voti compotem), Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (co-opia (Varr.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mots.</text:span> inopia):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: (relativt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förråd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rik) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillgång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rikedom, mängd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> frugum, agri, vectigalium, pecuniæ; festiva liberorum c.; affluere omnium rerum c-ā; c. poētarum, magistrorum, exemplorum, C.; navium, voluntariorum, pecoris, frumenti, pabuli, remigum, principum, Cs.; latronum, necessariorum, Sa.; sit bona librorum et provisæ frugis in annum c.; c. narium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för näsan</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wällukt),</text:span> Hor.; pressi c. lactis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. (absolut):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. (<text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förråd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för underhåll, serskildt af här), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förnödenheter;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillgångar, förmögenhet, medel, (rikedom):</text:span></text:span> domesticæ; quotidianis sumptibus c-æ suppetunt; c-æ singulorum parvæ; quas c-as proximis relinqui æquius erat, eas transferunt ad alienos; inest in tali liberalitate (rapiendi cupiditas), ut ad largiendum suppetant c-æ; earum rerum, quibus utuntur homines, facultates, opes, copiæ, C.; reliquam partem hiemis se Menapiorum c-is aluerunt; c-as Dyrrhachii parare; ut quisque est genere c-isque amplissimus, ita plurimos circum se ambactos habet, Cs.; plebes - cui omnes c-æ in usu quotidiano et corporis cultu erant; suis filiæque c-is Orestilla et alienis nominibus persolvit, Sa.; frumentum aliæque c-æ, L.; c-as in castra convehere, T.; inops c-arum hostis, Vell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wapenstyrka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwaröfwer ngn förfogar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">manskap, här, trupper:</text:span></text:span> cum omni c-ā ad aliquem venire (omnis armatorum c.); c-as comparare, contrahere; c-as alicujus minuere, profligare, C.; equites ex omni c-ā singuli singulos pedites delegerant; augebatur c-a; Helvetii per fines Sequanorum copias suas traduxerant; tres copiarum partes, Cs.; Catilina ex omni c-a - duas legiones instituit; (servorum magnæ c-æ ad eum concurrebant); c-as armare, parare; pedestres, equestres c-æ; videt montibus atque c-is hostium sese clausum, Sa.; c-as in terram exponere; egressus omnibus copiis - hostem castris excivit; terrestres, navales, peditum, equitum, L.; exiguis c-is dimicare; c-as trajicere, transportare, deducere in campum, disjicere, N.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om skrifter och författare = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sak-, innehållsrikhet, lärdom, mångkunnighet:</text:span></text:span> c-ā rerum instructa eloquentia; rerum c. verborum c-am gignet; homines summā in studiis suis varietate et copiā; Aristoteles vir summo ingenio, scientia, c-ā, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställningens form: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikedom, fyllighet, ledighet i </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">framställning, talare-, stilistisk talent, förmåga:</text:span></text:span> c. dicendi, verborum; in jure civili satis facere non potuit, nisi dicendi c-am assumpsisset; in dicendo c. et ubertas; materia digna c-ā alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillgång, tillfälle, tillträde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förmåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer ngt:</text:span> facere alicui spectandi, conveniendi c-am, Pt.; facere civibus consilii sui c-am, C.; facere alicui frumenti c-am, Cs.; magna mihi est c. memorandi, quæ - populi irā impulsi male consuluerint; c-am habere societatis jungendæ, emundi; alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till att gripa);</text:span> c-am pugnandi facere alicui; iis in otio - vivere c. erat, Sa.; fit alicui pugnæ c., L.; c. fandi data, Vg.; facta est (Phaëthonti) immensi c. mundi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att genomfara);</text:span> sit tibi c. nostri, Ov.; c. inveniendi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfinnings-gåfwa),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōpia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ymnighetens gudinna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpiŏlæ</text:span>, arum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten truppstyrka:</text:span></text:span> Brut. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förse sig:</text:span></text:span> Claud. Quadr. ap. Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ymnig, rik, riklig, rikt försedd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> rebus omnibus; victus; a frumento c., C.; hostis, Su.; oppidum re cibariā, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i oeconomiskt hänseende) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förmögen, bemedlad:</text:span></text:span> patrimonium; mulier locuples et c.; Mummius numquid c-ior, postquam urbem c-simam sustulit?, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andligt hänseende: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikt begåfwad, utrustad, mångkunnig, lärd:</text:span></text:span> ingenium, Qu.; Dicæarchus magnus et c. Peripateticus, C.; artibus honestis c., T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning och talare l. författare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik, ledig, fyllig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (widlyftig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wältalig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> jejunus, exilis): multa et varia et c. oratio; homo in dicendo, ad dicendum c.; orator, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om språket sjelft: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpiōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikligt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> large et c. comparare pastum; laudare, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikt, ledigt, utförligt:</text:span></text:span> oratoris est composite, ornate, c. loqui; dicere de re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percōpiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket rik:</text:span></text:span> p. fuisti in ea re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utwecklat stor rikedom i framställningen):</text:span> Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏpis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sabel:</text:span></text:span> gladius curvatus falci similis, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Copo = Caupo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏprĕa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gycklare, hofnarr:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coptŏplăcenta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kaka:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>optos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/>Coptus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Ægypten.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōpŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmodl.</text:span> co-ipula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af st.</text:span> ap <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uti</text:span> aptus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> cogo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> ago): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanhållningsmedel, band:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: (koppel, lina):</text:span> naves c-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(linor?)</text:span> continentur, Cs.; c. detrahitur canibus, Ov.; Datames Thuynem c-ā vinctum ante se agebat, N.; in c-am conjici = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sammankopplas,</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Föreningsband, kärleksband:</text:span></text:span> res aliqua societate cum <text:soft-page-break/>rebus se c-āque teneant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i framställning),</text:span> Qu.; is fuit c. talium virorum, N.; felices, quos irrupta tenet c., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpŭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanbinda,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">koppla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">knyta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">foga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vitem arbusto, Cato; in animo nihil est c-tum, nihil coagmentatum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> voluptatem cum honestate tamquam belluam cum homine; c-ati in jus pervenimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(då den ene hängt sig fast wid den andre),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanföra, förena:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om förbund, föreningar) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sluta, stifta:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> cave siris hanc cum filia mea c-ri, Pt.; vinculum non mediocre ad voluntates nostras c-andas; hæc cogitatione differunt, re c-ata sunt; se cum inimico; societatem cum deo; res inter se, C.; concordiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stifta),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanfoga, sammansätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ord):</text:span> verba conjunctionibus; verba c-ndo jungere; verba c-ta, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som står i sammanhang med, förhållande till:</text:span></text:span> somnium quid habuit naturæ c-tum?, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förenlig, egnad för förening:</text:span></text:span> nihil est c-ius, quam, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpŭlāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättning:</text:span> diequinti c. dictum est, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansättning, -fogning; förening:</text:span></text:span> atomorum inter se; rerum, C.; verborum inter se <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordställning och ordfogning),</text:span> Qu.; hominum congressus et c., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōpŭlātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbindande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> blott</text:span> Gramm. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om conjunctioner:</text:span> Char.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concōpŭlo</text:span>, 1.: = copulo: aurum argento, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏquo,</text:span> coxi, coctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: genom eld l. wärme uppmjuka, bereda:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka:</text:span></text:span> cibum, Lucr.; cibaria, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Baka, grädda:</text:span></text:span> panem, Varr.; liba, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillaga, anrätta:</text:span></text:span> coenam, Cato; cibum, medicamenta, Liv.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (metaller):</text:span> æra fornicibus, Liv.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bränna, eldtorka, (steka):</text:span></text:span> laterculos, Cato; sol locum, Varr.; æstas glebas, Vg.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bringa till mognad, göra mör:</text:span></text:span> uvam sol, Vg.; poma cocta et matura, C.; fructus solibus coctus, Pn. <text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om maten i magen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bereda, smälta:</text:span></text:span> C., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka, hopkoka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppgöra, anstifta:</text:span></text:span> bene coctum dabit consilium, Pt.; consilia, bellum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bränna) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwälja, ängsla:</text:span></text:span> cura te c., Enn. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cocta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">destilleradt (kokt och åter afkyldt) watten:</text:span> nivea (æstati apta), Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coctĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af brändt l. smält gods, af tegel:</text:span> lateres, Varr.; lapis, Sen; muri, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Mat)smältning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coctīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är tjenlig att kokas:</text:span> castaneæ, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coctor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kock:</text:span></text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Coctūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kokning; smältning; mogning:</text:span></text:span> nitri; æris, Pn.; brassicæ, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättkokt:</text:span></text:span> caro, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquīnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquīnāris</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquīnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Köks-:</text:span></text:span> forum c-inum, Pt.; vasa c-aria, Pn.; culter c-aris, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (v. obs.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kök, kokkonst:</text:span></text:span> Pall., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquŭlum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kokkärl:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏquus</text:span> (ol. Cocus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏqua</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kock, kokerska:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammankoka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngt med ngt):</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om mat) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smälta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom wärme </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">upplösa, bereda, smälta, bringa till mognad:</text:span></text:span> cibum, Varr.; cibus facillimus ad c-dum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att smälta);</text:span> stomachi calore aliquid, C.; foenum in se c-itur, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: vomicæ facile c-entes, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plåga, qwälja:</text:span></text:span> ego me, Pt. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopkoka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppgöra, öfwerwäga, upptänka:</text:span></text:span> diu deliberandum et c-dum est, utrum - an, C.; clandestina consilia, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kunna smälta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fördraga:</text:span></text:span> odia non c. solum, sed etiam sorbere, C.; civitas senatorem, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concoctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Matsmältning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka bort, ut:</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> pars quarta d-ta erat, L.; mustum usque ad tertiam partem d-tum, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> suavitas orationis austera et solida, non dulcis et d-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utkokt, -lakad),</text:span> C.; multum inde (ex luxuria juvenilis ingenii) d-ent anni, multum ratio limabit, Qu. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(koka bort, fördunsta):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tryta, ej motswara, ej tillfredsställa:</text:span></text:span> non tibi ornithon d-et, Varr.; (minus turpe est creditori, quam) bonæ spei d-re, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej kunna tillfredsställa fordringsegare, göra bankrutt:</text:span></text:span> creditori, Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> fortunæ vitio, non suo, C.; imperium inertiā Cæsarum quasi consenuit et d-xit, Fl. <text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färdigkoka, bringa till mognad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> olus, Hor.; acini d-untur, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. consilia, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcocta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcoctum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">destilleradt och iskyldt watten; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Decoct:</text:span></text:span> hæc est d. Neronis, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcoctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcoctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afkokning, kokning, smältning:</text:span></text:span> radicum, Ap.; gemmarum in melle, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcoctor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som swiker sina creditorer, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bankruttör:</text:span></text:span> rustici, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Sönderkoka), genom kokning göra mör:</text:span></text:span> aliquid in aqua cum sale, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka, smälta, bränna, torka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ut (saften l. dylikt ur ngt, l.) ngt ur -:</text:span> e-tum parum habet suci, Cato; vitium metallis e., Ov.; terram sol, Lucr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedsmälta:</text:span></text:span> statuas, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttänka:</text:span></text:span> malum alicui, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inkoka, koka, insmälta; färga:</text:span></text:span> herbis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) cruor viperinus i-tus, Hor.; radices Baccho, Vg.; argentum alicui rei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försilfra),</text:span> Pn.; vellera Tyrios i-ta rubores, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> pectus honesto i-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> imbutus, infectus, tinctus), Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incoctĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: vasa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förtennade,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incoctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Osmält, okokt:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i bild. (om en plan):</text:span> quidquid est i-um, non expromet, bene coctum dabit, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomkoka, wäl koka; upphetta, torka, bränna; färga; bringa till mognad:</text:span></text:span> carnes, Pn.; sol terram; niger p-tusque calore, Lucr.; sol fructus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Starkt torka; wäl bringa till mognad:</text:span></text:span> acini in callum p-untur; uva p-ta, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcŏquus</text:span> (Col.),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcŏquis</text:span> (id.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcox</text:span>, cŏcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I förtid mogen, brådmogen:</text:span></text:span> fructus, Ct.; vites, uvæ, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brådmogen, förtidig, otidig:</text:span></text:span> ingenium, Qu.; modestia, St.; pugna, Enn.; gaudium, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcŏquo</text:span>, xi, ctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koka upp; koka på nytt; omsmälta:</text:span></text:span> massam (casei), Mt.; r-unt fornacibus enses, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omkoka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">genom kokning föryngra; ombilda, omskapa:</text:span></text:span> nemo me tanquam Peliam recoxerit, C.; ex quinqueviro scriba r-tus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏr,</text:span> cordis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjerta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> c-i suffusus sanguis; c. palpitat (evulsum), C.; micat timore, Ov.; exsultantia haurit c-a pavor pulsans, Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom smekord: ”mitt hjerta,”</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mod (bröst):</text:span></text:span> juvenum fortissima c-a; dura, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förstånd, wett:</text:span></text:span> ex adyto c-is tamquam responsa edere, Lucr.; discidium c-is et linguæ, ut alii nos sapere, alii dicere docerent; stupor c-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Tusc. I. 9); ei sapit cor, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr:</text:span> in læva parte mamillæ nil salit Arcadico juveni, Juv.).<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjerta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">själ</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. från känslans l. sinnelagets sida</text:span> (= animus): meo c-i carus, Ter.; amens malis c., L. 38, 39; c. spectantis tangere querelā; c. purum vitio, Hor.; aliquid c-i est mihi: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ligger mig om hjertat, är mig kärt, angeläget</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personliga och sakliga subject):</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>C., L., Hor.; c-i habere aliquid, Gell.; c-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= af hjertat,</text:span> ex animo) amare aliquem, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Litet hjerta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= ”stackars hjerta”):</text:span> (amor) amburit c. ei, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">smekord = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjerta lilla:</text:span></text:span> meum, Pt. <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">snille, såsom tillnamn för person:</text:span> C. Tusc. I. 9.<text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T1">Corcŭlus</text:span> = corculum c.: Pn.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cordātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(högt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begåfwad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> å förståndets wägnar:</text:span> egregie c., Enn. ap. C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cordāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klokt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cordŏlium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (doleo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjertesorg, ängslan:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concors</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enig, endrägtig:</text:span></text:span> fratres c-issimi; caritas; status civitatis moderatus et c., C.; animi, Vg.; regnum; secum, L.; alicui, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.:</text:span> torus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äktenskap),</text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerensstämmande (harmonisk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jemn, likformig:</text:span></text:span> sono c-i, Ov.; figura; aquis c-ibus totum se jungit flumen, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concordia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sämja, endrägt, enighet:</text:span></text:span> c-am constituere, conglutinare, confirmare, restituere; adducere, reducere in c-am; tantam morum similitudo habebat c-am; reconciliatio c-æ; redire in c-am cum aliquo, C.; perpetua, fidelis, L.; c-ā res parvæ crescunt, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Harmoni, öfwerensstämmelse; genomgående sammanhang:</text:span></text:span> rerum agendarum, C.; rerum c. discors, Hor., Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>oncordia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gudomlighet, som hade ett tempel wid foten af</text:span> Mons Capitolinus: Ov. Fast. I. fin.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concordĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enigt, endrägtigt, i god sämja:</text:span></text:span> congruere inter se, Pt.; vivere cum aliquo c-issime, C.; -ius, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concordo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lefwa i sämja; öfwerensstämma:</text:span></text:span> vir cum uxore, Ter.; judicia animi et opiniones, C.; varii modi (cantus); carmina nervis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Ov.; sermo cum vita, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discors</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oense, osams, oenig, twedrägtig:</text:span></text:span> homines ambitione d-es, C.; civitas secum ipsa, L.; patri filius, Vell.; venti, Ov.; d. cum matre animo, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej öfwerensstämmande, stridig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinsemellan l. med ngn: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Olik:</text:span></text:span> homines moribus d-es, Ct.; sententiæ, linguæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sig sjelf:</text:span> symphonia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oharmonisk),</text:span> Hor.; d-em fetum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= tweskapt</text:span> ɔ: Minotaurum) Pasiphăe utero tulit, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg:. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Osämja, miß-sämja, oenighet, mißhällighet, twedrägt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">strid, upprördt tillstånd:</text:span></text:span> d-æ nascuntur; d-am concitare, sedare, C.; tetra, Hor.; demens; mentis incertæ, Ov.; rerum, Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordiālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förorsakar oenighet:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Full af twedrägt:</text:span></text:span> Sa. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: = discordia, Pacuv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara oense:</text:span></text:span> inter se, Ter.; secum, C.; ab aliquo, Vell.; adversus <text:soft-page-break/>aliquem, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej öfwerensstämma, skilja sig ifrån:</text:span></text:span> a sermone tenui sublime verbum d-at, Qu.; parcus avaro (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) multum, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discordābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej öfwerensstämmande:</text:span></text:span> ingenium, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excors</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hufwudlös, wettlös:</text:span></text:span> nisi qui est admodum e.; anus, C.; turpis et e., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcordia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ”membrana, quæ cordi prætenditur et exta ab inferiori parte viscerum separat,” (Pn.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mellangärdet, hinnan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mellan bröstet och bukcaviteten:</text:span> ossa natura p-is et vitalibus circumdedit, ventri non item, Pn.; cupiditatem Plato subter p. locavit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">De inre,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ädlare </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">delarne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af kroppen</text:span> (p. vocamus uno nomine exta, Pn.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inelfwor, bröst, hjerta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (äfwen såsom säte för förstånd och känsla):</text:span> anulus in p-is piscis inventus est; mortem p-is conceptam tenere, C.; redit virtus in p., Vg.; p. mollia cinguntur libro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Daphne);</text:span> stolidæ mentis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. qual.</text:span>) p., Ov.; leni mulso proluere p., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcordor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Erinra sig, draga sig till minnes; i minnet genomgå, dröja wid minnet af, tanken på ngt; besinna:</text:span></text:span> discere est r.; credo etiam te reminiscentem r-ri; hujus meriti in me r-or; bella a se gesta r.; cum animo meo gradus ætatis tuæ r-or; r-or de lacrimis illis; r-or hoc usurpatum esse; r-or, unde ceciderim, C.; si rite audita r-or, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besinna, betänka:</text:span></text:span> mecum loquor hæc tacitusque r-or, Hor.; quæ sum passura, r-or, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcordātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Erinring:</text:span></text:span> veteris memoriæ non satis explicata r.; præteriti doloris r. secura; benefactorum, ultimi temporis r.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">minnen:</text:span></text:span> fugio r-es; dare alicui r-es, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sōcors</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Festus = Sēcors, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> se = sine <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> cor):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dum, slö:</text:span></text:span> homo non s., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slapp, wårdslös, liknöjd:</text:span></text:span> rerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för allt),</text:span> Ter.; naturā s. negligensque, C.; victoriā s. factus, Sa.; s. animus (Vitellii); s. futuri, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sōcordia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dumhet, slöhet:</text:span></text:span> s. quidam pro ignavia posuerunt, Cato pro stultitia, Fs.; Tiberius non peccabat s-ā, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slapphet, wårdslöshet, liknöjdhet, owerksamhet:</text:span></text:span> philosophia vitanda est: affert enim s-am atque desidiam, C.; s-ā bonum otium conterere; animum situ ac s-ā torpescere sinunt, Sa.; per s-am uti re, L.; languescet industria, intendetur s., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sōcordĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ius: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slappt, liknöjdt:</text:span></text:span> acta res, L.; agere, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏrānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coracinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corax.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏrallum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrallus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cō̆rā</text:span>̆<text:span text:style-name="T1">lium</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cū̆rā̆lium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korall:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōram,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> os, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">acc. sing. fem. af ett adj.</text:span> co-orus?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ansigte mot ansigte, öga mot öga med en person, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I personlig samwaro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med hwarandra l. med ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i ansigtet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (midt i synen) på ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inför</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns (mina, sina) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ögon, personligen:</text:span></text:span> te c. præsens præsentem video, Pt.; c. laudare aliquem, Ter.; c. intueri; c. conferre inter se de aliqua re.; c. agere, loqui de re; c. audire aliquid ex aliquo; c. deferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(instämma en närwarande person),</text:span> C.; timent absentis crudelitatem, velut si c. adsit; existimate, imperatorem hic adesse et hæc c. cernere, Cs.; arguere aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ansigtet),</text:span> L.; jussa c. (id.) non sine conscio surgit marito; c. veni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inför hans, Mæcenas’ ögon);</text:span> rexque paterque audisti c. nec verbo parcius absens, Hor.; c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inför edra ögon),</text:span> quem quæritis, adsum; c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inför drottningen)</text:span> data copia fandi; c. agnoscere vultus alicujus, Vg.; c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inför sina ögon)</text:span> eum confodi jussit, Su.; c. convinci, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Personligen, med egna ögon,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (neml. der ingen person står emot den seende):</text:span> eadem fere, quæ ex nuntiis cognoverat, c. perspicit, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stundom ställd efter sitt nomen): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inför, inför - ögon:</text:span></text:span> c. genero meo, C.; ne pueros c. populo Medea trucidet; c. rege sua de paupertate tacentes plus poscente ferent; te c., Hor.; Germanico c., T.; cantabit vacuus c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ansigtet på)</text:span> latrone viator, Juv. <text:line-break/>3. in c. alicujus = c. aliquo, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏrax,</text:span> ăcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korp:</text:span></text:span> Sol. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hake:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrăcĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korpswart:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orbio, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Hortensia.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orbio, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Corbis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (flätad):</text:span> messoria, C.; pabulatorius, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corbītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med mastkorg:</text:span> navis, Lucil. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corbīta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sådant skepp, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Corvett:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corbŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten korg:</text:span></text:span> Cato; uvarum, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orbŭlo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Domitia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corcodilus = Crocodilus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corculum,<text:line-break/>Corculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orcȳra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Ioniska hafwet.</text:span><text:line-break/>Corcȳræus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cordate,<text:line-break/>Cordatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cordax,</text:span> ăcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dans i den gamla attiska comoedien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om det, som har en dansande rörelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dansande:</text:span></text:span> trochæum c-ca appellat Aristoteles, C.; c-es sententiæ, Front.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cordolium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ordŭba, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Spanien</text:span> (Cordova).<text:line-break/>Cordŭbensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cordus</text:span> (Chordus). <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senfödd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wuxen:</text:span></text:span> agnus, Varr.; fenum, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orfīnium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Pelignernes land.</text:span><text:line-break/>Corfīniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coriaceus,<text:line-break/>Coriago <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏriandrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏriandrus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coriander</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en wäxt):</text:span> Col., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coriarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrinna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrinthus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Grekland.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏrinthĭăcus,<text:line-break/>Cŏrinthĭensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cŏrinthĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af corinthisk brons</text:span> (æs C-um): C-ia, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">corinthiska bronssaker.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. columnæ C-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med corinthiska capitäl),</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏriŏli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏriŏlānus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. tillnamn</text:span> (C. Marcius).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrippus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏrium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sällan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tjock) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. om djur), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">läder:</text:span></text:span> elephanti; periit meum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ryggläder),</text:span> Pt.; animantes c-o tectæ, C.; canis c-o uncto non deterretur, Hor.; piscium, Pn.; c-o suo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på egen risk),</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på frukter:</text:span> castaneæ, Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kalkband, stucco; lager</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> parietum, Vitr.; chartæ secundum c., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏriāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af hud:</text:span></text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏriāgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hudsjuka:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏriārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: frutex = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som brukas till hudberedning:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏriārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Garfware:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ormăsa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Pisidien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ornēlius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corneolus,<text:line-break/>-nesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornetum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Cornus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Cornicen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornīcor,<text:line-break/>Cornīcula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornix.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornĭcularius,<text:line-break/>Cornĭculatus,<text:line-break/>Cornĭculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ornĭcŭlum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cornĭcŭlānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ornĭfĭcius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornifrons,<text:line-break/>Corniger,<text:line-break/>Cornipes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cornix,</text:span> īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kråka:</text:span></text:span> annosa, vaga, vetula, Hor.; garrula, Ov.; sinistra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från wenster, lyckosam),</text:span> Vg.; inauspicata, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordspråk:</text:span> c-i oculos configere, effodere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(narra en skarpsynt),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornīcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sqwattra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (prata):</text:span> secum, Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cornu,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornum</text:span>, i, Varr., C.;<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornus</text:span>, i, Lucr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i hufwudet hos hornboskap, skaldjur m. m.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> animantes c-bus armatæ, C.; ducere, tenere taurum c-ū; c-a arborea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(greniga);</text:span> c-bus inter se luctari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stångas),</text:span> Vg.; c-ua cava, solida, decidua, adunca in dorsum, in adversum; erecta, contorta; cochlearum; ramosa cervi, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. talesätt:</text:span> c-ua obvertere alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisa ngn tänderna),</text:span> Pt.; surgere in c-ua, irasci in c-ua, Vg.; vinum c-ua addit pauperi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwer honom mod),</text:span> Hor.; sumit pauper c-ua mero, O.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom ämne i kroppar, t. ex. i hästs l. oxes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hof:</text:span></text:span> ungula sonat c-u, Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fågels </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">näbb:</text:span></text:span> Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ögat (hornhinnan),</text:span> Pn.; Indicum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">elfenben,</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ting, som äro af horn eller ha form deraf eller bådadera:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blåshorn (herdehorn, trumpet),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. krökt blåsinstrument, ware sig af horn eller annat ämne:</text:span> non tuba directi, non æris c-ua flexi, Ov.; pastorale canit signum c-u recurvo; c. æreum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dryckeshorn, flaska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med hornform; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ymnighetshorn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom attribut för</text:span> Copia, Pomona, Flora, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flodgudar m. m.):</text:span> vinum per c-ua faucibus infundere, Col.; c. bilibri oleum cauli instillare; aurea fruges Italiæ pleno defundit Copia c., Hor.; c. Amaltheæ cinctum recentibus herbis, pomis plenum, nympha donum tulit Jovi, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Båge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af horn:</text:span> flexile c. tendere, Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som bildar wäggarne i en lykta:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">resonanssidor af lyran:</text:span> corna, quæ resonant ad nervos in cantibus, C. de nat. D. II. 59.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom prydnader på en hjelm:</text:span> præfregit c. alterum galeæ, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>III. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hörn, utskjutande del, arm, ände, spets</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett land, en ort, en anläggning, arm af en flod o. s. w.:</text:span> in duobus velut c-bus Græciæ, L.; portūs c-ua, C.; c. Parnassi, St.; in c. tribunalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ett hörn af),</text:span> T.; Nilus digestus in septem c-ua, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">månens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn:</text:span></text:span> obtusa lunæ, Vg.; cornua extremæ lunæ evanescunt, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flygel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en här:</text:span> sinistrum et dexterum, Ter.; tenere c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(befinna sig på),</text:span> C.; circumvenire aciem a c-bus; locare equites pro c-bus, L.; promovere c-ua, Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> experiamur, si possimus commovere c-ua disputationis tuæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rubba Dina argument),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">segelrårnas ändar (rånockar):</text:span> c. antennarum, Vg.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ändarne, knapparne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på de stafwar, wid hwilka bokrullar fästades och kring hwilka de wecklades:</text:span> Ov., Tib., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bli hornartad, hård:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corneus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corneŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Horn-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som är af horn l. liksom af horn:</text:span> rostrum; c-lus introitus aurium, C.; arcus, Ov.; color c., Pn.; non est mihi c-ea fibra, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭcen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hornblåsare:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Cornu:<text:line-break/>a. papilionis, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dryckeshorn; tratt:</text:span> Col. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjelmprydnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> cornu II. f.): Pn.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom militäriskt hederstecken:</text:span> c-is armillisque argenteis donare equites, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭcŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">adjutant i romerska arméen:</text:span> tribuni, præfecti, subpræfecti et c., Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: luna, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭfer</text:span> (Mcb.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hornbärande, behornad:</text:span></text:span> cervus; caput Fauni, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭfrons</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med horn i pannan:</text:span> Liv. Andr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornĭpes</text:span>, pĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hornhofwad, -fotad:</text:span></text:span> equus, Vg.; Faunus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornuātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hornformig:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornūtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Behornad:</text:span></text:span> quadrupedes, Varr.; luna, Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Bĭcornĭger, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den twåhornade (om Bacchus):</text:span> Ov. Her.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭcornis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twåhornad:</text:span></text:span> furca, Rhenus, Vg.; luna, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭcornis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ūnĭcornis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tre-, enhornad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornuatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Cornus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cornus,</text:span> us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hagtorn, benwed, cornellträd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom träd:</text:span> Pn., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spjut af sådant träd:</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lund af cornellträd:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af cornellträd:</text:span> virgulta, Vg.; venabula, Ov.; pyxis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cornum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cornellfrukt:</text:span> rubicunda, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något som är af cornellträd: (spjut),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cornutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cornu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏroebus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coroll . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corona.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏrōna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krans, rund, rand:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krans, som bäres på hufwudet l. halsen:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> florea et rosea, Pt.; habere in capite, in collo, C.; nectere alicui, Hor.; honoris c. populo data; aurea c-ā donare aliquem, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. såsom belöning i romerska arméen, af åtskilliga slag:</text:span> c. muralis, obsidionalis, civica, navalis, L. <text:line-break/>c. sub corona vendere, venire: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sälja, säljas såsom slaf (med krans på hufwudet),</text:span> Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krets,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omgifwande skara af menniskor, t. ex.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid en domstolsförhandling:</text:span> ipsi tibi maximā c-ā causa dicenda est, C.; clamor c-æ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af en här, som omsluter en ort:</text:span> c-ā urbem cingere, circumdare, aggredi, capere, defendere, Cs., L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rand,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kring en åker:</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kranslist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en byggnad:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>c. montium c-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en krans af berg)</text:span> circumdatus populus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrolla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pt., Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrollāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kranshandlerska:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrollārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: c. dicitur, si additum, præter quam quod debitum ejus, a corollis, quod eæ, quum placuerant actores, iis dari in scena solitæ, Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hedersskänk (douceur):</text:span></text:span> C., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som anwändes till kransar:</text:span> æs <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brons),</text:span> Pn.; aurum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som af provincialer plägade betalas till en proconsul, som wunnit en seger och fått triumph sig tillerkänd),</text:span> C.; opus c-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stucco till kranslister),</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōnāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kransförsäljare, -erska:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōnis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swäng (krumelur),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed en skrift afslutas:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kransa, bekransa:</text:span></text:span> aliquem, C.; vina, Vg.; aliquem fronde, Hor.; postes lauro, Qu.; c-ri Olympiă <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna pris wid spelen i Ol.),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsluta:</text:span></text:span> silva aquas c-at, Ov.; aditum custode c., Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrōnāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blommor till en krans:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coronæus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corone <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Coronea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coronamentum,<text:line-break/>Coronarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corona.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrōnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Messenien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏrōnæus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrōnēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏrōnæus,<text:line-break/>Cŏrōnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrōnĕus, ei, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coronides <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Coronis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Coronis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corona.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏrōnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏrōnīdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Coronis’ (och Apollos) son</text:span> = Aesculapius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corono <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corona.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Corpus,</text:span> ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kropp:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ämne, materia, massa:</text:span> c. sine loco intelligi non potest, C.; individua c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(atomer),</text:span> C., Lucr.; quattuor illa omnia gignentia c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(elementerna),</text:span> C.; facere et fungi sine c-e nulla potest res, Lucr.<text:line-break/>II. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">organisk kropp: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c. quasi vas est aut aliquod animi receptaculum; discessus animi a c-e; c. exercendum est, ut animo parere possit; animus est in c-e, tanquam alienæ domi; animus vacans c-e; c-e senex, non animo; c-is contentio, voluptas, dolor; c-is pars; c. ita figuratum, ut temperatione naturæ vigeat et sentiat, C.; omnis nostra vis in animo et c-e sita est; vis c-is, virtus animi, Sa.; non tu c. eras sine pectore; salubres c-i malvæ; c. plenum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mätt, stoppad),</text:span> Hor.; c-is statura, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på fyllighet l. magerhet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kropp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kött), hull:</text:span> c. solidum et suci plenum, Ter.; c-is tenuitas, siccitas, gracilitas; ossa c-i subjecta, C.; c. tenerum et juvenile, Vg.; tenuatum, Hor.; habitus c-is; c. exile, amplum, Su.; c. facere, amittere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lägga till på, mista hullet),</text:span> Ov., C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> sunt oratores, qui non tam habitus c-is opimos, quam gracilitates consectentur, C.; c. eloquentiæ, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kropp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till hufwud (bål):</text:span> caput est a corpore longe, Ov.; avulsum humeris caput et sine nomine c., Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lik:</text:span></text:span> corpus Priamo reddidi, Hectorem abstuli, Acc. ap. C.; non Hectora traxit (Achilles), sed c. quod fuerat H-is, C.; occisorum, Cs.; c-a extra vallum abjecta ostentui, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hela det lefwande, enkannerligen menskliga wäsendet = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lif, person;</text:span></text:span> ut c-a nostra ab injuria tuta forent, Sa.; et c-a et omnia sua patriæ restituere; mollirent iras et, quibus fors c-a dedisset, darent animos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sina hjertan,</text:span> Sabinæ); serva c-a, L.; pro tribus c-bus (matre et duabus filiabus) talentum auri accipias, Ct.; huc (in equum Trojanum) delecta virorum c-a condunt, Vg.; pro c-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att ej bli stympad)</text:span> nummos dare, Hor.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kropp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = ngt helt i förhållande till delarne:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c. navium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skrof);</text:span> c. munitionum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det hela, systemet af förskansningarne),</text:span> Cs.; c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(volum)</text:span> modicum libri conficere; c. universitatis, C.; c. omnis juris Romani, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samhälls-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">samfundskropp; samfund, corporation, stam:</text:span></text:span> commune velut humanitatis c.; totum reipublicæ c. curent neve, dum alteri parti consulant, alteram negligant, C.; multitudo nisi legibus in unius populi c. coalescere non poterat; oriundi a Sabinis sui c-is creari regem (Romæ) volebant, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŏrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kroppslig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som finnes hos kroppen:</text:span> vitia, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŏreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kroppslig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till andlig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">materiel:</text:span></text:span> natura, Lucr.; ignis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŏror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Få kropp:</text:span></text:span> semen animatur et c-atur, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŏrātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kroppsbyggnad, wäxt:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hullig:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpŭlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Godt hull:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corpuscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. liten kropp:</text:span> Sen.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">atom:</text:span></text:span> C., Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. c. facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få hull),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭcorpor</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har twå slags kropp (om en centaur):</text:span> C. poēt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concorpŏrālis</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kamrat:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concorpŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Införlifwa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incorpŏrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Okroppslig, immateriel:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incorpŏreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">okroppslig:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incorpŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">införlifwa:</text:span> Amm., Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭcorpor</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har tre kroppar:</text:span> forma t-is umbræ, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Correct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corrigo, Rego.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corrept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corripio, Rapio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Corrĭgia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skorem:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corrigo,<text:line-break/>Corripio,<text:line-break/>Corrupt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rego, Rapio, Rumpo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cors = Cohors.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orsĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ön Corsica.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orsĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>orsus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Corsicanare och corsicansk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cortex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bark, skal; kork:</text:span></text:span> denudare truncos c-e, C.; c. glandis, Pn.; ovi, Vitr.; nabis sine c-e, Hor.; summā c. levis innatat unda, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omgifwen af bark:</text:span> pix, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortĭceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af bark:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortĭcōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Barkig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med tjock bark:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: olivæ, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcortĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afbarka, skala:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcortĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskalning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cortīna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kittel, kyp:</text:span></text:span> plumbea c. in locum posita, quo fluat oleum, Cato; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> cæli c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= hwalf),</text:span> Enn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trefot:</text:span></text:span> Phoebi, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortīnāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rum, der kittlar förwaras:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cortīnŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Cortina: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ortōna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cortōnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corvinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corvus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corulus = Corylus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Corus = Caurus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏruscus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Darrande, dallrande, nickande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fram-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">glimmande, skimrande:</text:span></text:span> silvæ; capita cristis, Vg.; vis fulminis, C.; ignis auro c., Vg.; sol, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrusco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hastigt röra sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Darra, fladdra, nicka, framglimma, -skimra:</text:span></text:span> apes pennis, Vg.; abies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bjelke),</text:span> Juv.; flamma inter nubes, Pacuv. ap. C.: fulgor, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swänga:</text:span></text:span> gæsa manu, Vg.; hastam, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: (= stöta hufwudet l. hornen mot ngn) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stångas:</text:span></text:span> caput alicui opponere c-ntem, C.; agni ludentes c-ant, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏruscāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏruscātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skimmer:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Corvus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korp:</text:span></text:span> C., Ov., Hor.; c-o rarior albo, Ps.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Båtshake, harpun:</text:span></text:span> Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Corvīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korp-:</text:span></text:span> ovum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏry̆bas, antis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cabirernes prest.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŏry̆bantĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōry̆cus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: med sand fylld säck, hwarmed man i gymnasierna öfwade sina krafter.</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfningsfält:</text:span></text:span> vocis meæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cōry̆cēum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe för öfning med</text:span> corycus: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōry̆cus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ortsnamn (städer och landtudde i Asien).</text:span><text:line-break/>Cōry̆cĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: antrum C-ium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid foten af Parnassus; deraf</text:span> C-ius = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parnassisk.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cōry̆cis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adj. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏry̆lus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hassel:</text:span></text:span> fragilis, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏry̆lētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hasselskog:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏrymbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blom-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fruktklase: murgrönskrans:</text:span></text:span> Col., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">knappar i skeppets för och akter:</text:span> Vfl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏrymbĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bär murgrönskransar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kransad med murgrön:</text:span></text:span> Bacchus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏry̆phæus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hufwud-man:</text:span></text:span> Epicureorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏry̆thus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cōrȳtus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gōrȳtus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koger:</text:span></text:span> Vg., St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cos (cotis) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cautes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōs (<text:span text:style-name="T2">cas. obl.</text:span> Co) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏos, ŏi, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i ægeiska hafwet.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ōus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏsa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien (äfwen</text:span> Cossa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Cosæ).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Lucanien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏsānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cosmētes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cosmēta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slaf, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kammartjenare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ombesörjde romersk dames toilette:</text:span> Juv. VI. 476.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cosmētrĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kammarjungfru:</text:span></text:span> Næv. ap. Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>osmoe, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">statsråd eller regerings-collegium på Creta:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cossim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coxim.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ossus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen</text:span> (Cornelius).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Costa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Refben:</text:span></text:span> tergora diripiunt c-is, Vg.; c-æ aselli, leonis, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sidostycke, sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> navium, Pn.: aheni, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Costātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med starka refben:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Costum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk buske och deraf beredd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Balsam:</text:span></text:span> Achæmenium, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cothon,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags rundt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dryckeskärl:</text:span></text:span> Cs. Afr. 63.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏthurnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöfwel:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jagtstöfwel:</text:span></text:span> ad pedem apte convenit, C.; virginibus Tyriis mos est - suras alte vincire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omlinda medelst remmar)</text:span> cothurno, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den tragiske skådespelarens fotbetäckning - deraf symbol för tragisk poesi, tragisk konst, högstämd l. högtidlig stil:</text:span> hunc socci pedem (iambum) cepere grandesque c-i; grande munus Cecropio repetes c-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom tragisk skald),</text:span> Hor.; Sophocleus, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏthurnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: klädd i cothurn = tragisk skådespelare:</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Högstämd, högtidlig, allwarlig:</text:span></text:span> Maronis c-i opus, Mt.; sermo, Mcb.; Flora non est inter c-as deas, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Coticula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cautes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cotidianus,<text:line-break/>Cotidie = Quotid . . .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>otta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Aurelia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cottăbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klang, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smäll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af i höjden kastadt win mot ett kopparkärl, hwari det nedföll - en i Grekland öfwad lek (jfr</text:span> C. Tusc. I. c. 40; Xenoph. Hist. I. 2). - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf bildl.:</text:span> cave, ne c-i bubuli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oxsmällar</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af läderpiska)</text:span> in te crebri crepent, Pt. Trin. 1011.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ottius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Alpis C-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Alpes C-æ = Mont Genevre, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett af de sydligare alppassen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏtŭla</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏty̆la</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags kärl l. mått för wåta waror</text:span> (6 cyathi): Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏturnix,</text:span> īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Waktel:</text:span></text:span> c-es inter sua proelia vivunt, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏtys, y̆is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (Cotus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thraciskt konunganamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏtytto, ūs, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thracisk gudomlighet.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŏtyttĭa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cotyttos fest.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏvīnus</text:span> (-innus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gallisk (britannisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stridswagn, liewagn:</text:span></text:span> Luc., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŏvīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wagnskämpe:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cous <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coxa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höft:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coxendix,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höftled:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Coxim</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cossim, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På huk:</text:span></text:span> insidere, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rabra aqua, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bäck i närheten af Rom.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crābro,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bål-geting:</text:span></text:span> irritare, Pt.; asper, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>răgus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Lycien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crambē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kål:</text:span></text:span> occidit miseros c. repetita magistros, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ranii, ōrum <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rānon <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rannon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crānōnius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rantor, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crāpŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rus:</text:span></text:span> edormire et exhalare, C.; c-ā plenus, L.; discutere, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusdryck:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crāpŭlārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hörer till rus eller dryckeslag: Pt.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crāpŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Berusad:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crās,</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I morgon:</text:span></text:span> c. scies, C.; quid sit futurum c., fuge quærere, Hor.; c. vocare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bjuda för morgondagen),</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Morgondagen:</text:span></text:span> istud, Mt.; c. hesternum, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crastĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Morgondagens, morgon-:</text:span></text:span> dies c. dat ad cogitandum -, C.; Aurora; Titan, Vg.; quis scit, an adjiciant hodiernæ tempora summæ c-a di superi, Hor.; c. ætas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= framtiden),</text:span> St. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crastĭnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: = in c. vocare, Pt.; in c. differre, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crastĭno</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I morgon:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcrastĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppskjuta till morgondagen, uppskjuta:</text:span></text:span> rem differre et p., C. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcrastĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppskjutande:</text:span></text:span> tarditas et p. in rebus gerendis odiosa est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcrastĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dröja till morgondagen:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crassus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjock:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till dimensionen (mots.</text:span> tenuis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">smal): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjock, diger:</text:span></text:span> arbores c-æ digitos duos, Cato; homo c., Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till consistensen (mots.</text:span> subtilis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fin): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjock, tät, grof, grumsig, fet:</text:span></text:span> āer c. et concretus; caelum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(luft);</text:span> caligo, C.; ager <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fet),</text:span> Cato; unguentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grumsig);</text:span> toga <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grof),</text:span> Hor.; farrago, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grof</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">enfaldig, konstlös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> subtilis; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">synonym.</text:span> pinguis): senex, Varr.; sapiens abnormis c-āque Minerva, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crasse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjockt:</text:span></text:span> vasa picare, Cato.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konst-, smaklöst:</text:span></text:span> illepide c-eque compositum, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassesco</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjockna:</text:span></text:span> aër, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fetna:</text:span></text:span> turtur, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjocklek:</text:span></text:span> parietum, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjockhet:</text:span></text:span> aëris, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassĭvēnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (vena): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjockådrig:</text:span></text:span> acer, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjockna, förtätas:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crassāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjocklek; tjockt ämne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (grums):</text:span> Pn., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percrassus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ganska tjock:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcrassus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owanligt tjock:</text:span></text:span> cortex, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcrassŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något tjock:</text:span></text:span> Clp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rassus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Licinia.<text:line-break/>Crassiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crastin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cras.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rătæis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crātēr,</text:span> ēris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crātēra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. ”blandare,” blandningskärl) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i vasform), hwari winet blandades med watten och hwarur det med</text:span> cyathi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">östes i bägare</text:span> (scyphus, poculum): c-es magni, aheni, auro solidi, Vg.; c-æ pulcherrimæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> fuso c-es olivo, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kar, bäcken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en springkälla:</text:span> in fonticulo c., Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en vulcans </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crater</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. liknande fördjupning:</text:span> Aetnæ, Lucr., Pn.; currum Plutonis tellus medio c-e recepit, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rătĕrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crātes,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korg-, galler-, flätwerk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af widje l. dylikt.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stängsel, häck:</text:span></text:span> claudere pecus textis c-bus, Hor.; locus conseptus c-bus, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarunder förbrytare dränktes:</text:span> c. superne injecta mergi, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för bruk i krig: fascin (hwarmed grafwar fyllas); skyddswägg o. s. w.:</text:span> L., Ct. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Harf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">trumla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kubb):</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> c. pectorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bröstkorg);</text:span> favorum, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crātīcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som består af korswerk:</text:span> parietes, Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crātīcula</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halster:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crātio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Harfwa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rāthis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Lucanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Craticius,<text:line-break/>Craticula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crates.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rătīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crates.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rătippus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Creat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Creo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crēber,</text:span> bra, brum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> cresco?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förefinnes i massa och med små mellanrum:</text:span> delectabatur c-o funali <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fackeltåg),</text:span> C.; salictum, Cato; arbores, ædificia, Cs.; ignes, Sa.; c-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i massor)</text:span> lapides cecidere caelo, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tätt besatt med:</text:span> locus arundinibus, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tiden:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som följer tätt på hwartannat: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät, ständig, idkelig:</text:span></text:span> contentiones proeliorum; sermo; peccata c-a et quasi quotidiana, C.; excursiones; nuntii, N.; gemitus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos hwilken ngt följer tätt på hwartannat, som ofta gör ngt, flitig med ngt:</text:span> Thucydides ita c. est rerum frequentiā, ut numero sententiarum verba consequatur; in scribendo c., C.; procellit c. Africus; densis ictibus c. utrāque manu pulsat, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbră</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. plur. neutr.</text:span>),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbre</text:span> (Vitr.),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbro</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbrĭter</text:span> (Vitr.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tätt; tidt och ofta, ideligen:</text:span></text:span> perlucet villa, quam cribrum c-ius, Pt.; pede terram c-a ferit equus, Vg.; c-o sarrire, Cato; mittere literas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbresco</text:span>, brui (<text:line-break/>Crēbesco, bui), 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa tätare, tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> c-unt optatæ auræ, Vg.; fragor, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om rykten: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utbreda sig; taga fart;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.</text:span> = fama c-scit: sermo, Vg.; fama; motum a Vespasiano bellum c-scit, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēbrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Täthet, ständighet, idelighet, talrikhet:</text:span></text:span> arborum, Vitr.; literarum, officiorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrēbresco</text:span>, brui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēbresco</text:span> (<text:line-break/>Incrēbesco), brui (bui), 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa tät, tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> ventus, C.; auster, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa allmän, gängse, sprida sig:</text:span></text:span> consuetudo, sermo, C.; rumor, fama, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ofta göra:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percrēbresco</text:span> (<text:line-break/>Percrēbesco), brui (bui), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa allmän, gängse, wanlig; blifwa allmänt bekant:</text:span></text:span> fama, Cs.; opinio, scelus, C.; conjugia consobrinorum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crēdo</text:span> (creduam, -as, Pt.), dĭdi, dĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tro:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hafwa förtroende till, lita på:</text:span></text:span> alicui, C.; loco, tempori; virtuti militum, Sa.; parum alicui, Cs.; heu formose puer nimium ne crede colori, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtro, betro, anförtro;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">se rei,</text:span> poēt.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tro sig till:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> se alicui, Pt.; consilia, animum, vitam alicui, Ter.; fidei alicujus aliquem, C.; se suaque alienissimis, Cs.; fortunas suas alicui, Sa.; navis, tibi c-tum debes Virgilium finibus Atticis, Hor.; se pugnæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Låna:</text:span></text:span> pecuniam alicui; res, pecuniæ c-tæ, C., Cs.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (på hans ord;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>; poēt. <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt (på sanningen, äktheten af ngt:</text:span> rei, de re; c. alicui aliquid, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngn i, på ngt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hålla för sant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med pronominala och allmänna nominala obj.:</text:span> aliquid), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på ngns ord), (icke twifla) att -:</text:span> mihi crede <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tro mig!),</text:span> C.; c-e mihi, militat omnis amans, Ov.; c. visis, somniis, criminibus allatis; non temere c. de aliqua re; hoc magis c-o; c. facinus; c. ea, quæ non sunt c-nda; re c-ta, C.; his auctoribus, Cs.; aliquid pro vero, certo, Sa.; Romani satis c-bant patribus (dicentibus), regem raptum esse procellā; bovem locutam (esse), cui rei priore anno fides non fuerat, c-tum est, L.; perjuri arte Sinonis c-ta res; audit is c.; Cassandra non unquam c-ta Teucris, Vg.; caelo tonantem c-idimus Jovem regnare; c-at Judæus Apella; ne, quodcunque volet, poscat sibi fabula credi, Hor.; c-o pudicitiam Saturno rege moratam in terris, Juv.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tro</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mena, föreställa sig, anse, hålla före:</text:span></text:span> c-o vos, judices, mirari; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn. parenthetiskt</text:span> credo = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som jag tror, jag skulle tro, ofta ironiskt = kantänka:</text:span> male, c-o, mererer de civibus, si ad eorum cognitionem illa divina ingenia transferrem, C.; Pompejus insidias timens, (c-o quod hæc præter spem acciderant), Cs.; aliquem idoneum c.; maesti (c-res victos = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man skulle trott dem wara - -)</text:span> in castra redeunt, L.; haud, c-o, invisus caelestibus auras vitales carpis, Vg.; c-itur comoedia minus oneris habere, Hor.; c-batur Drusus, si rerum potitus foret, libertatem redditurus, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdĭtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lån:</text:span></text:span> Sall., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trolig, trowärdig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om uppgifter):</text:span> conjectura, narratio, C.; c-e est, numen adesse, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdĭbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett troligt sätt:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Borgenär, långifware:</text:span></text:span> fraudare c-es, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjd för att tro, lättrogen, snartrogen:</text:span></text:span> auditor; se præbere c-um, C.; c. alicui, Vg.; carpe diem, quam minimum c-a postero; spes c-a animi mutui, Hor.; c. fama inter gaudentes et <text:soft-page-break/>incuriosos, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crēdŭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättrogenhet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accrēdo</text:span>, dĭdi, dĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta tro till ngt, tro ngn på hans ord:</text:span></text:span> alicui aliquid, Pt.; alicui, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> non a., C., N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrēdo</text:span> (-duo, Pt.), dĭdi, dĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtro, anförtro:</text:span></text:span> auri thesaurum alicui; aliquid taciturnitati alicujus, Pt.; fortunas suas alicui commendare et c-re, C.; nugas suas alicui, vites solo, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēdĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aldrig trodd, otrolig:</text:span> Sen., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēdĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otrolig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta blott hyperboliskt epithet):</text:span> i-ia narrat, Ter.; crimen i-e confingunt; virtus singularis et i,; perversitas, C.; fama, Vg.; i-e auditu, Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otillförlitlig:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēdĭbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otroligt:</text:span></text:span> delector, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">icke willig att tro, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twiflande:</text:span></text:span> quidquid ostendes mihi sic, i. odi, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otrolig:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēdŭlitas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">otrogenhet, twifwelsjuka:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crematio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cremo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕmĕra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">m.,</text:span> Ov.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten flod i Etrurien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crĕmĕrensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕmo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bränna; upp-, förbränna:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> damnatum poenam sequi oportebat, ut igni c-retur, Cs.; mortuum, C., N.; Ilium, Hor.; urbem, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om offer:</text:span> spolia Vulcano, L.; hostiam, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbränning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrĕmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbränna, genom eld förstöra:</text:span></text:span> domos super se ipsos; arma igne, subdito igne, L., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕmōna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Italien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crĕmōnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕmōnis jugum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett alp-paß, wäl</text:span> = Mont Cenis, L. XXI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕmor,</text:span> ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saft,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> pressad ur säd och andra wäxter:</text:span> Pt., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>remŭtius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Creo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> cresco):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om naturen, jorden): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alstra, frambringa:</text:span></text:span> natura c-at et tuetur omnia; natura c-at homines et fingit - -; quæ in terris gignuntur, in hominum usum c-antur omnia, C.; terra c-at omnia, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om menniskor och djur) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Föda, afla, blifwa far</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mor till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> Silvius Aenean Silvium c-at, L.; fortes c-antur fortibus et bonis: est in juvencis - patrum virtus; quæritur argentum puerisque beata c-ndis uxor, Hor.; Cæculus Volcani stirpe c-tus, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frambringa, gifwa uppkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förorsaka, anstifta:</text:span></text:span> similitudo errorem; periculum alicui; artis proprium c-re aliquid; in <text:soft-page-break/>urbibus luxuries c-atur, C.; fastidium, Pn.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om wal i staten):</text:span> consules, C., Cs.; magistratus, Cs.; ducem bello; regem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till k.)</text:span> aliquem, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Creātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wal:</text:span></text:span> magistratuum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Creātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fader</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och oeg. men.):</text:span> ipse deûm c., C. poēt.; Romulus hujus urbis c., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Creātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Moder:</text:span></text:span> natura rerum c., Lucr.; diva c. (Aeneæ), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcreo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framalstra, alstra:</text:span></text:span> vis terræ ex minutissimis stirpibus magnos ramos truncosque, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om mannen; åtminstone aldrig om qwinnan ensamt):</text:span> natura ingenerat præcipuum quendam amorem eorum, qui p-ti sunt, C.; Proca Numitorem atque Amulium p-at, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcreātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aflande:</text:span></text:span> liberorum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcreātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcreātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fader,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föräldrar; moder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i oeg. men.):</text:span> a p-bus amari; mundi p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skapare)</text:span> deus; philosophia p-x omnium laudatarum artium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcreo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter frambringa, skapa:</text:span></text:span> solis lumen, Lucr.; carnes cibus, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter lifwa, styrka, wederqwicka, lisa; återställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till krafterna);</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medialt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hemta sig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen:</text:span> ex vulnere, ex morbo r-ri; voculæ r-ndæ causa, C.; vires r., Lucr.; arbor æstivā r-atur aurā; tenuatum corpus, Hor.; r-ndæ defectioni cibum afferre, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinnet, modet:</text:span> animos afflictos r.; conspectus vester mentem meam r-t; literis amicorum r-ri; ex magno timore se r-re, C.; animum; a timore se, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om liflösa l. abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bringa till lif</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krafter igen; återställa:</text:span></text:span> veritas debilitata tandem æquitate talium virorum r-atur; urbes dirutas r., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcreātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillfrisknande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crepax <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crepo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕper,</text:span> ĕra, ĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (vox fere obsoleta): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mörk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twifwelaktig, wådlig:</text:span></text:span> res c. dicitur pro dubia a Sabinis, Varr.; bellum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpuscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gryning;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oftast) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skymning:</text:span></text:span> primo c-o, Pt.; sera c-a, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕpĭda,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: (κρηπίς): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sandal, toffel:</text:span></text:span> C., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭdārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Toffel-:</text:span></text:span> sutor, culter, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭdātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klädd i tofflor:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭdŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕpīdo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> v. gr.: (κρηπίς): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. utskjutande rand l. omfattning kring ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fot, sockel, postament</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kring byggnad, statue o. d.:</text:span> obelisci, Pn.; c. ambibat tumulum, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trottoir:</text:span></text:span> Diogenes in c-e collocatus, Val.; nulla c. vacat (mendicis), Juv.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hamnbrygga, kaj:</text:span></text:span> omnes urbis c-es pirata accessit, C.; ratis stabat celsi c-e saxi, Vg.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hög strand, brädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid en flod:</text:span> fluvius continetur c-bus, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crepit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crepo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĕpo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm. om oarticulerade, twärt afbrutna ljud): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klappa, smälla, skallra, slamra, knaka, spraka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> fores, Ter.; sistrum, Ov.; dentes, Ps.; flamma, arma, catena, Sen.; lympha pede c-nte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(porlande)</text:span> desilit, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knaka, braka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i sönder:</text:span> domus, Sen. ep. 96.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">causativt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klappa; låta ljuda, skalla:</text:span></text:span> populus frequens lætum sonum, Hor.; sonum, Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prata, slamra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> antiquum genus (<text:span text:style-name="T2">obj.</text:span>), Lucr.; quis post vina gravem militiam c-at?; si quid Stertinius veri c-at, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knarrande:</text:span></text:span> mola, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skallra, slamra, spraka, smattra, gny, knaka:</text:span></text:span> flamma; æra; auster; multa grandine nimbi culminibus c-ant; leni c-bat bractea vento; duro sub vulnere mālæ c-bant, Vg.; arma, Ov.; ciconia, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭtāculum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭtācillum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skramla, skallra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom leksak):</text:span> puerilia, Qu.; = sistrum, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knarrande, skallrande, klappande, slamrande, smäll, gny:</text:span></text:span> cardinum; ventris, Pt.; dentium, pedum, plagarum, C.; gladiorum, Cs.; imbrium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crĕpundia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skramla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom leksak l. såsom ett slags musikaliskt instrument</text:span> (sistrum): Pt., Ter., C.; Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrĕpo</text:span>, ui, (ĭtum), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (samman), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">knäppa, gny:</text:span></text:span> ostium, Ter.; digitis, C.; arma; armis, gladiis ad scuta, Cs., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slå, smälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans, mot hwartannat:</text:span> æra, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcrĕpĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. brusten?): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utlefwad:</text:span></text:span> senex, Pt.; anus, Ter.; ætas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discrĕpo</text:span>, ui, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mißljuda, wara oharmonisk:</text:span></text:span> ut in fidibus, quamvis paulum d-ent, a sciente animadverti solet, sic videndum est in vita, ne quid d-et, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afwika, ej öfwerensstämma, swära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngt l. hwartannat:</text:span> omnia peccata æque d-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från det rätta);</text:span> ea, quæ multum ab humanitate d-ant; d-uit ab Antonii divisio nostra; hæc duo inter se verbo d-re, re unum sonare videntur; philosophi de ea re d-ant; nulla in re inter se d.; facta cum dictis d-ant, C.; primo ne medium, medium ne d-et imo (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara omtwistad, föremål för olika meningar:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">impers.</text:span>: d-at inter auctores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(meningsolikhet råder -);</text:span> d-at de latore legis; haud d-at, quin -, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">personl.</text:span>: causa d-at, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är omtwistad,</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discrĕpantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brist på öfwerensstämmelse; meningsolikhet:</text:span></text:span> in vitam nullam d-am conferre debemus; rerum est, non verborum d. inter Stoicos et Peripateticos, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discrĕpātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Osämja:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrĕpo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klappa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälla, gny, susa, knäppa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w. (emot ngn, för ngns öron):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> discus; quidquid i-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för hwarje knäpp som hörts),</text:span> Catilina timetur, C.; arma, L., mālis; clipeo, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om rykten, mißtankar o. d. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förljudas, yppa sig, höras:</text:span></text:span> suspicio, C.; si quid ab Aequis increpuit terroris, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klappa, slå, brusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot l. på, (skaka, anslå):</text:span> fores digito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå allarm på),</text:span> Pt.; lyram digitis; unda latus navis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brusar emot),</text:span> Ov.; boves stimulo, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ord, röst, ljud i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dundra, klinga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ropa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngn; deraf öfwerhufwud </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bestraffa, förebrå, klandra, beskylla:</text:span></text:span> Phoebus me i-uit lyrā, ne <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ett slag på lyran warnade mig för att -);</text:span> Sabella carmina pectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skaka</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förfära),</text:span> Hor.; simul verbis i-ans transfigit puellam; exercitum, hostes, probris aliquem; timeri hostes, i-ns, L.; perfidiam, arrogantiam, fugam alicujus, C.; dictis aliquem, Sa.; aliquem avaritiæ, Su.; scrobem ut humilem, T. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T2">causativt</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Låta skalla, ljuda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> sonitum, Vg.; manus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klappa i -),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dundra = hårdt, med klander yttra:</text:span> hæc Aricinus in regem i-ns abiit; hæc ille pavidis i-at, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrĕpĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Susa:</text:span></text:span> arbor, Sil.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ropande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppmana; bestraffa, håna:</text:span></text:span> Bitiæ dedit i-ns (poculum Dido), Vg.; verbis quoque i-ns adjecit, L.; aliquem vocibus, Cs.; æstatem seram <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klaga öfwer),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillwita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt:</text:span> alicui ignaviam, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percrĕpo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomljuda, skalla af:</text:span></text:span> vocibus lucus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcrĕpo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skalla, återskalla:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crepusculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Creper.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rēs, ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ressa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cretenser, -sisk.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rēsius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rēta, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rētē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ön Creta.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crētæus,<text:line-break/>Crētānus,<text:line-break/>Crētensis,<text:line-break/>Crētĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Crētis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cresco,</text:span> crēvi, crētum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af samma rot som</text:span> Creo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om naturlig, organisk wäxt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">komma upp; födas;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>: Crētus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">född, boren, härstammande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, från -:</text:span> rosa, Vg.; quos utriusque figuræ esse video - corpore de patrio et materno sanguine c-unt, Lucr.; quo sanguine c-tus?; Trojano a sanguine c-tus, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> unā c-runt, Pt.; fruges, Lucr.; lacte ferino, Ov.; corpus equorum, Vg.; in altitudinem, longitudinem, Pn.; arbor, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerhufwud = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tilltaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i storhet, antal, kraft, betydenhet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förstoras, förkofras, ökas, stiga, stegras:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> Nilus, Lucr.; opes, odium; amici c-erunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ökats);</text:span> morbus, C.; res (Romana) ab exiguis profecta initiis adeo c-vit, ut jam magnitudine laboret sua; c-ente in dies grege juvenum; c-bat interim urbs, alia atque alia munitionibus appetendo loca; mihi materies scribendi c-it; in tantas opes c-it, L.; amicitia, æs alienum, fama; aliquis dignitate, gratiā, N.; flumen ex nivibus; annona c-vit, Cs.; regnum per scelus; mala; imperii cupido; respublica, civitas opibus; concordiā res parvæ c-unt, Sa.; c-it indulgens sibi dirus hydrops; usque ego postera c-am laude recens; cetaria c-ent; - c-re res (familiaris) posset, minui damnosa libido, Hor.; de tenui origine in immensum, Ov.; villa, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om personer,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">absol.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stiga till makt och anseende, komma sig upp:</text:span></text:span> ex, de aliquo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på ngns axlar, bekostnad);</text:span> ex invidia alicujus, C.; occasio in curia c-ndi, L.; per fratrem c-rat Dumnorix, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accresco</text:span>, crēvi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa, ökas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">komma till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt förut warande; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillfalla, blifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn till del:</text:span> dictis accrevit fides, L.; negotia nova veteribus, Pn.; quantum tibi litibus a-evit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad du wunnit på -),</text:span> Sa.; iambus, pes citus, trimetris a-re jussit nomen iambeis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gjort att de fått namn af</text:span> trimetri), quum senos redderet ictus, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa upp; ökas:</text:span></text:span> puer, Qu.; amicitia cum ætate, Ter.; flumen subito, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accrētio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltagande:</text:span></text:span> a. et deminutio luminis (lunæ), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concresco</text:span>, crēvi, crētum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanwäxa:</text:span></text:span> terra ex parvis terris; semina (in) membris, Lucr.; ora rigido rostro, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om luftiga och flytande ämnen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skocka sig, stelna, löpna:</text:span></text:span> nubes in alto, Lucr.; aqua nive pruināque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i = till snö),</text:span> C.; imbres ventis gelidis, Vg.; sanguis frigore, Ov.; lac, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanwuxen:</text:span></text:span> corpus ex elementis; lumen lunæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liksom sammanwuxet, -flutet till rund form),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtätad, stelnad:</text:span></text:span> aër, C.; dolor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stelnad = som ej mera kan gråta),</text:span> Ov.; lac c-ius; in lapidem c., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrētio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammansättning, sammansatthet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till enkelhet):</text:span> individuorum; animus segregatus est ab omni c-e mortali, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concrētus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stelnande:</text:span></text:span> suci myrrhæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcresco</text:span>, crēvi, crētum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förminskas, aftaga, tryta:</text:span></text:span> ostrea, C.; d-ntia ripas flumina prætereunt, Hor.; dies, Pn.; febris, Cels.; oratio, <text:soft-page-break/>Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcrescentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcrēmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aftagande:</text:span></text:span> Gell., Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excresco</text:span>, crēvi, crētum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa ut, upp:</text:span></text:span> caro in latere alicujus, Su.; boves, Col.; arbores in altitudinem, Pn.; in omni domo (Germani) nudi ac sordidi in hæc corpora, quæ miramur, e-unt, T.; lites mirum in modum, Su.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf. dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excrētus</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppwuxen:</text:span> hoedus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incresco</text:span>, crēvi, crētum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa i, på, in i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (upp till):</text:span> squamæ cuti, Ov.; seges telorum jaculis i-it acutis; ira animis, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa, tilltaga, stegras:</text:span></text:span> arbor, Col.; audacia, certamen, L.; febris noctu, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarur ngt uppstår, hwarmed det ökas:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillwäxt, -ökning:</text:span></text:span> res aucta ingenti i-o, L.; i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rekryter)</text:span> renovari exercitum, Ct.; legata cum i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(renta)</text:span> restituere, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarur en slägt framgår l. hwarmed den ökas: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frö; afkomma:</text:span></text:span> dentes draconum populi i-a futuri, Ov.; cara deûm suboles magni Jovis i., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i abstract men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppwäxt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bildningswäg); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillwäxt, -ökning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sätt för, stadier i -):</text:span> hæc ducum i-a et rudimenta (custodia regis), Ct.; res est in i-o; rei afferre i-a; vitium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winträdens)</text:span> ortus, satus, i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stadierna af deras wäxt),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcresco</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa fram, uppkomma:</text:span></text:span> ex quattuor rebus omnia, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa, tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> vis morbi, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcresco</text:span>, crēvi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa ut, upp igen:</text:span></text:span> accisis stirpibus aliquid, L.; recisa ossa non r-unt, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succresco</text:span>, crēvi, crētum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa upp i ngns ställe, att efterträda, ärfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. ngt:</text:span> dum boni mores aegrotant, mali mores s-vere aegerrime, Pt.; herbas s-re patiamur, Col.; is (orator) vestræ ætati s-it, C.; gloriæ seniorum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpercresco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxa öfwer, ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cresius,<text:line-break/>Cressa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cres.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crēta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kalk, kritjord; krita:</text:span></text:span> tenaci c-ā solidanda est area <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(logen);</text:span> c. exesa nigris chelydris; laudatio c-ā consignata <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i stället för det wanl.</text:span> cerā), C.; figularis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(krukmakare-),</text:span> Pn.; humida c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom smink);</text:span> c-ā an carbone <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med hwitt l. swart tecken)</text:span> notandi?, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crētāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krithwit:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crētāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: taberna, ubi venit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(säljes)</text:span> creta, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crētātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kritfärgad:</text:span></text:span> fasciæ, C.; candidati, Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crētōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik på kalk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kritjord:</text:span></text:span> locus, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crētŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: signum in c-ā epistulæ animadvertere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrēto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bestryka med krita:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Creta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ön),</text:span> <text:line-break/>Cretæus, <text:line-break/>Cretanus, <text:line-break/>Cretensis, <text:line-break/>Creticus, <text:line-break/>Cretis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cres.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cretio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cerno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĕūsa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cribr . . .,<text:line-break/>Crimen,<text:line-break/>Crimin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cerno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rīmissus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod på Sicilien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crīnis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> (obsol. <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (enl.</text:span> Paul. Diac. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> cerno):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskors hufwud-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">collect.; wanligare i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>): c. madidi, flavi, longi, passi, effusi, compositi; c-em vertici auferre, Vg.; compti, adulteri, Hor.; solvere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utslå)</text:span> c-es, L.; lacerati, Ct.; vagi per colla c-es; desecare c-es, Ov.; promittere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta wäxa),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hårlika bildningar hos djur och wäxter:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cometens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swans:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crīnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till håret, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår-:</text:span></text:span> aurum, vitta, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårlik:</text:span></text:span> corpus polypi, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crīnāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårprydnad:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crīnĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långhårig:</text:span></text:span> Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crīnior</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få hår), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löfwas:</text:span></text:span> arbor, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crīnītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långhårig, med långt hår:</text:span></text:span> Iopas, Vg.; puella, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med hjelmbuske, swans:</text:span></text:span> galea, Vg.; stella, C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löfrik:</text:span></text:span> arbuscula, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĭnum</text:span> (-on), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lilja:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĭsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wändpunkt, omskifte i sjukdom; kris:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crispus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krusig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> cincinni, Pt.; folium c-issimum, Col.; juba, brassica, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krushårig:</text:span></text:span> homo, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wågformig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till teckning, form, rörelse):</text:span> marmor, Pn.; latus, Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsirad:</text:span></text:span> oratio, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crispĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krusa:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crispĭsulcans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krusigt fårande:</text:span></text:span> fulmen, poēt. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crispo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krusa:</text:span></text:span> capillum, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swänga:</text:span></text:span> hastilia manu, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crispans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som krusas, rynkas, böljar:</text:span> nasus, Ps.; buxus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crispŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Småkrusig, sirligt krusad:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rispus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen</text:span> (C. Sallustius Cr.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kam:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på en fågels hufwud:</text:span> upupæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett blad (centralådern):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på en hjelm; oeg. om </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fjäderbusken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> derpå:</text:span> c-æ comantes galeæ; equina, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cristātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kamprydd:</text:span></text:span> ales, Ov.; galeæ, L.; angues, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cristŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĭtĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crĭtĭcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konstdomare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (æsthetiker):</text:span> C., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĭto, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĭtŏbūlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rĭtŏlāus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crocatus,<text:line-break/>Croceus,<text:line-break/>Crocinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crocus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crōcio,</text:span> 4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crōcĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kraxa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> skrika som en korp:</text:span> Pt.; Auct. Philom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crŏcŏdīlus</text:span> (Corcodilus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokodil:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcŏdīlēa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokodilträck:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcŏdīlīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokodil</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">slut,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sophism:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crocota,<text:line-break/>Crocotula,<text:line-break/>Crocum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crocus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crŏcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saffran, saffransfärg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">essence:</text:span></text:span> ruber, Ov.; spirans, Juv.; c-um floresque perambulat fabula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(går öfwer scenen, som doftar af saffransessence och blommor),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">färgad i saffran, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saffransgul:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏceus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af saffran, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saffran-:</text:span></text:span> odores, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcĭnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (oleum), Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saffranslik, -färgad, gullgul:</text:span></text:span> c-eus acanthus, amictus; cubile Auroræ c-eum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i gull rodnande),</text:span> Vg.; tunica c-ĭna, Catl. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcōta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏcōtŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(saffransgul) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Praktklädning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för damer:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>roesus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lydiskt namn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rŏmy̆on, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crŏtălum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skallra, hwaraf danserskor betjente sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Castagnette:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏtălia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(små skallror), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Örhängen:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŏtălistria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skallrerska) = danserska, som skallrar med castagnetter:</text:span> Ppt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om storken för hans skallrande läte,</text:span> Publ. Syr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rŏto, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekisk coloni i södra Italien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crŏtōniātes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i C.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crŏtōniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rŏtōpĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cruci . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crux.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crūdēlis</text:span> (: crudus = fidelis : fidus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grym; hård:</text:span></text:span> c. Hannibal (fuit); in liberos et sanguinem suum; mulier; consilia; bellum, C.; rex; facinus, Cs.; animus; parricida, Sa.; c. tu quoque, mater (Aeneas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till</text:span> Venus); amor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tärande);</text:span> odium, funus, Vg.; hostis, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūdēlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grymhet, blodtörst, hårdhet:</text:span></text:span> c. est atrocitas in exigendis poenis, Sen.; carnificina et c.; eorum c. nostro sanguine non potest expleri; hominum naturæ inimica est c.; importuna in me c.; adhibere, exercere, exprimere, uti in aliquem, C.; c. erga aliquem, N.; c. in supplicio; Ariovisti, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūdēlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grymt, på grymt sätt:</text:span></text:span> interficere, exstinguere, perire, C.; imperare, Cs., N.; se gerere, N.; torquere, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crudesco,<text:line-break/>Cruditas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crudus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crūdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> cruidus: cruor = calidus: calor?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rå, färsk, frisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = osmält, okokt, omogen, ej läkt:</text:span> caro, Su.; exta, L.; lateres <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obrända),</text:span> Col.; corium, Varr.; poma, C.; vulnus, Ov., Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej smält l. kan smälta maten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magsjuk:</text:span></text:span> alvus, Cato; Roscius hodie c-ior fuit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frisk, kry:</text:span></text:span> c-a deo viridisque senecta, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ny, omogen, oförsökt, obrukad; (ej bearbetad), grof:</text:span></text:span> servitium, T.; puella viro c-a, Mt.; terra, Luc.; solum, Col.; lectio c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(osmält),</text:span> Qu.; materna tibi farinast ex c-issimo Ariciæ pistrino, Su.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grym, hård:</text:span></text:span> vir, Pt.; bella, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūdesco</text:span>, (dui), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa swårare, häftigare:</text:span></text:span> morbus, pugna, Vg.; seditio, T.; Gorgo asperso sanguine, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförmåga att smälta maten, dålig matsmältning, indigestion:</text:span></text:span> c. ei causa morbi fuit; carere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara fri från)</text:span> c-e et insomniis, C.; c-em contrahere, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om wäxter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stockning af wätskor:</text:span></text:span> arbores laborant c-e, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percrūdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ganska rå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (omogen, färsk l. frisk):</text:span> pruna, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcrūdesco</text:span>, dui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. blifwa frisk på nytt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter börja blöda, återupprifwas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om sår); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förnyas:</text:span></text:span> vulnera, C.; seditio, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cruentus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (: crudus, cruor = fluentum : fluidus, fluor):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blödande, blodig, blodbestänkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och hyperbolisk betydelse):</text:span> cadaver, gutta, mucro; sanguine c-us; victoria, bellum, C.; palma, arma, præda, Ov.; frustra c-o Marte carebimus, Hor.; vir c-ior, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blodröd:</text:span></text:span> myrta, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blodtörstig, grym:</text:span></text:span> Achilles, Ov.; ira, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cruento</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bloda, fläcka, besudla med blod, blod</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(röd)-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">färga:</text:span></text:span> gladium; respublica vulneribus, secures scelere c-antur; hæc te c-at oratio, C.; manus sanguine suorum, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incruentus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incruentātus</text:span> (Ov.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej blodig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blodad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som ej kostar blod):</text:span> miles; integri i-ique <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan blodförlust),</text:span> T.; proelium, victoria, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcruentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något blodig, blodblandad,</text:span> Cels.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crŭmēna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭmīna</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭmilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Penningepung</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som bars kring halsen):</text:span> Pt.; mundus victus non deficiente c-ā, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cruor,</text:span> ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blod:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: rinnande, utrunnet; meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blodsutgjutelse:</text:span></text:span> recens, C.; sparsus c-bus, Hor.; tepidus, crassus, Vg.; foedus, fusus; c-em sitire, Sen.; ad cædem et c-em abstrahi, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.: blod i kroppen:</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> scit, c. imperii qui sit, quæ viscera rerum, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cruppellārii,</text:span> ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fäktare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bland Gallerne:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Crur . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Crus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crūs,</text:span> ūris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sken-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ben</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från knäet till fotsålan); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en wäxt:</text:span> c-a suffringere alicui, C.; succidere, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stam:</text:span></text:span> arboris, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är för benet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ben</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> fascia, Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūrĭcrĕpĭda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (crĕpo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwars ben smälla af piskrapp:</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crūrĭfrăgius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwars ben sönderslås:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cruscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pt., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crusma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Musikstycke:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crusta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skorpa, skal, rufwa:</text:span></text:span> panis, locustæ, Pn.; fluminis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(isskorpa),</text:span> Vg.; Heliadum c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bernsten),</text:span> Juv.; ulcerum, Cels.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i konsten: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerdrag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beklädnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af metall, stucco, marmor o. d.:</text:span> c-æ parietum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(marmorskifwor),</text:span> Pn.; argenti cælati c-æ et emblemata, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som arbetar konstwerk med upphöjda figurer:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tjockskalig:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: ulcerum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kaka, sockerbröd:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sockerbagare:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crusto</text:span>, 1.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerdraga, bekläda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt (såsom med rappning, stucco, marmor):</text:span> domum marmoribus, Luc.; aliquid gypso, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crustātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: vasa; animalia c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skaldjur),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incrusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerstryka, -draga, bekläda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> Pn.; vas sincerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smutsa),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>rustŭmĕria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Crustŭmĕrium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Crustŭmĕrii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Crustŭmium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span><text:line-break/>Crustŭmĕrīnus,<text:line-break/>Crustŭmīnus,<text:line-break/>Crustŭmius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crux,</text:span> crŭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kors,</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stock, påle</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarpå den lifdömde spetsades l. hängdes (jfr</text:span> patibulum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och Rich; Marquardt,</text:span> V. 1. 191)], <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">galge;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plåga, olycka:</text:span></text:span> c-em mereri, Ter.; in c-em tollere, agere alqm; c-i suffigere, C., Sen. consolatio ad Marc. c. 20; c-e dignus, Hor.; illæ c-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om personer);</text:span> ire in malam c-em, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">korsfäst:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭcio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pina, mißhandla, martera, plåga, qwälja:</text:span></text:span> omni supplicio c-tum necare, L.; fame et vigiliis c-batur Regulus; conscientiā scelerum c-ri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">plågsam:</text:span> exitu perire, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciābĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plåga:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciābĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plågsamt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pina:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭciātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pina, marter, plåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till kropp l. själ, af andra tillfogad l. sjelfförwållad), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">qwal:</text:span></text:span> abi in malum c-um, Pt.; Regulus ad c-um revertit; in c-um dari; maximi totius corporis c-us; interfici per <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under)</text:span> c-us; timoris c-u angi; dolorum c-u confici, C.; corporis, Sa.; necari cum c-u, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crŭcĭsălus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (salio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som får bestiga korset: på skämt bildadt ord af</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discrŭcio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sönderpina, jemmerligt plåga, oroa, ängsla:</text:span></text:span> animi d-or, Pt.; d-tum necare aliquem; d-or, Sextilii fundum a verberone possideri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excrŭcio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utpina, martera, swårt plåga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen:</text:span> tormentis, fame, Cs.; omni supplicio; fumo e-re, C.; e-tum necare alqm, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till sinnet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pina, plåga:</text:span></text:span> miseriæ me, libido et ignavia animum e-ant; sollicitudo alqm, C.; Antipho me e-at animi, Ter.; honore alicujus e-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(täras af afund öfwer),</text:span> Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excrŭciābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: anus e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förtjenar att läggas på pinbänk, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskywärd:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percrŭcio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swårt pina:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crypta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr. (κρύπτειν):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluten gång (corridor),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> begagnad till förwaringsrum (källare, höbod m. m.) eller, för deß swalhets skull, till promenadplats (jfr</text:span> cryptoporticus): in ædibus c-æ, horrea, apothecæ, Vitr.; in c-a pueri ad edendas in scena operas præparabantur, Su. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Villa Diomede <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Pompeji af Overbeck).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Underjordisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i berg sprängd gång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (grotta):</text:span> c. Suburæ (cloaca), Juv.; c. Neapolitana (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tunneln mellan Neapel och Posilippo),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cryptŏportĭcus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (vox hybrida, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> κρύπτειν <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> porticus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sluten portik,</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af wäggar innesluten, endast medelst fönster öppen gång, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">corridor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (begagnad såsom promenad l. i allm. swal wistelseort, då man för solhetta l. köld ej kunde wistas i fria luften l. i öppna portiker):</text:span> Pn. ep. II. 17. §. 16 ff. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den af</text:span> Pn. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beskrifna c. war belägen i en trädgård; jfr</text:span> Crypta 1).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Crystallum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crystallus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(is), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krystall:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Crystallĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krystall-:</text:span></text:span> vasa, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>tēsĭphon, ontis:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad wid Tigris.</text:span> <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cubicul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cubicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cubile,<text:line-break/>Cubit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭbo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> in carcere; cum aliqua, Pt.; in lectica, lecto, C.; summo æquore saxi, Lucr.; ossa, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och sofwa:</text:span> c-um ire, discedere, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga till bords:</text:span></text:span> propter alqm, C.; super alqm, Ct.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga sjuk:</text:span></text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om byggnader, localiteter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slutta:</text:span></text:span> tectum, Lucr.; Ustīca, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sofrum;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kammare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kejsarens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Loge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på theatren o. s. w.:</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i byggnadskonsten: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Foga:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcŭlārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till</text:span> c.: Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcŭlārius</text:span>, i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcŭlāris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kammartjenare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: navis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med hytt),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbīle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggställe, lägerställe, säng:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskors:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">allm.:</text:span> terra erat ei c.; collocare alqm in c-i, C.; viduum, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Äkta bädd:</text:span></text:span> patrium temerare c., Ov.; Aurora surgebat Tithoni c-i, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck:</text:span> Hesperium solis c., Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">djurs </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo, ide, näste:</text:span></text:span> bestiæ delitescunt in c-bus; avium, C.; rimosa, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Foga:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtissim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i liggande ställning:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pläga ligga:</text:span></text:span> pusio cum majore sorore propter nocturnos timores, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som lägger sig (under plöjandet):</text:span> bos, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.,</text:span> Cels.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Armbåge, båge:</text:span></text:span> c-o inniti, Vg.; ossa c-i, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aln:</text:span></text:span> columella non altior tribus c-is, C.; adolevit in tria c-a, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtal</text:span>, ālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Armkudde:</text:span></text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alnshög:</text:span></text:span> L., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liggande:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggande, läger:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga bredwid, wid sidan af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. ngt:</text:span> ei bini custodes semper a-ant, Pt.; juxta, Vg.; monti theatrum, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga wid bordet, till bords:</text:span></text:span> in conviviis, apud alqm, C.; eodem lecto, L.; Furiarum maxima (in epulo) juxta a-at, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig bredwid:</text:span></text:span> alicui, Tib., Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig till bords, gå till bords:</text:span></text:span> in convivio; in epulo; hora nona, C.; apud alqm; lauti a-bant; in summo, medio, infimo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(högste o. s. w. platsen; jfr</text:span> triclinium); super, supra, infra alqm, C., Hor.; in acta cum suis, N.; tu das epulis a-re divom, Vg.; cum aliquo, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sittande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gående) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">till bords:</text:span></text:span> epularis a.; status, incessus, sessio, accubitio (al. -ātio), C.<text:line-break/>2. = triclinium: Lpd.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbĭtōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: vestimenta = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som brukas wid bordet,</text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbĭtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bordssoffa:</text:span></text:span> Lpd.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbĭtālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Täcken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på bordssofforna:</text:span> Treb. Cl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggande till bords:</text:span></text:span> turpis mulieri a., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭbuo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I liggande ställning wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bordet), ordlek med</text:span> assiduo: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭcŭbĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twå alnar lång:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga, lägga sig tillsammans, hos</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (isynnerhet om man och qwinna):</text:span> hic (in Palatio) Evandri c-uere boves, Ppt.; cum uxore c-uit, C.; alicui, Ov., Ppt.; c-unt Græce, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: man och qwinna, som dela hwarandras säng:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om äkta folk:</text:span> c-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om brudgum),</text:span> Catl. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ogifta, som lefwa tillsammans, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Älskare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">frilla:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; pellicum c-i, Ct.; in c-æ locum duci, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbīnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samboende (utan laggildt äktenskap); frillostånd:</text:span></text:span> emere aliquam sibi in c-um, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samlag:</text:span></text:span> Hyg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liggande tillsammans wid bordet:</text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samlag, älskog:</text:span></text:span> ferarum ritu promiscue in c-us ruere, L.; deorum cum genere humano, C.; vago prohibere c-u, Hor.; vetitos petere, turpes sequi c-us, Ov., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: nox c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den tid af dygnet, då man går till sängs),</text:span> C., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭbium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samlag:</text:span></text:span> Enn.<text:line-break/>b. = nox c-ia, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga utom:</text:span></text:span> de lecto, Fab. Pict. ap. Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbitum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig ned:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Till bords:</text:span></text:span> in triclinio, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa sängliggande:</text:span></text:span> familia decubuit, Sen. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla, stupa:</text:span></text:span> gladiatores curant, ut honeste d-ant, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig hwar på sin plats:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till bords:</text:span> omnes præter illam, C.; in convivio, T.; super strato ostro, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gå till sängs:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gående till bords:</text:span> Val. Max.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŭbo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga ute:</text:span></text:span> in agro, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga, stå på wakt, hålla wakt, wara på wakt, waka öfwer:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> pro castris, Cs.; ad portam, in muris, L.; ante domum, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> consilio et labore e-abo et vigilabo pro vobis; sapiens animo sic e-at, ut nihil ei improvisum accidere possit, C.; Cupido in genis puellæ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŭbātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wakt, wakthållning:</text:span></text:span> Cs., Val. Max.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŭbiæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggande utom hus:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wakt, skiltwakt:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">waktposter, -trupper (garde):</text:span></text:span> L. Visidii e-as mei capitis cognovi in consulatu; e. et vigiliæ, quæ custodient corpus Pompeji, C.; agere, Ov.; habere, Pn.; disponere e-as, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excŭbĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Waktare, waktpost:</text:span></text:span> e. vigilans canis, Col.; e-bus et præsidiis tenebantur omnia, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbo</text:span>, ui, ĭtum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span> āvi, ātum), 1.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga, hwila på,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer:</text:span> cortici i-ns Tiberim tranavit, L.; ponto (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) nox, Vg.; stramentis, Hor.; super aliquid, Sen. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">specielt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett tempel för att få uppenbarelse:</text:span> in fano, C.; pellibus stratis, Vg.; Jovi, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om fåglar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rufwa:</text:span></text:span> ova, Varr.; ovis, Col.; ova i-ita, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppehålla sig;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bebo:</text:span></text:span> Erymantho aper, Ov.; lucos et specus, Ap.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = ängsligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bewaka; lura på:</text:span></text:span> auro defosso; divitiis, Vg.; <text:soft-page-break/>pecuniæ spe et animo, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbātio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbātus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggande, rufwande på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> dextri lateris i-itus; rara i-atio ovis noxia, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som ligger, rufwar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på:</text:span> thesauri, Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŭbĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ständigt ligga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> gallinæ, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpĕrincŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> substratus vivus s-nti mortuo, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig, falla, störta, kasta sig på,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer:</text:span> in gladium; ferro, mucroni, gladio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(falla på sitt swärd),</text:span> Phdr., L., Pt.; nova febrium terris i-uit cohors, Hor.; toro; remis; venti i-uere mari; tempestas silvis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om hwila) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stödja sig på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">emot, hwila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">luta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer:</text:span> Damon olivæ; humero alicujus; aratro; laurus i-ens aræ; silex ad lævum amnem, Vg.; baculo, Ov.; tecta columnis, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla, kasta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med sin tyngd) på, öfwer ngn:</text:span> oratio jam inclinato oratori i-it; orator, quocumque i-uit, animos impellit; temporum inclinatio in me, C.; inclinatio voluntatum in aliquem, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personliga subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ansätta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">falla, hwila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på -, öfwer -:</text:span> in hostem, L.; alicui acriter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i en disput);</text:span> ira militum in aliquem, invidia alicui, T. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom sin tyngd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedtrycka, påskynda fallet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> id malum inclinatis rebus maxime i-uit, L.; urgenti i-re fato, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, kasta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">winnlägga, beflita sig om -, sträfwa för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">egna sig åt:</text:span></text:span> in id studium i-ite, ut patriæ utilitati esse possitis; in eam curam et cogitationem; toto pectore in causam; ad salutem reipublicæ; ad ulciscendas injurias; omni curā in rempublicam, C.; et animis et opibus in bellum, Cs.; cogitationi, T.; stilo, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpĕrincumbo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, kasta sig ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga fallen, död:</text:span></text:span> morte, L.; tumulo; crudelibus umbris, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla, duka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> under för ngn l. ngt:</text:span> Rullo, C.; ferro, neci, Ov.; in gladium, Vell.; alicui, Sil.<text:line-break/>2. mortem (C.), morte (L.), morti (Vg.) o-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dö.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>3. = occidere, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gå ned:</text:span> cometes, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga utsträckt, sträcka sig:</text:span></text:span> umbra, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, kasta sig, falla, störta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ned, framåt, framstupa:</text:span> Galli ad pedes Cæsaris; vulneribus confectum p-re; frumenta imbribus, Cs.; Hercules fessus viā p-uit; ad genua alicujus; agger in fossam p-uit, L.; olli certamine summo p-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om roende);</text:span> Penelei dextrā; p-it humi bos; culmus gravidis aristis, Vg.; genibus p.; domus in caput domini, Ov.; in genua, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luta, slutta:</text:span></text:span> tigna secundum naturam fluminis; planities, Cs.; Hæmus in Pontum, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förfalla, komma på förfall:</text:span></text:span> in voluptates, Sen.; res meæ p-uere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga, hwila tillbakalutad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (makligt):</text:span> molliter et delicate in hortis, C.; sub tegmine fagi; sus in herba, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig tillbaka, tillbakalutad:</text:span></text:span> surrexit, deinde r-uit; in herba; in cubiculo, C.; mulier sopita, Lucr.; in sinu alicujus, Pn. ep.; Archiacis lectis convivam r-re, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjunka, falla ned:</text:span></text:span> minax unda ponto, Hor.; nebulæ, Vg.; onus in proclinatas partes, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedfallande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēcŭbo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga för sig sjelf, ensam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om makar):</text:span> ab aliqua, Catl.; causæ s-andi, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bo ensam, i tillbakadragenhet:</text:span></text:span> miles annosus depositis armis, Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēcŭbĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liggande för sig sjelf:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succŭbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ligga under:</text:span></text:span> alicui rei, aliquid, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succŭba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som intager ngns plats, (gengångare, repræsentant):</text:span></text:span> meæ formæ; tori, Ap.; florulentus hyacinthi s. (flos hyacinthi puero Hyacintho tanquam substitutus), Prud.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succŭbo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succŭbōneus</text:span>, ei, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: id.: Tit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succumbo</text:span>, cŭbui, cŭbĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla under, för:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ferro, Catl.; oneri, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Duka under för, öfwerwäldigas af; gifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">få wika för:</text:span></text:span> nulli neque homini nec perturbationi nec fortunæ; ingravescenti senectuti; doloribus; orator philosopho, C.; labori, Cs.; Asia Europæ, N.<text:line-break/>c. viro virgo, Varr.; gallina marito, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tärning, kubisk figur:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kub af ett tal:</text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭbĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kubisk:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cucŭbo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta som en nattuggla:</text:span> Auct. Phil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcullus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭcullio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">capuchong (på en kappa):</text:span> Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Strut:</text:span></text:span> piperis, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcūlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gök:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom skymford (lat l. dum):</text:span> Hor., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcŭma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kittel:</text:span></text:span> Petr., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcŭmis,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> -mim, <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> -mi, Pn.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gurka:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcurbĭta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kurbits:</text:span></text:span> Pn.; c-ā glabrior, Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopphorn:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭcurbĭtīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lik kurbits:</text:span> pira, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcūrio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gala som en tupp (kukuliku):</text:span> Auct. Phil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: = Cuculus: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭcutium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags</text:span> cucullus: Treb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūdo,</text:span> s. p. et s., 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slå:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttröska:</text:span></text:span> frumenta, Col.; fabam, Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prägla:</text:span></text:span> argentum, Ter.; numos, Pt.; monetam, Treb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accūdo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ytterligare prägla:</text:span></text:span> tres minas, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excūdo</text:span>, cūdi, cūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utslå:</text:span></text:span> scintillam silici, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utkläcka:</text:span></text:span> ova, Varr., Col.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">konstfärdigt arbeta:</text:span></text:span> librum, T.; spirantia æra, Vg.; e-am aliquid - quod lateat in thesauris tuis, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aftwinga, framtwinga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (frambringa):</text:span> - mihi, ut scriberem, Col.; ut usus meditando artes excuderet (al. extunderet), Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excūsor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopparsmed:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūdo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott brukl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smidd, tillhuggen:</text:span></text:span> crater auro incusus, Ps.; lapis molæ i-us, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incus</text:span>, ūdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smedjestäd:</text:span></text:span> imponere ensem i-i, Vg.; i-i reddere aliquid, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> eandem i-em diem noctemque tundere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percūdo</text:span>, cūdi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sönderhacka:</text:span></text:span> ova (alii pertundo), Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūdo</text:span>, cūdi, cūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smida, hwässa:</text:span></text:span> dentem vomeris, Vg.; enses, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppöfwa:</text:span></text:span> linguam, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frambringa; anlägga:</text:span></text:span> ignis ignem; prolem, Lucr.; dolos, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcūdo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omsmida:</text:span> Varr. (inc.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūdo,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjelm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af läder:</text:span> Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cujas, Cujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Culcĭta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kudde, dyna:</text:span></text:span> plumea, C.; tumet lanis, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culcĭtŭla</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culcĭtella</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Lucil., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūleus</text:span> (Coleus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culleus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culleum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säck</text:span></text:span> (ex lino, cannabe, corio): alqm in c-um insuere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(straff för fadermördare),</text:span> C.; utres et c-os comparare, N. <text:line-break/>b. = testiculus, C., Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mått för flytande waror, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fat</text:span></text:span> (20 amphoræ): Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cullēaris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som rymmer en</text:span> culeus: labrum, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭlex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mygga:</text:span></text:span> Hor., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭligna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten bägare:</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭlīna</text:span> (Colina, Pt.), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kök:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> Pt., C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förplägning:</text:span></text:span> c-am præbere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> domum), Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭlīnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till köket:</text:span> Fronto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Culleus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Culeus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Culmen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Columen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Culmus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Culmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sädesstjelk, -strå, halmstrå:</text:span></text:span> geniculatus, C.; fragilis hordei c.; c-o horrebat regia (Romuli), Vg.; c-men inane fabæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Culpa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skuld, förwållande, fel, last</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i uttr.: räkna till l.):</text:span> in c-ā esse; a c-ā abesse, abhorrere, remotum esse; c-ā carere, liberari; c. est penes aliquem; senatori, qui non aderit, aut causa aut c. esto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(antingen giltigt förfall l. skuld, answar);</text:span> ponere aliquem in c-ā; eximere aliquem ex c-ā; maxima c. est ejus, qui -; de reliquo nostra c. fuerit, nisi impetraverimus; contrahere, sustinere rei c-am; teneri erroris c-ā; transferre, conferre, derivare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skjuta, skjuta ifrån sig)</text:span> c-am in aliquem; dare alicui c-æ aliquid; c-am præstare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(taga på sig),</text:span> amovere ab aliquo, C.; vacuus a c-ā; suam c-am auctores in negotia transferunt; conscientia de c-ā; non mea c-ā sæpe ad vos oratum mitto, Sa.; in c-ā versari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa skulden);</text:span> c-am conjicere in aliquem, Cs.; nil conscire sibi, nullā pallescere c-ā, Hor.; ubi consilium abfuit, c. abest, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= felaktig egenskap), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">last, brott:</text:span></text:span> c-æ libidinis, avaritiæ sunt in eo, C.; utcunque defecere mores, dedecorant bene nata c-æ, Hor.; non omnium Albanorum ea, quam arguo, c. est, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">naturligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fel, sjuka, smitta:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culpo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skylla på, kasta skulden på, anklaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> arbores aquas c-ant, Hor.; non tibi - c-tus Paris - has evertit opes, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klandra:</text:span></text:span> versus inertes; c-atur ab his, laudatur ab illis, Hor.; ob aliquid, in aliqua re, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culpābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klanderwärd:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culpātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klander:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Culpĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårdt tadla:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēculpātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utmönstrad:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inculpātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ostrafflig:</text:span></text:span> vita, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Culta,<text:line-break/>Culte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cultellatus,<text:line-break/>Cultellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Culter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Culter,</text:span> tri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knif:</text:span></text:span> tonsorius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rakknif),</text:span> C.; mucro longi c-i, Juv.; venatorius, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plogbill:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultellus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten knif:</text:span></text:span> c-o purgare ungues, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultellātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knifformig, skarp:</text:span></text:span> dorsum piscis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offerslagtare:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cultrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knifformig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cultio,<text:line-break/>Cultor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cultrarius,<text:line-break/>Cultratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Culter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cultrix,<text:line-break/>Cultura,<text:line-break/>Cultus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭlullus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bägare:</text:span></text:span> multis urgere c-is, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säte, bak:</text:span></text:span> Catl., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Cum,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= tillsammans, tillika med, i förening, förbindelse, sällskap med -:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> ire in via c. aliqua, Ter.; c. Crasso exierant duo adolescentes; c. eo erat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gift)</text:span> nostra matertera; c. Græcis Latina conjungere, C.; una c. reliquis Gallis Hæduis libertatem eripere, Cs.; caelo palmas c. voce tetendit; Remo c. fratre Quirinus, Vg.; tene tympana c. cornu; tecum vivere amem, tecum abeam libens, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i önskningar:</text:span> ite c. Diis benevolentibus, Pt.; abi ad sponsum c. immaturo amore, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utmärkande (wänligt l. owänligt) förhållande till ngn:</text:span> contrahere, habere rationem, agere, colloqui, bellum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> pacem habere c. aliquo; bellum gerere, certare, pugnare, facere foedus, hospitium c. aliquo, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om det (inre l. yttre), som ngn har på, med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hos</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, är beklädd med, omgifwen af (i eg. och oeg. bet.):</text:span> esse c. veste purpureā; c. febri domum redire; c. capite humano porcus natus; esse c. imperio, C.; multo majoris alapæ mecum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos mig)</text:span> veneunt, Phdr.; esse c. insignibus imperii et lictoribus, L.; c. telo esse; c. literis dimitti; c. magna gloria esse, Sa.; c. veste madida esse; quercus annoso c. robore, Vg.; noctu ambulare c. facibus; c. integra mente senectam degere, Hor.<text:line-break/>4. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samtidigt med, wid, i:</text:span></text:span> c. primā luce, C.; c. ortu solis, Sa.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utmärkande de omständigheter, hwarunder ngt sker, de wilkor, det sätt, hwarpå, -med, den följd, hwarmed, hwartill subjectet företager en handling:</text:span> facere aliquid c. fide, c. virtute, c. labore, c. causā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med skäl);</text:span> magna c. audiendi exspectatione considitur; c. pace dimittere alqm; sit sane, sed c. eo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med det wilkor),</text:span> quod sine peccato meo fiat; liberalitas c. mercede; hostis interitum c. scelere senatus non approbavit; auspiciis nos c. magna reipublicæ salute præsumus, C.; c. periculo facere aliquid; c. magno metu dicere, Cs.; c. turpitudine vitam agere; c. summo studio assequi, c. cura reficere aliquid, Sa.; magno c. murmure - fremunt, Vg.; c. stridore acuto apicem sustulit, <text:soft-page-break/>Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span> ager efficit, effert c. octavo, decimo - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gifwer 8:de, 10:de kornet:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>6. (rarissime) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uttryckande medlet:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>7. cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansättningar</text:span> (com <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framför</text:span> m, b, p <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och (stundom) vocaler,</text:span> co <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. framför vocaler,</text:span> con <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framför tung- och gomljud,</text:span> col-, cor- <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framför</text:span> l, r): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med, samman, hop, full-, för-:</text:span></text:span> coeo, compono, convello, concutio, conficio, comedo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Cum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Conj.</text:span> = Quum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ūmæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i södra Italien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cūmæus,<text:line-break/>Cūmānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cumatile <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cymatile.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cumba <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cymba.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭmĕra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sädes</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-)Binge, -lår:</text:span></text:span> frumenti, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭmīnum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kummin:</text:span></text:span> exsangue, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭmīnīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af kummin:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cumque</text:span> (cunque) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> cum (quum) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> que = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">när ock, när helst, wid hwarje tillfälle (som):</text:span> mihi c. salve rite vocanti, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. blott i sammansättningar med andra relativa:</text:span> qui-, qualis-, quomodo-c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. fl., se dessa.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭmŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hög; uppstaplad hop; massa:</text:span></text:span> Gallorum cæsorum; legum, L.; lapidum, Ct.; arboreus, aquarum, Ov.; sequitur c-o præruptus aquæ mons, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarmed ett mått fylles l. ytterligare ökas:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i bild = spets, krona af, på ngt):</text:span> c. vocatur, quod supra mensuram in modio adjiciebatur, Fs.; c-um afferre rei; c-um gaudii afferre populo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätta kronan på ngns glädje);</text:span> res ad rem tamquam c. accedit; aliquid accedit in c-um; deruere c-um de laudibus alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillökning:</text:span></text:span> non tam c. bonorum jucundus esse potest, quam molesta decessio; adventu tuo magnus ad lætitiam meam c. accessit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭmŭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i eg. och oeg. men.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopa, samla:</text:span></text:span> pilorum missu c-atur et concidit multitudo, Cs.; opes, Ct.; arma in acervum, sarcinas; clades aliæ super alias c-bantur, L.; honores in aliquem, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råga, göra fullständig:</text:span></text:span> gaudium alicujus c-re; eloquentiam; officia vitæ c-ta erant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fyllda);</text:span> summum bonum c-atur ex -, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öka, råga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt med ngt:</text:span> scelus scelere, maleficia m-iis c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hopa brott på brott);</text:span> bellicam gloriam eloquentiā c-vit, C.; æs alienum usuris, L. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppfylla, öfwerhopa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> cor irā c-atur, poēt. ap. C.; aras donis, L.; c-ant altaria donis; muneribus aliquem, Vg.; gaudio c-ri, C.; aliquem laudibus, præmiis c-re, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭmŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rågad, fullkomlig, fullständig, riklig:</text:span></text:span> c-iore mensurā reddere <text:soft-page-break/>aliquid; perfecta et c-a virtus, C.; gloria spreta c-ior redit, L.; (gratiam) - mihi si dederis, c-am morte remittam, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppfylld, öfwerhopad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> voluptatibus c.; rebus c-a oratio; hoc vitio c-a est eruditissima Græcorum natio, C.; honoribus c., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭmŭlāte</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭmŭlātim</text:span> (Varr.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I rågadt, fullt mått:</text:span></text:span> perfectum c., c-ius augere; alicui c-sime satisfacere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭmŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppstapla, hopa, samla i hög</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">massa:</text:span></text:span> acervos pecuniæ, C.; honorem alicui, Ov.; congeriem arenæ, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öka:</text:span></text:span> curas alicujus, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerhopa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> donis aliquem, Vg.; vites, arbores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med jord, löf för wintern; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kupa),</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭmŭlāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I fullt, rikt mått:</text:span></text:span> polliceri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭmŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kupning:</text:span></text:span> arborum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accŭmŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samlare:</text:span></text:span> opum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūnæ,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wagga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> in c-is vagire, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> hirundo sub trabibus c-as parvaque tecta facit, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūnābŭla</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wagga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> erat in c-is; in c-is consulem fieri, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Näste:</text:span></text:span> avium, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Födelse-, hemort, första boningsort:</text:span></text:span> gentis c-a nostræ (in Creta), Vg.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begynnelsen, utgångspunkten:</text:span></text:span> a primis c-is, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūnābŭla</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linda, waggtyg:</text:span></text:span> cunis et i-is opus est, Pt.; infantium puerorum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Födelseort:</text:span></text:span> nostra, C.; Jovis in Crete, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Späd barndom:</text:span></text:span> locus i-orum alicujus, Su.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begynnelse, utgångspunkt:</text:span></text:span> non repetam ab i-is nostræ puerilis doctrinæ ordinem quendam præceptorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cunctim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunctus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cunct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Cunctor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cuncto</text:span> (Enn., Pt.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: T.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cunctor</text:span> (Contor), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dröja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af senfärdighet, betänksamhet l. obeslutsamhet, ej af lätja l. likgiltighet</text:span> (cesso), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">derför synonymt och ofta sammanstäldt med</text:span> hæsito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> dubito), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förhala tiden, tweka, betänka sig:</text:span></text:span> unus homo nobis c-do restituit rem, Enn.; assequor omnia, si propero: si c., omnia amitto; diutius in vita c-ri inutile putabat; c. et hæsitare; c. et tergiversari; non est c-dum profiteri, C.; alius alium exspectantes c-amini; ne c-etur ipse propius accedere; c-amini etiam nunc et dubitatis, quid faciatis, Sa.; non c-dum existimavit, quin decertaret; c-tibus nostris militibus maxime propter altitudinem maris; si c-etur et agat lenius -, Cs.; dum c-ntur in ripis, oppressi sunt, L.; c. in thalamo; metu, Vg.; ne c-retur Agrippam morte afficere; non c-tum est apud latera, T.; c., an -, utrumne - an, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -tior: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som dröjer l. betänker sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senfärdig, betänksam, obeslutsam:</text:span></text:span> excitare c-em et verecundantem; c-em et diffidentem incitare, C.; socios c-es increpare, Vg.; c-ior cautiorque, Pn.; ad dimicandum c., Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med dröjsmål, twekan:</text:span></text:span> haud c. cotem discidit Nævius, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senfärdig:</text:span></text:span> milites c-i et restitantes castris egressi sunt, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dröjande, dröjsmål, twekande, senfärdighet, betänklighet:</text:span></text:span> his abjectā omni c-e adipiscendi magistratus et gerenda respublica est; studium adsit (amicos juvandi), c. absit; eximere senatui c-em belli; c. et tarditas, C.; aliquot dierum; in rebus gerendis c., Cs.; quæ tristitia, milites, hæc, quæ insolita c. est?, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dröjare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som betänker sig wäl eller för mycket (sölare):</text:span> scis, Servius quam sit c., C.; Minucius Fabium pro c-e segnem, pro cauto timidum compellabat; ex acerrimo bellatore c. factus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Percunctor,<text:line-break/>Percontor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se under</text:span> P.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cunctus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (conjunctus? convinctus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samtlig, hel;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">alla tillsammans, alla:</text:span></text:span> c. populus, terra, civitas, Asia, C.; Gallia, equitatus, materia, Cs.; plebes, Sa.; Græcia, N.; c-us cecidit pelagi fragor, Vg.; c-i cives, C.; c-a oppida, c-æ præfecturæ, Cs.; c-a maria, Sa.; c-i hominum, Ov.; c-a terrarum subacta, Hor.; c-a tibi fatebor, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cunctim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i det hela, såsom ett helt:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cunela <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunila.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭneus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kil, wigge:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom werktyg:</text:span> c-os inserere, C.; c-is findere lignum, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kilformig figur, kilform:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. in abstracto: T., Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kilformig slagordning:</text:span></text:span> c-um facere, Cs.; c-os rumpere; viam rumpere c-o, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Segment, kilformig afdelning af sittplatserna på theatren l. amphitheatren, sådana de bildades, när de concentriskt löpande</text:span> gradus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> sedilia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skuros af trappor, på hwilka man gick upp och ned:</text:span> assignare alicui c-um, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭneŏlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten kil:</text:span></text:span> C., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭneo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hop-, fast-, tillkila; sammanhålla:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inkila:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bildl. om en digression i talet)</text:span> per vim (oratio) c-atur, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bilda i kilform, tillspetsa:</text:span></text:span> Mel. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭneātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kilformig, spetsig:</text:span></text:span> jugum montis; forma scuti ad imum c-ior, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭneātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I kilform, -ställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om en här):</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discŭneo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppkila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (liksom medelst kil hålla öppen):</text:span> conchæ frustra se contrahunt d-tæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcŭneo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Under, nedantill inkila:</text:span></text:span> postes, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭnīcŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gång, fåra, rör</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inuti ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i purpursnäckan)</text:span> latere introrsus tubulato; terræ cavernæ c-ive; Tigridis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(underjordisk strömfåra),</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Schakt, mina</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i grufwor:</text:span> sulphur ex c-is effoditur, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i krigsspråket) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löngraf, mina:</text:span></text:span> c-os agere, C., Cs.; c-is subtrahere aggerem, Cs.; excipere hostium c-os transversis c-is, L.; subruere muros c-is, Ct. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck:</text:span> id occulte c-is oppugnatur, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kanin:</text:span></text:span> Varr.; c-i habent multifores specus in terra, unde nomen animali, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭnīcŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Minör:</text:span></text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭnīcŭlātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I rörform:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭnīcŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik på kaniner:</text:span></text:span> Celtiberia, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭnīla</text:span> (<text:line-break/>Conila),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭnēla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭnīlāgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cunnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: = loci muliebres, Hor., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cunque = Cumque.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūpa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tunna, fastage:</text:span></text:span> lignea, circulis cincta, Cato; vinum de c-a, C.; vinaria, Varr.; tædā et pice referta, Cs.; ratem vacuæ sustentant undique c-æ, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūpa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Handtag:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cuped . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cupes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūpes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cuppes</text:span>, (ĕdis), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läckermun,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gom:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūpēdia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kräsenhet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">gourmandise:</text:span></text:span> vinolentia, c., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läckerbitar:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūpēdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läckerbit:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūpēdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begär, trånad:</text:span></text:span> ardescit dira c-e pectus, Lucr. <text:line-break/>2. forum c-is = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mattorg:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūpēdĭnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sockerbagare:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cupi . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cupio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭpio,</text:span> īvi, ītum, 3. (4., Lucr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åstunda, åtrå; hafwa begär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ifra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gerna wilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">se:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nuptias, Ter.; aliquem conventum; c. ut -, ne -, Pt.; appetitus c-ndo aut fugiendo exsultantes; ardenter, mirabiliter, mire c. aliquid; c-rem utrumque, si posset; c. audire, discere, videre; hanc partem tibi cupio esse notissimam; patriam exstinctam c.; c. et optare, ut sæpissime peccet amicus, C.; summe aliquid c.; in conspectu imperatoris operam navare c., Cs.; agros, novas res, aliena, alta; proficisci, Sa.; hos destinari consules - specie recusantis flagrantissime c-erat, T.; c-at metuatne, quid ad rem?, Hor.; c., ut -, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara förälskad i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> alicujus, Pt.; aliquam, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui, alicujus causa c.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wilja ngn wäl, ngns wäl, önska framgång:</text:span></text:span> alicui maxime; alicujus causa omnia, C.; favere et c. Helvetiis, Cs. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hafwa egennyttiga önskningar:</text:span></text:span> judices aut sperant aut metuunt aut c-unt, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpiens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åtrående, lifligt önskande; förälskad; ifrig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn:</text:span> c-i animo, Sa.; liberorum, T.; tui, Pt.; Marius c-sima plebe consul factus, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpienter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ifrigt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpīdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i betydelse af person, samt hos</text:span> Hor., Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen i abstract betydelse):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lust, lystnad, begär, åstundan, åtrå:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ordet förekommer i denna abstracta betydelse ej hos</text:span> C., Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligen hos</text:span> Sa., L., T. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och poeterne):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt (till, efter ngt):</text:span> honoris, victoriæ; oppidi potiundi, Sa.; Romulum ac Remum c. cepit urbis condendæ; certamen regni ac c. versabat patrum animos, L.; amor patriæ laudumque arrecta c., Vg.; furiosa opum; prædæ; virginis c-e flagrat, Ov.; tolle c-em immitis uvæ, Hor.; Cæsarem Germanicum c. invadit solvendi suprema militibus ducique; c. rei incedit, involat aliquem, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lusta, begär, lidelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. af otillbörlig l. lumpen art, såsom snöd lusta, egennytta, girighet o. d.):</text:span> captus pravis c-bus; c-e cæcus animus; neque c. Jugurthæ minuebatur, quippe qui totum ejus regnum animo jam invaserat, Sa.; c-bus statuit natura modum; fortis responsare c-bus; fervet avaritiā miseroque c-e pectus; - ne te semper inops agitet vexetque c.; pravus, sordidus, Hor.; incusare aliquem c-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(girighet, besticklighet),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificeradt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kärleksgud:</text:span></text:span> C.; mater sæva C-um, Hor.; pro Ascanio mutatus C., Vg.; militat omnis amans, habet et sua castra C., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpīdĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cupidos:</text:span> tela, sagittæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm.) som har lust för, fikar efter, har håg, ifwer, intresse för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hågad, lysten, begärlig, fikande, ifrig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (intresserad), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mån:</text:span></text:span> ad rem militarem aptus et c. bellorum gerendorum; spectandi valde c.; pecuniæ; vitæ; contentionis c-or, quam veritatis; c. sum te audiendi; non tam commutandarum rerum, quam evertendarum; c. reipublicæ satisfaciendi, C.; rerum novarum c., Cs., Sa.; bellandi; imperii, Cs.; incerta patrandi, Sa.; hujus conjugii; literarum Græcarum, N.; honorum c., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicujus hominis</text:span> c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bewågen, tillgifwen:</text:span></text:span> adolescens nostri c-issimus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ifrig, passionerad, lättfängd, het:</text:span></text:span> in perspicienda cognoscendāque rerum natura, C.; juvenis sublimis c-usque et amata relinquere pernix; stultus c-usque, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kär, älskogssjuk, älskande:</text:span></text:span> amor nunquam postulat nisi c-um hominem in plagas conjicere, Pt.; Venus primum est c-o commissa <text:soft-page-break/>marito, Ov. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Girig, egennyttig, sjelfwisk:</text:span></text:span> multitudo c-orum hominum, C.; divitiæ te minus c-um facere (non) possunt, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Partisk:</text:span></text:span> judex, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med ifwer, med begärlighet:</text:span></text:span> c. arripere; c-ius instare, C.; c-ius insequi; c-sime petere, Cs.; c-sime facere alqd, Sa.; c-sime elaborare, ut -, N.; quod c. petiit, mature plena reliquit, Hor.; legere aliquid, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Egennyttigt, sniket:</text:span></text:span> agere; alienos agros c-e appetere, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med partisinne,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ifwer; med weld; partiskt:</text:span></text:span> nos nihil agimus c. eoque major est auctoritas; c. et temere factum est a senatu, C.; c. condemnare aliquem, Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpĭdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begär, begärelse, åtrå, åstundan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ifwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn:</text:span> c. honorum, imperii, pecuniæ, principatus, gloriæ, veri videndi, dominandi, vincendi; capere, habere c-em rei; c-e rei flagrare, incendi, inflammari, ardere; trahi et duci rei c-e; erigere, incitare, explere alicujus c-em, C.; regni, prædæ, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begär, lusta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (pl. lustar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lidelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom en själsyttring (del af själen) i motsats till</text:span> ratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ira, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller såsom en mångfald):</text:span> non consentaneum est, qui metu non frangatur, eum frangi c-e; omni c-e vacare; c-es tenere, coërcere, frangere; c-bus imperare; necessaria, naturalis, inanis, C.; ardens in c-bus Catilinæ animus, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ifwer, häftighet, enwishet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rätthafweri):</text:span> nimis confidere propter c-em; emptoris; patroni, C.; militum ardor et c., Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjelfwiskhet, egennytta, girighet:</text:span></text:span> sua c-e, non communi utilitate duci; nulla est in iis avaritiæ, cupiditatis suspicio; sine c-e vivere, C.; etiamtum vita hominum sine c-e agitabatur: sua cuique satis placebant, Sa.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Partiskhet, weld:</text:span></text:span> judicare sine c-e; c-i alicujus temperare, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpītor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som åtrår, wurmar för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> Nero c. incredibilium, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭpiens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begärlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter -:</text:span> Enn., Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concŭpisco</text:span>, pīvi, pītum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Få lust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">intagas af begär, åtrå, längtan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter ngt (constr. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">objects-acc.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">infin.</text:span>): ad injuriam faciendam aggrediuntur, ut adipiscantur ea, quæ c-verunt; difficile est, quum præstare omnibus c-ieris, servare æquitatem; Decii mors tam gloriosa fuit, ut eam c-ret filius; inanes cupiditates nihil desiderabile c-unt, C.; domum aut villam, Sa.; tribunos plebis c-istis: concessimus, L.; non intemperanter c., quod a plurimis videas, continentis est, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discŭpio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ängsligt åtrå:</text:span></text:span> aliquem videre, Pt., C. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percŭpio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Högligen åstunda:</text:span></text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percŭpĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Synnerligen tillgifwen:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcŭpĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Serdeles begärlig:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cupo = Caupo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Cuppes = Cupes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭpressus,</text:span> i, (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> -u, Varr.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc. pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">-ūs</text:span>, Hor.?), <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆părissus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cypreß:</text:span></text:span> c-i mæstæ, ferales; coniferæ cyparissi, Vg.; nec præter invisas cupressus ulla brevem dominum sequetur; funebres c., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpressētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cypreßskog:</text:span></text:span> Catl. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpressĕus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpressĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cypreß</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> Col., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭpressĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cypreß-bewuxen:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭprum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. af</text:span> Cypros q. v.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koppar:</text:span></text:span> Sp.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭprĕus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koppar-:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quor, Qui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (arch. coera): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorg:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom handling: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorg, wård</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bestyr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ngt och absol.):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> cum Scipione mihi conjuncta c. de publica re et privata fuit; suscipere, habere rei c-am; c-am operamque ponere in re; c-am conferre, adhibere ad rem; difficilis est c. rerum alienarum; quum sumus necessariis negotiis c-isque vacui, quum laxati c-is sumus, spectare aliquid et visere avemus, C.; defungi c-is, L.; his c-am redde brevem, Hor.; iis c. erat struere; Junoni sunt vincla jugalia c-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hon har wård om),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">läkares </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wård, kur:</text:span></text:span> Vell., C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwaltning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bestyr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med offentliga wärf:</text:span> c. rerum publicarum, Sa.; ea c. demandata est ædilibus, T.; c. ærarii; duplicem c-am administravit, annonæ et repurgandorum ergastulorum, Su.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = skriftligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Arbete:</text:span></text:span> inedita, Ov.; - quorum in manus c. nostra (ɔ: annales) venerit -; si ad plures c-as vitam produxero, Trajani tempora senectuti seposui, T.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skötare, wårdare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af -:</text:span> (Eumæus) immundæ c. fidelis haræ, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom sinnets rigtning l. beskaffenhet, egenskap, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">omtanke, angelägenhet, sorgfällighet, månhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om -:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> habere rei c-am; acris c. et diligentia, C.; majore c-ā; rem c-æ habere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= wårda sig om);</text:span> si hominibus bonarum rerum tanta c. esset -, non regerentur magis, quam regerent casus; utinam apud vos aut apud deos - rerum humanarum c. oriatur, Sa.; magna cum c-ā; c-am remittere, Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span> res est curæ alicui = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ngn har omsorg om, sörjer för, är angelägen, mån om, ser gerna, älskar:</text:span></text:span> mihi non minori c-æ est, qualis post meam mortem respublica futura sit, quam qualis hodie sit; salus mea ei c-æ fuit, C.; pollicitus est, sibi eam rem c-æ futuram, Cs.; non est diis c-æ securitas nostra, T. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nyfikenhet:</text:span></text:span> Hannibal c-ā ingenii humani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af mensklig n.)</text:span> oculis temperare non potuit, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = föremål för ngns omsorg:</text:span> Ascanius mea (Veneris) maxima c., Vg.; sancti vates et divom c. vocamur, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bekymmer, oro:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> injicere alicui c-am, Ter.; si c-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> securitatem) fugimus, virtus fugienda est, quæ necesse est cum aliqua c-ā res contrarias <text:soft-page-break/>aspernetur et oderit; acerba recordatio veterem animi c-am molestiamque renovavit; levare c-am, aliquem c-ā; confici c-is; c. et angor; c. et sollicitudo et metus, C.; hæc te c. remordet; c-æ ultrices <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samwetsqwal),</text:span> Vg.; c-am eximere alicui; post equitem sedet atra c., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föremål för bekymmer:</text:span> mihi tu (navis) desiderium c-que non levis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrio</text:span>, (ōnis), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: agnus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">aftärdt, ordlek hos</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfällig, uppmärksam:</text:span></text:span> ad investigandum; c-is oculis perspici poterat, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wetgirig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (intresserad):</text:span> Chrysippus est in omni historia c.; homo et prudens et quod juvet c., C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som bryr sig med (will weta eller lägger sig i) det, som ej angår honom) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nyfiken, förweten, beställsam:</text:span></text:span> peregrinum minime decet esse in aliena republica c-um; isti sunt c-i, quos offendit noster minime injucundus labor, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alltför noggrann, nogräknad, granntyckt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (pedantisk):</text:span> c. est, qui curā præter modum utitur, Varr.; c. et molestus; c-is difficile satis fit, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ius:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfälligt, uppmärksamt, wetgirigt:</text:span></text:span> ista conquiram c-ius; pueri, quid domi fiat, c. animadvertunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pedantiskt, noggrannt:</text:span></text:span> c. loqui potius, quam Latine, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriōsĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nyfikenhet:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fuskande i mångahanda; mångslöjd:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriōsŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Småförweten:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda, sköta, draga försorg, hafwa omsorg om,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> neml.:</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda, sköta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt lefwande (isynnerhet om kroppens wård och hwad dermed förliknas):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> se molliter, Ter.; c-a te <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tag wara på dig),</text:span> mi Tiro; se reficere et c.; acies animi ita c-ata, ut ne cæcetur erroribus; qui civitati præfuturi sunt, totum reipublicæ corpus c-ent, C.; corpora c-re milites jubet; c-tus cibo, L.; corpora, vites, Vg.; in cute c-dā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fodra köttet)</text:span> plus æquo operata juventus, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om läkare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköta, behandla, bota:</text:span></text:span> corpora; medici leviter ægrotantes leniter curant; medicaminibus aliquem, C.; herbis, Ov.; quum nec c-ri posset nec officium desereret, vim morbi sustinere non potuit, Cs.; sanguinis detractione, Qu.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköta, ombesörja, draga försorg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">taga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hafwa bestyr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">laga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att -:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: (construeradt med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">obj. acc., gerundivum, ut</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.</text:span>): funus, Ter.; negotia; senes, quæ c-ant, omnia meminerunt; magna dii c-ant, parva negligunt; c-a, ut valeas; c-a, ne quid desit; Fimbria c-verat, ut Scævola laniaretur; epistolam referendam c., C.; facile vobis injurias sociorum c-re licet; ex coriis utres uti fierent, c-bat, Sa.; pontem in Arari faciendum c-at; obsides dandos c-verat, Cs.; aliena negotia curo excussus propriis, Hor.; convivia, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om offentliga ärenden och förrättningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwalta, styra, förestå;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föra befälet:</text:span></text:span> provinciam, C.; rebus publicis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i analogi med</text:span> præesse), Pt.; rempublicam; Manlium in dextrā c-re jubet, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. pecuniam alicui c-re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utanordna, -betala:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hafwa omsorg, wårda sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bry, bekymra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fråga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter (wanl. med negation l. i fråga, constr. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc., inf., ind. frågesats</text:span>): c-ns, cogitans, Pt.; id populus c-et scilicet!, Ter.; quando me ista c-asse arbitramini?; nihil c-dum est post mortem; de emendo nihil c-t; quantum famæ dandum sit, vivi c-ent; liberi esse non c-atis; non c-it redire, C.; dii non c-ant, quid agat humanum genus, Enn.; o crudelis Alexi, nihil mea carmina c-as; nihil ille deos, nil carmina c-at, Vg.; sunt, qui non habeant: est, qui non c-et habere, Hor.; non c-o tumulum, Mæcenas ap. Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäl skött, fodrad:</text:span></text:span> bos c-ior, Cato.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfällig, angelägen:</text:span></text:span> c-issimis Augustæ precibus protectus est, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfälligt, angeläget, ifrigt:</text:span></text:span> Sa., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">werkställbar, som kan tillwägabringas:</text:span> vox incerta: Juv. XVI. 21. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppslig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wård, skötsel:</text:span></text:span> c. et cultus corporis; ovium, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Helsowård, botande, cur:</text:span></text:span> præscribere valetudinis c-em; c-es ancipites et periculosas adhibere, C.; c. procedit, recte p., Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ombesörjande, förwaltning, förrättning:</text:span></text:span> id est meæ c-is; pecuniæ c. (et valetudinis); Asiatica frumenti c., C.; Lætorio data est c. altior fastigio suo, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdare, uppsyningsman, föreståndare; förwaltare:</text:span></text:span> urbis, annonæ, ludorum c-es ædiles, C.; it. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på embetsmän i colonier,</text:span> Iscr.; viæ Flaminiæ; Demosthenes c. muris reficiendis fuit; præficere aliquem c-em, qui -, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ombud:</text:span></text:span> Sulla reipublicæ Romanæ c. ad Bocchum missus; negotiorum fidus c., Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förmyndare; administrator:</text:span></text:span> a prætore datus, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skötsel, förplägning, underhåll:</text:span></text:span> c-ā facere junceam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smal som ett säf),</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ombesörja, laga, sköta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gå noggrannt, sorgfälligt till wäga:</text:span></text:span> prandium alicui, Pt.; rem cautius, Ter.; melius a-antur, quæ consilio geruntur, quam quæ sine c., C.; a-ato opus est, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om saker) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Noggrann, laggrann, wårdad, omsorgsfull, -fullt utarbetad, punktlig:</text:span></text:span> literæ a-issimæ; diligentia a-issima; oratio, sermo, C.; malitia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(studerad),</text:span> Pt.; delectus a-ior, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accūrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorgsfullt, noggrannt, grundligt:</text:span></text:span> defendere alqm; scribere ad alqm; ædificare; disputare; perscribere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Artigt:</text:span></text:span> a. et liberaliter recipere, habere, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Noggrannhet:</text:span></text:span> in inveniendis componendisque rebus mira a., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillika sköta, laga:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omsorgsfullt lagad:</text:span></text:span> victus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Icke skött, wanskött:</text:span></text:span> ulcus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdslöshet, owårdsamhet:</text:span></text:span> vituperanda est rei tam necessariæ tanta i., C.; non ego paucis offendar maculis, quas i. fudit, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanwård, -skötsel;</text:span></text:span> milites fame et i-ā consumpti, C.; ædes vetustate et i-ā prolabebantur, N. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdslös:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">activ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Likgiltig:</text:span></text:span> vetera extollimus, recentium i-i, T.; in capillis comendis i., Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: multiplex et non i-a historia, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incūriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: C<text:span text:style-name="T2">omp.</text:span> -ius: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårdslöst:</text:span></text:span> castra ponere, L., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percūriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket nyfiken:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Riktigt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillfyllest hela, bota:</text:span></text:span> vixdum satis p-to vulnere, L.; mentem, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda, sköta, omhulda:</text:span></text:span> arbores, Cato; pueros; mihi bene, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ombesörja, besörja, bestyra:</text:span></text:span> sacrificia, Cs.; sacra, N.; hæc, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ngns uppdrag </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwalta:</text:span></text:span> negotia et rationes, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: wara kejserlig förwaltare (procurator):</text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i religionsspråket:</text:span> monstra, prodigia, ostenta, fulgura, somnia p.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sona, försona</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (medelst ceremonier afwända de olyckor, hwarmed de hota):</text:span> C., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wård, uppsigt, omsorg, förwaltning:</text:span></text:span> ædium sacrarum; deus habet p-em rerum humanarum; ut tutela, sic p. reip. ad utilitatem eorum, qui commissi sunt, gerenda est; provinciæ, annonæ, C.; ejus ministerii p. (census), L.; regni, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kejserlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwaltningspost</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> procurator): T., Lpd.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Försoning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (se</text:span> procuro, 4.): sue fit plena p., C.; prodigii, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūrātiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten förwaltning:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwaltare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för ngns räkning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föreståndare, fullmäktig, fogde:</text:span></text:span> per p-em agere aliquid; p-i mandare aliquid de aliqua re, C.; regni, Cs.; vilæ, Pn.; apum, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: kejserlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Procurator,</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">embetsman, som dels uppbar kejsarens inkomster i provinser i allm., dels i wissa provinser (såsom</text:span> Judæa) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">war den högste styresmannen</text:span> (cum gladio): p. fisci, Su.; p. Judææ Pontius Pilatus, T. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se Marquardt, Röm. Alt.</text:span> III. 299 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcūrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwalterska:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sköta, ansa om; wäl bearbeta:</text:span></text:span> se, corpus, Catl., Ap.; chartam, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēcūrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> sē <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan och</text:span> cura): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bekymmerslös, sorglös, obekymrad, fri från bekymmer, utan farhåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fara, trygg, säker, lugn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till sinne l. tillstånd):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span> legio reddit nos s-os; s-um proficisci; s. ab hac parte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från denna sida, i detta hänseende);</text:span> animi esse s-i de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lugn för)</text:span> re, <text:soft-page-break/>C.; de bello Romano rex s. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan fruktan för);</text:span> a Samnitibus, L.; s. poenæ (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan farhåga för),</text:span> Hor.; mollia s-æ peragebant otia gentes (aureæ ætatis), Ov.; s. de constantia alicujus; suæ potentiæ s. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(säker på),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> res ab hoste s-æ; locus quietus et s., L.; vita, N.; otia s-a agere, Vg.; s-um olus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i lugn njutna grönsaker);</text:span> deos didici s-um agere ævom, Hor.; somnus a metu, locus ab afflatu s., Pn.; materiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för historieskrifning)</text:span> uberiorem et s-iorem senectuti seposui; loca s-a ejusmodi casuum, T.; convivium, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tadlande men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obekymrad om, likgiltig för;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wårdslös, lättsinnig:</text:span></text:span> s. solutusque, L.; s-us amorum germanæ (maritum obtruncat), Vg.; s., cadat an recto stet fabula talo, Hor.; luxus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fri, fräck),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēcūre</text:span>, -cūrius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bekymmerslöst, sorglöst, tryggt, utan fara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">farhåga:</text:span></text:span> vivere, Val.; continere, Vell.; intueri, Pn.; pugnare, Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sēcūrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet från bekymmer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">farhåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fara), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sorglöshet, säkerhet, trygghet, lugn:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">subj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">obj.</text:span>: caput est ad beate vivendum s.; s. est vacuitas ægritudinis; s. est animi tranquillitas; præstare alicui s-em, C.; s-is magna portio est nihil iniqui facere, Sen.; otium et s., Pn.; s. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lugn)</text:span> novissima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i döden);</text:span> s. publica <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samhällslugn),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättsinne, wårdslöshet, säkerhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blind l. fräck):</text:span> infelix; scribendi, Qu.; inhumana s. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fräckhet);</text:span> - cladibus approbatum est, non esse curæ diis s-em nostram, esse ultionem, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säkerhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för en fodran l. utbetalning (revers, qvittance, pant o. d.):</text:span> Jct., Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curo, Cura.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curalium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coralium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curo, Cura.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Curcŭlio,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sädesmask:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Vg., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curcŭliuncŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŭres, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Sabinum.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŭrensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ūrētes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Jupiters prester på Creta.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cūrētis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cretisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūria,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Curia</text:span></text:span> i. e.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afdelning af romerska folket (patricierna) enligt</text:span> Romuli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anordning</text:span> (3 tribus, 30 curiæ): L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samlingsort (helgedom, tempel) för en curia:</text:span> c., ubi curant res divinas sacerdotes, ut c-æ veteres, Varr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Helgedom,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> samlingsort för religiösa brödraskap:</text:span> Saliorum, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senatshus:</text:span></text:span> c., ubi senatus curat res humanas, Varr.; c. Hostilia, Pompeja, Julia; dies c-æ fuisse videbatur, convivium Tusculani, C.; c-æ, quum profana loca fuissent, templa per augures constitutæ sunt, ut in iis senatus consulta justa fieri possent, Gell.; c-a pauperibus clausa est, Ov. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Romerske senaten:</text:span></text:span> c. mæsta orat consulem, L.; Pollio præsidium consulenti c-æ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rådhus, senatshus</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerhufwud:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medlem af samma curia - af</text:span> C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anwändt = medlem af samma</text:span> demos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i Attica):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hofman:</text:span></text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter curier:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūriātus</text:span>, comitia c-a = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">curieförsamling, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Folkförsamling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af curierna;</text:span> lex c-a, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af curierna stiftad, wedertagen,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūrio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Föreståndare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (prest) för en curia:</text:span> in curiis sacrorum cura publica: ab his c-es, Varr.; C. maximus, L.; c. sacra indicit, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curialis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curianus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>uriatii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de albanske trillingarne, som kämpade med de romerske</text:span> Horatii: L. I. 24 ff.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curiatim,<text:line-break/>Curiatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Curio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cura.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Curio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">III. <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ūrio, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Scribonia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curios . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cura.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cūris,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kastspjut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sabiniskt ord, enligt)</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ŭrius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cŭriānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cura.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curriculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Curro,</text:span> cŭcurri, cursum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, springa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> ad me c-itur, Ter.; si ingredere, c-e; si c-is, advola; ad complexum Tulliæ; incitare c-entem; stadium c-ere, C.; mures pavidi, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om hastig, brådskande rörelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, ila, fara,</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerfara):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor:</text:span> c-is mercator ad Indos; caelum, non animos mutant, qui trans mare c-unt, Hor.; cavā trabe c-mus æquor, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra subject, som röra sig i rummet:</text:span> sidera, Ov.; classis c. iter tutum; rubor per ora; fluvii in freta c-unt; stella, Vg.; rota, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om l. i tiden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, förlöpa, -flyta:</text:span></text:span> nox, Ppt.; ætas, Hor.; secula c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomlefwa),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tal (prosa och vers) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, ila:</text:span></text:span> oratio c-it proclivius, C.; incomposito dixi pede c-ere versus; est brevitate opus, ut c-at sententia, Hor.<text:line-break/>e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sträcka sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om det som ej röres):</text:span> litus, Lucr.; purpura circum chlamydem, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Currĭcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lopp, språng:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> curre strenue et unum c. face, Pt.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> c-o, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">språng,</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kappränning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till fots, häst, wagns):</text:span> semel quadrigis, s. desultore misso vix unius horæ tempus utrumque c. complebat, L.; - quod sine c-o et sine certatione corporum fiat -, C. de Leg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bana,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> der ngn löper:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> solis, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> consuetudo deflexit jam aliquantum de spatio c-oque; exiguum vitæ c., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rännarebana;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfningsplats:</text:span></text:span> quum athletas se exercentes in c-o videret, aspexisse lacertos suos dicitur illacrimansque -, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wädjobana, öfningsfält</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fält l. utrymme för ngns werksamhet l. talanger):</text:span> tuum erat forum, tuum illud c.; (vereor), ecquodnam c. habitura sit tua natura admirabilis doctrina et industria; mentis, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarpå man färdas, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wagn,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kappränningswagn:</text:span></text:span> c-o pulverem Olympicum collegisse, Hor.; c-o quadrigarum insistere, T.; equi præcipitare c. in amnem, Ct. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> currus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I språng, i ilmarsch:</text:span></text:span> rapere ad carnificem, Pt.; agmen agere, L.; irrumpere in Asiam, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I hast, i förbigående, flygtigt:</text:span></text:span> arripere studium, C.; legere et annotare c., Pn.; percensuit c. numerum legionum, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpande:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curso</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ideligen löpa, löpa hit och dit:</text:span></text:span> ultro citroque c-satur, Ter.; per foros nautæ; circum patronos c-sant, C.; c-itat turba, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snabb-, kapplöpare;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kapprännar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">e (äfwen till häst l. wagns):</text:span> c. sibi visus est in somnis curru quadrigarum vehi, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ilbud, curir:</text:span></text:span> Athenienses c-em miserunt Lacedæmonem, N. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> framför wagn:</text:span> sic peregrinantur, ut agmen c-um antecedat, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpande:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lopp, språng, springande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> ingressus, c., C.; c-u exanimari; c-u fugere, Cs.; c-u tendere, Sa.; c-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med språng)</text:span> in hostem ferri, L.; c-u superare canem, Hor.; celer, citus c., Sen. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om kapplopp, -ränning:</text:span> c., certamen, Ov.; optatam c-u contingere metam, Hor.; c-u certare cum æqualibus, Sa.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i widsträcktare betydelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rörelse, färd, fart, resa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span><text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor och deras fortskaffningsmedel:</text:span> est mihi c. in Italiam; c. maritimus; naves in c-u viderat tendentes Rhodum; revocare a c-u; sustinere, inhibere c-um, C.; navium, Cs.; amnis c., L.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om naturföremål: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rörelse, lopp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (omlopp):</text:span> stellarum, lunæ, amnis, C.; fluminis, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttryck:</text:span> vos jam estis in c-u (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">studiet);</text:span> cui censemus c-um ad deum faciliorem fuisse quam Scipioni?; ita minus retardabitur c. animorum (e corpore egressorum); c-um orationis impedire; tuum c-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(färd till ärans höjd)</text:span> importuna premit clades reipublicæ, C.; spes fuit in c-u, Ov.; vocis per omnes sonos c., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på rörelsens hastighet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fart, lopp:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> duplicare c-um, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck.:</text:span> tantus fuit c. verborum; c. in oratione incitatior, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lägenhet för resa, befordringssätt:</text:span> c-um exspectare, C., Sa.; c-u publico uti, Pn. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rörelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afseende på deß rigtning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rigtning, kosa, bana:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> c-um tenere Syracusas; c-um commutare; navis retinet motum c-mque eundem; (duplices sunt c. animorum e corpore excedentium), C.; incerto c-u navigare; c-um aliquem tenere, Cs.; c-um dirigere, tendere aliquo, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> eum c-um vitæ tenere, sequi; certo genere c-uque vitæ implicari; animi c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinnesrigtning);</text:span> omnium virtutum c. ad voluptatem, C.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på rörelsens längd l. förlopp:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färd, resa:</text:span></text:span> c. brevissimus, Vg.; c. secundus, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bana, sträcka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tidens, lifwets, händelsernas </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gång, utweckling:</text:span></text:span> vitæ brevis c.; tantus illi c. honorum fuit; c. rerum; temporum; facile totius vitæ c-um videt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> ad uos, ad Tusculanum; Romam; ad præmium, C.; in auxilium, Sa.; equo ad aliquem, Cs; a-it homo notus mihi nomine tantum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Accursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillopp:</text:span></text:span> multitudinis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antĕcursor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förelöpare;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förtrupp:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumcurro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa i krets:</text:span></text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumcurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ideligen löpa omkring:</text:span></text:span> omnia, Pt., Ter., Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personliga subject:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, strömma tillsammans, till; skocka sig, slå sig tillsammans</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för l. emot ngn):</text:span> populus, tota Italia; civitas Lampsacenorum; c-ant omnes philosophi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låt dem slå sig tillsammans),</text:span> C.; ad arma c., Cs.; undique ex agris c., N.; in Capitolium c-sum est, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammandrabba:</text:span></text:span> infestis signis; equis; magno clamore, Sa.; Antonius sine mora; ad non dubiam mortem, C.; inter se, Cs.; cum aliquo, L.; ferro, Ov.; c-itur: horæ momento venit aut mors aut victoria, Hor.; hosti, Vg., Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakliga subject:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanstöta, slås (slå) tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> verba aspere, C.; montes montibus, Vg.; naves proris, L.; dextera lævæ, Hor.; labra, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om händelser, omständigheter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanträffa:</text:span></text:span> quæ ut c-ant omnia, optabile est, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om drömmar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slå in:</text:span></text:span> somnia casu, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanstötande:</text:span></text:span> corpusculorum; vocum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stöta ihop:</text:span></text:span> primordia animai c-ant et coëunt, Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, ströfwa, resa omkring:</text:span></text:span> leno circum tabernas; præcones in provincia, C.; toto foro candidati; Celtiberis in proelio c-re mos est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att angripa än här, än der),</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomströfwa:</text:span></text:span> omnes omnium domos, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanlopp, upplopp:</text:span></text:span> nocturna, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanträffande, öfwerensstämmelse:</text:span></text:span> qui ordo, quæ c. somniorum?, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringlöpande:</text:span></text:span> Libonis, C.; incerta mulierum, L.; formicæ, Pn.; miles melior c-e, quam cominus, Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concursātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: levis et c. hostis (in pugna huc illuc discurrens), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Concursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskors:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanlopp, -strömmande, tillopp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (folkskockning, upplopp):</text:span> c. fiunt undique ab agris, C.; in forum a tota urbe; Tatius Lavinii c-u facto interficitur, L.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammandrabbning:</text:span></text:span> utriusque exercitus, Cs.; acerrimo c-u pugnare; uno c-u, N.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanstötning, -strömning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> m. m.:</text:span> Democritus fortuito c-u atomorum mundum efficit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tänker sig uppkommen);</text:span> verborum asper aut hiulcus c., C.; navium, L.; torrentium, Ct. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanträffande, samwerkan:</text:span></text:span> occupationum, calamitatum; artium maximarum c. quantam vim habeat, existimari potest, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fara, swäfwa, rycka, segla) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ned:</text:span></text:span> ex montibus, Cs.; de tribunali, de Janiculo, L.; Laocoon ardens summā d-rit ab arce; Iris cito tramite, Vg.; piscis ad hamum, Hor.; celeri cymba <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedåt strömmen),</text:span> Ov.; fluvius ad oceanum; India ad planitiem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sänker sig till, löper ut i -),</text:span> Pn.; naves (Romā Ostiam), T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa till målet, till ett mål, fara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någorstädes hän:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> ad calcem d-sum est; rus, C.; rhythmi, qua coeperunt, sublatione et positione ad finem usque d-unt, Qu. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Komma till ett resultat, wända sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wälja en utwäg, taga sin tillflykt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span> omnium sententiæ eo d-erunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stannade derwid),</text:span> ut pax peteretur, L.; eo d-sum est, ut -, L., T.; ad jura, ad hortationem, C.; Lucilius nunquam alio, d-bat, si male cesserat -; ad preces d., Hor.; ad remedium, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om trupper (för öfnings, uppwisnings skull, till ngns honnör): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Marschera, tåga i procession, paradera:</text:span></text:span> legiones in armis IV milium spatium d-erunt; ad rogum Gracchi exercitus Hannibalis decucurrit, L.; honori patris Germanicus cum legionibus d-rit, T.; circa Drusi tumulum miles quotannis, Su. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i eg. och oeg. men.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomlöpa, tillryggalägga, genomgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rum, tid, framställning):</text:span> d-so spatio a calce ad carceres revocari; mille passus d.; ætatem; ista, quæ a te breviter d-sa sunt, explices, C.; vitam, Phdr.; laborem, Vg.; per capita aliquid, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utfall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (krigiskt):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fältmanöver, parad, revy:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedlöpande, -ryckande, -störtande:</text:span></text:span> Albanorum subitus ex collibus, L.; aquarum, Lucr.; montanorum in litora, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilländalöpande:</text:span></text:span> temporis mei; d-u honorum, flexu ætatis, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfningsmarsch, militärisk manöver; festtåg:</text:span></text:span> justus, L.; cur me in d-u lampada poscis, Ps.; femina (Agrippina) intererat legionum d-bus, T.; d. ludicri et simulacra proeliorum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa hit och dit, omkring, sprida sig:</text:span></text:span> in muris, Cs.; juventus ad capiendas virgines; in cornua, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sprida sig, fördela sig:</text:span></text:span> Nilus in septem ora, Vg.; fama totā urbe, Ct.; venæ ex fonte in priora et terga, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa hit och dit:</text:span></text:span> in agendo orator, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringlöpande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rännande:</text:span></text:span> officiosa per urbem d., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discursātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: pedes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skärmytslande):</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Discursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpande (hit och dit), kringspringande, -ströfwande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">farande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">flygande:</text:span></text:span> militum, Cs.; candidatorum, Pn. ep.; telorum, Val.; stellarum d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid stjernfall),</text:span> Pn.; quidquid agunt homines, votum, timor, ira, voluptas, gaudia, discursus nostri est farrago libelli, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, fara, swäfwa ut, göra en utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> domo; in Pompejanum; legati ad aliquem; Sicilia provincia propinqua, quo facile cives Romani e. possint; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> animi spretis corporibus evolant e-untque foras, C.; orator e-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(löper, störtar fram mot åhörarne),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra ett utfall, ströfwa in på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> ex Africa, C.; armati in fines Romanos, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om orter, massor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skjuta ut -, strömma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ut:</text:span></text:span> peninsula, L.; planities in meridiem, Pn.; fons ex monte, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om rhythmer, ord, werksamhet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swäfwa ut, utbreda sig, röra sig fritt:</text:span></text:span> longius oratio; aures immoderatius e-tia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der det rhythmiska målet öfwerskrides)</text:span> sentiunt; campus, in quo virtus e. possit, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">till ända, ändas;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">genomlöpa:</text:span></text:span> oratio pariter cum sententia, C.; verbum in IV syllabas, Qu.; e-so spatio, Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ut-, framlöpande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflygt, resa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">talarens framgående mot åhörarne:</text:span> rarus incessus, e. moderata, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utfall; infall, ströftåg:</text:span></text:span> crebræ hostium, barbarorum e-es, N.; fines ab e-bus hostium et latrociniis tueri, C.; invicem e-es facere, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> tanquam levis armaturæ prima orationis e., C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra utfall:</text:span></text:span> St. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utfall:</text:span></text:span> Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excursātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fribytare:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excursor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fribytare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som för ströfkrig):</text:span> Verris emissarius et e., C.; paratissimus pro nobis, Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Excursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflygt:</text:span></text:span> apum brevis, Varr.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Digression:</text:span></text:span> varii e., Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utfall:</text:span></text:span> navigiorum, Cs.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsprång:</text:span></text:span> montis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg:.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, störta, stöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra anfall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">infall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någorstädes:</text:span> caeco impetu in aliquem; in tenebris nusquam i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stöta emot),</text:span> C.; in nostros; Mauris, Sa.; in Romanos, in Macedoniam, L.; Romano hostis, Hor.; densis i-mus armis, Vg.; ursi armentis, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anfalla</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>): latus hostium, L.; novissimos, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anfalla:</text:span></text:span> in aliquem, C., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöta, gränsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> intill:</text:span> ager in publicum Campanum i-it, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">falla i = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa föremål, råka ut för:</text:span></text:span> in oculos aliquid; in varias reprehensiones, in odia, in morbos, C.; oculis, Sen.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om händelser) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infalla, inträffa:</text:span></text:span> id in Etesias; tempora i-unt, quæ conturbent animos, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På-, motstötning:</text:span></text:span> atomorum, armorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fiendtligt):</text:span> i-em facere in fines Romanos, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusa in, stöta på;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerfalla, göra infall på:</text:span></text:span> ramis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Ov.; arietes in aliquem; pugnis aliquem, Pt.; in hostem; agros (<text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>), L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om abstracta subject) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Träffa:</text:span></text:span> in te dolor, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla i, bli föremål för:</text:span></text:span> oculis aliquid, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incursĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusa emot; stöta på, emot:</text:span></text:span> in aliquem; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.,</text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anrusande, -fall:</text:span></text:span> primo i-u pulsi hostes, L.; moles i-ūs aquarum prædelassat, Ov.; luporum, Vg.; solis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intercurro</text:span>, curri, cursum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, fara, komma emellan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> fretum, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga sig emellan:</text:span></text:span> misimus, qui - i-erent, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om händelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Komma emellan, afbryta:</text:span></text:span> dolor his exercitationibus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Under tiden fara till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> dictator Vejos, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intercurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fara, ströfwa emellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> barbari, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intercursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpande, farande, flygande emellan:</text:span></text:span> nox horrida i-u luminis diri, Sen.; matronarum, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mellankomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (medlande):</text:span> rixa sedata est i-u consulum; usus hastarum impeditus i-u suorum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occurro</text:span>, curri, cursum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: löpa emot, i wägen för -:</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personliga subject:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusa, skynda emot, möta, träffa på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">möta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= inställa sig):</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>hostibus; armatis; o. aliquo et ferre auxilium; signis, Cs.; acies ex adverso, L.; obviam o. alicui, Pt., C., Cs.; rex o-it; hostilis facies; turmæ; telis, Vg.; posticæ sannæ, Ps.; ad tempus, C.; ad concilium; comitiis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>), L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Komma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gå ngt till mötes</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (träffa på, finna, söka):</text:span> alio consilio venerat, aliis rebus o-it, Cs.; ultro negotiis o., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakliga subj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">möta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöta på, emot:</text:span></text:span> silex ferro, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skjuta ut emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> Media Parthiæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gå, komma till mötes, emot</text:span></text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta sig emot, söka mota, förekomma:</text:span></text:span> quid o-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(står i wägen),</text:span> non vides; consiliis alicujus; malevolentiæ; satietati aurium, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Söka tillfredsställa, hjelpa:</text:span></text:span> exspectationi alicujus; misericordia supplicibus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bemöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns ord, serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra ett inkast, en inwändning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot:</text:span> orationi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beswara),</text:span> T.; dictis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>), Vg.; o-itur nobis a doctis viris - quærentibus -, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">möta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framställa sig, framträda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för ngns ögon:</text:span> non jam amplius ullæ o-unt terræ, caelum undique et u. pontus, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för ngns inbillning eller tanke (komma för ngn, falla ngn in, erbjuda sig):</text:span> id animo, menti, in mentem; res inquirenti o-it; omnes loci - anquirentibus ostendunt se et o-unt; dicacibus difficillimum est - ea, quæ o-unt, quum salsissime dici possint, tenere; tu mihi o-bas dignus eo munere; o-bat ei, mancam præturam suam futuram consule Milone, C.; quotiescunque patria in mentem veniebat, hæc omnia o-bant - colles, campus, Tiberis -, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Möte:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rusa emot; gå emot:</text:span></text:span> gladio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med swärd),</text:span> Cs.; o-ntes interficere, Su.; portis, L.; capro, Vg.; numinibus, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställa sig i wägen, emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> nobiles o-bant, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">in:</text:span></text:span> id animo, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occursācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: nocturnum o. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= spöke),</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skyndande emot -, förbindligt tillmötesgående:</text:span></text:span> o. et blanditia popularis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occursātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som möter:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Occursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Möte:</text:span></text:span> hominum, L.; luporum, Ov., T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöt, stötande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot:</text:span> rota o-u stipitis fracta, Ov.; dentis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. och oeg.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">igenom, öfwer:</text:span></text:span> per civitates (oratio), C; per temonem, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fram till, till:</text:span></text:span> ad aliquem, C.; ad forum, Ter.; citato equo Cales, L.; ad præturam, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet, med ögonen, i tanken, framställningen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomlöpa, -fara, öfwerfara, genomgå:</text:span></text:span> regiones, agrum, Cs.; pectine telas, Vg.; pectora metus, Ct.; oculo aliquid, Hor.; animo aliquid, C., Hor.; legendo p. aliquid; oratione multas res; hæc properans p-o; debemus habere hos omnes locos animo p-sos et <text:soft-page-break/>tractatos, C.; nomina, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flygtigt genomgående, öfwerfarande:</text:span></text:span> (animi) multarum rerum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomströfwa, kringströfwa:</text:span></text:span> ripas, Pn.; finibus nostris, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Percursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomströfwande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">resande:</text:span></text:span> Italiæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda, komma förut, i förwäg:</text:span></text:span> præcurre!, Ter.; p-unt equites: quanto sit res in periculo, cognoscunt; ante omnes; ad Cæsarem; fama eo præcurrerat, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i tiden) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gå, komma förut, föregå</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem</text:span>): certis rebus certa signa p-unt; p-ntia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= det, som föregår en sak);</text:span> ætate aliquem; nihil turpius est, quam cognitioni - assertionem approbationemque p-re; appetitus rationem neque p-ant neque propter ignaviam deserant; ita p-it amor judicium, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerträffa, få försteg framför:</text:span></text:span> homo iners diligentem; vobis illum p-ere vix honestum est, C.; celeritate aliquem, Cs.; licet sub paupere tecto reges et regum vitā p-re amicos, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Föregående</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tid):</text:span> assensio non fit sine visorum p-e, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">För-fäktning:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: (om talarens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inledning):</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcursor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förelöpare:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i krig:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förtrupp:</text:span></text:span> L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för ngns wagn, bärstol o. s. w.:</text:span> Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> in omni calumnia habere alqm p-em et emissarium, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Præcursōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förelöpande, förberedande:</text:span></text:span> epistola, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prætercurro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, fara förbi:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, springa, fara, rycka fram:</text:span></text:span> ultra, C.; in publicum; in pugnam, Cs.; in vias, L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skjuta fram:</text:span></text:span> mons in mare, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltaga:</text:span></text:span> pecunia, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcursio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framspringande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (under föredraget):</text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflygt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från ämnet):</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framrycka:</text:span></text:span> a stationibus, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcursātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framrusande</text:span></text:span> (instabili pugnā): Numidarum, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcursātōres</text:span>, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtrupper:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framryckande:</text:span></text:span> militum, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framskjutande:</text:span></text:span> chlamydis, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framsteg:</text:span></text:span> virtutis, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcurro</text:span>, curri, cursum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerhufwud i rummet): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda tillbaka, återgå, </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">återkomma, -wända:</text:span></text:span> puer ad me; ad rhedam, C.; ad Hispalim, Cs.; vir rure, Hor.; aqua ad fontes, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> naturam furcā expellas, tamen usque r-et, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tid, till ett tillstånd, om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Återkomma:</text:span></text:span> (sidera) unde generata sint, quo r-ant; luna defectionibus ad initia r., C.; bruma r-it iners; libertasque r-tes accepta per annos lusit -, Hor.; sol, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Återkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en tanke, utwäg, plan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">taga sin tillflykt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span> ad easdem condiciones, Cs.; ad eandem rationem, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om abstracta subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sträcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig tillbaka i tid; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">återkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngns tankar:</text:span> eadem æquitas retro r. (ad parentes); id r-et memoriæ, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcurso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ideligen återkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och oeg. bet.):</text:span> huc, Pt.; virtus hominis animo; sub noctem cura, Vg.; animo omina, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillbakalöpande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">swallande:</text:span></text:span> cursus atque r. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ridt fram och tillbaka);</text:span> languentis pelagi r., Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Återgång (wäg tillbaka); återkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tid):</text:span> ad moenia patet r., L.; pomorum annui, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Succurro</text:span>, curri, cursum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, gå inunder, hän under:</text:span></text:span> lunæ corpus, Lucr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda, ila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn till hjelp; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bispringa, bistå, hjelpa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med sakliga object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">söka afhjelpa, rädda:</text:span></text:span> licet impendeant pericula omnia, s-am atque subibo, C.; laborantibus, C., Cs.; auxilio alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngn till hjelp),</text:span> Sa.; afflictis; vitæ, saluti alicujus, N.; his malis hæc subsidia s-bant, Cs.; alicujus adversæ fortunæ s-sum velle, L. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Komma, falla, rinna ngn i hågen:</text:span></text:span> quidquid s-it, libet scribere; mihi verba; s-it grave esse; multa s-unt, L.; pulcrumque mori s-it in armis, Vg.; s. mirari, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sŭpercurro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerstiga:</text:span></text:span> ager vectigal large, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transcurro</text:span>, cŭcurri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> curri, cursum, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löpa, skynda förbi, öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ett ställe till ett annat, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwergå:</text:span></text:span> hinc ad forum, Ter.; remos t-tes detergere, Cs.; in altera castra t-sum est, L.; præter oculos, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwergå:</text:span></text:span> in rem dissimilem, C.; ad melius, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förgå:</text:span></text:span> æstas, Pn.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerfara; skyndsamt tillryggalägga:</text:span></text:span> nimbus caelum, Vg.; Hellespontum, N.; Campaniam, Su.; cursum suum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I korthet genomgå; förbigå:</text:span></text:span> aliquid, Pn.; ea sciens t-am, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Transcursus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genom-, öfwer-, förbifarande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gående:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> per aëra, Sen.; fulguris, Su.<text:line-break/>b. t-u, in t-u dicere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i förbigående),</text:span> Pn., Vell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Currūca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: vox incerta: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dumhufwud?):</text:span> Juv. VI. 275.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Currus,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> curro? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller med</text:span> carrus? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller med båda?): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wagn, hjuldon:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c-u vehi, c-um flectere, sustinere, C.; arcuatus c., L.; c-um agere; Phaëthon c-us auriga paterni, Ov.; c. aratri; quadrijugus, rapidus, secundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ilande)</text:span> Neptuni, Vg.; Palladis c.; nitidus solis, Hor.; aureus, inauratus, ovans <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(triumphwagn),</text:span> Ppt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. l. oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Triumphwagn, triumph:</text:span></text:span> uni huic externo c. datus, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ett skepp (Argo):</text:span> levi volitans flamine c., Catl.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spannet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för wagnen</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>): domitare, infrenare, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Curs . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>urtius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Curtus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarpå ngt är afslaget, -brutet, -hugget) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stympad, stubbad, stubbig, söndrig:</text:span></text:span> dolium, Lucr.; c-o temone jugum, Juv.; Judæus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omskuren);</text:span> c. mulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med stubbswans?),</text:span> Hor.; c-a testa, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">För kort, knapp, otillräcklig, bristfällig:</text:span></text:span> aures c-a sentiunt, non amant redundantia; sententia c-a (multa prætermittentis), C.; c-æ nescio quid semper abest rei, Hor.; c-a supellex, Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förminska; borttaga:</text:span></text:span> rem, Ps.; summæ aliquid, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēcurtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afstympad:</text:span></text:span> aures mutila et quasi d-a sentiunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭrūlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> currus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wagns- = som är för wagn, sker till wagns:</text:span> equi c-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmodligen för de circensiska spelen),</text:span> L.; triumphus c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> ovatio), Su.<text:line-break/>2. sella, sedes c-is = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten, på</text:span> tribunal <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stående stol af elfenben, hwarpå konungar, consuler, prætorer, censorer och</text:span> ædiles curules <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sutto: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Curulisk:</text:span></text:span> sella c., C., L.; sedes c., T. - c-e ebur, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf:</text:span> c-es magistratus, c-es ædiles = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som begagna</text:span> sella curulis: C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Curvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bågig, krökt, krokig, bugtig, krum:</text:span></text:span> cornua, Varr.; alvus equi; puppes, carinæ, falces, litora, arator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lutad),</text:span> Vg.; c-o dignoscere rectum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl.);</text:span> ungues, id, Hor.; anus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(böjd af ålder);</text:span> arcus, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokighet:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kröka, böja, bugta:</text:span></text:span> cornu flexile <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bågen),</text:span> Ov.; arcum manu, St.; portus c-atur in arcum, Vg.; aper lancem; c-ati ignes lunæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> te nec munera nec preces c-ant, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krökning, bugt:</text:span></text:span> ripæ, St.; limitis, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krökning:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krökning, hwalf, båge:</text:span></text:span> c. rotæ, Ov.; unguium, Pn.; montis, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Curvor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokighet:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjd, krökt:</text:span></text:span> homo i., tremulus, Ter.; lituus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurvesco</text:span> (-visco), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kröka sig, böjas:</text:span></text:span> rami baccarum ubertate, poēt. ap. C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kröka, böja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. och oeg.):</text:span> baculum i-tum, C.; arcum, Vg.; querelā i. aliquem, Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: caudæ, Hyg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incurvĭcervīcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med krökt nacke:</text:span> Pac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcurvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framåt böjd, krökt:</text:span></text:span> falx, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prōcurvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kröka framåt:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcurvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bakåt krökt, tillbakaböjd:</text:span></text:span> cornu, Vg.; pedes r-i corvi; æra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(metkrok),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcurvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böja, kröka tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> radicem, Col.; Mæandrus ludit in r-atis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillbakaslingrande)</text:span> undis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcurvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något krökt:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cuspis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spets, udd, gadd:</text:span></text:span> hastæ, Hor.; apis, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngt spetsigt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spett, spjut,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (treudd):</text:span> in c-e fumat aper, Mt.; conversa c-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spira)</text:span> montem impulit, Vg.; alte c-em gerere, L.; triplex Neptuni, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cuspĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillspetsa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cuspĭdātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I spets:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭcuspis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trespetsig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-uddig:</text:span></text:span> telum (Neptuni), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Custos,</text:span> ōdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Waktare, wäktare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-erska),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i concret men.):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: som står, går på wakt, håller wakt för ngns säkerhet l. för att inspärra ngn, såsom hjords waktare, waktpost, lifwakt, wakttrupp, besättning, fångwaktare:</text:span> ovium; portæ; capitis alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lifwakt),</text:span> C.; Dumnorigi c-es ponit; Commium cum equitatu c-is loco in Menapiis relinquit; vigiliæ c-esque nostri, Cs.; conjuratos cum c-ibus in ædem Concordiæ venire jubet, Sa.; pontis, gazæ regiæ, corporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lifwakt),</text:span> carceris c-es; domum c-bus sæpire; Cimon in hortis nunquam imposuit c-em, N.; stabuli c. canis, Vg.; corrumpere c-es, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Waktare, wårdare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= som wakar öfwer, beskyddar):</text:span> malus c. diuturnitatis metus; præsides libertatis custodesque tribuni; c. reipublicæ senatus; c. dignitatis fortitudo; c. rebus inventis - adhibeatur memoria; dii c-es conservatoresque Romæ, C.; montium c. nemorumque virgo (Diana); virtutis veræ c. rigidusque satelles, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moralisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppsyningsman:</text:span></text:span> apponere filio c-em, N.; imberbis juvenis tandem c-e remoto, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">qwarsittande skott på den afqwistade winstocken</text:span> (unde vitis sequenti anno renovatur): Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Custōdēla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wakt, bewakning;</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Custōdia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wakt, waktande:</text:span></text:span> pecudum, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wård, bewarande; tillsyn:</text:span></text:span> hoc volunt leges, ut libera sit et non sollicita suæ cujusque rei familiaris c.; eloquentiam velut adultam virginem domi sæptam liberali c-ā tenere, C.; pupillos - dura premit c. matrum, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Waktpost, -plats;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i synn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= de som hålla wakt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">waktposter:</text:span></text:span> in c-a collocare alqm; maximas familias - in portubus et c-is publicani habent; locum præsidiis, vigiliis, c-is munire, defendere, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fängsligt förwar, häkte, fängelse;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fångar:</text:span></text:span> in c-is haberi, teneri, Sa.; in c-am dare, tradere, conjicere, includere alqm; e c-ā <text:soft-page-break/>emitti, educi, eripi; dum sumus in hac c-a vinclisque corporis, C.; quidquid ubique erat c-æ; c-as audire, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Custōdio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wakta, hålla wakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer l. på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bewaka, låta bewaka:</text:span></text:span> corpus domumque; salutem alicujus; oram maritimam navibus; prædonum ducem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla i fängsligt förwar),</text:span> C.; ignem, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wårda, waka öfwer, bewara:</text:span></text:span> fac, ut te ipsum diligentissime c-as, mi Dolabella, C.; aliquem ab injuria, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwara:</text:span></text:span> aliquid memoriā, animo, literis, C.; poma melle, Col. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Iakttaga:</text:span></text:span> præcepta, Col.; regulam scribendi, Qu.; morem, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bewaka, -speja, taga sig i akt:</text:span></text:span> multorum te oculi speculabuntur et c-ent, C.; c., ne, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Custōdīte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Warsamt:</text:span></text:span> ludere, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incustōdītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obewakad:</text:span></text:span> ovile, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owarsam:</text:span></text:span> Pn., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subcustos</text:span>, ōdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Underwaktare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŭtis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hud, skinn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oafdraget):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på mennisko- l. djurkropp:</text:span> vulnus intra c-em, C.; ægra tumet, Ps.; tenuis; macies c-em adducit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hopsnörper);</text:span> diripere, Ov.; curare c-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fodra köttet),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. casiæ, uvæ, Pn.; tenuis c. elocutionis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fernissa),</text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cŭtīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med bibet. af ömtålighet, weklighet):</text:span> curare, Ps.; contracta, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intercus</text:span>, cŭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är emellan hud och skinn:</text:span> aqua, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rĕcŭtītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med huden upprifwen l. afskuren:</text:span> colla ruptæ mulæ, Mt.; Judæi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omskurne),</text:span> Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆ănē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆ănĕæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: =Symplegades, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klippöar i Bosporen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆ănus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blå saphir:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blåklint:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆ănĕus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mörkblå:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆ăthus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet öskärl, hwarmed winet hälldes ur</text:span> crater <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bålen) i</text:span> poculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bägaren); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(spetsglas):</text:span></text:span> Hor., Ter. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mått</text:span> = 1/12 sextarius: Col., Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆ăthisso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hälla i, slå upp:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆bæus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: c-a navis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆bæa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags transportskepp:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆bēbē <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆bĕlē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phrygisk gudinna</text:span> (Magna mater).<text:line-break/>Cy̆bĕlēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/>b.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆bĕlē <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.<text:line-break/></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆bēbus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Phrygien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆bĕlista, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cybeles prest:</text:span> Vg. Cop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆bistra, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Cataonien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆bĭum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">saltfisk:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆bĭŏsactes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saltfisk-säljare:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cyclas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dammantel:</text:span></text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cyclădātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klädd i</text:span> c.: Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yclădes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öar i Archipelagen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cyclĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: scriptor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som hör till den episke cykeln) cyklisk:</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yclops, ōpis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cyclop (enögd jätte):</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>Cyclōpĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cycnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cygnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> olor): moriuntur cum cantu et voluptate, C.; Dircæus c. (= Pindarus), Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cycnēus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swane-:</text:span></text:span> vox et oratio divini hominis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ydnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Cilicien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆dōnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Creta.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆don, ōnis,<text:line-break/>Cy̆dōnĭātes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i C.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆dōnĭus, <text:line-break/>Cy̆dōnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(cretisk).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cygn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cycnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆lindrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cylinder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. figur:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wals, trumla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed ngt jemnas l. utplattas:</text:span> æquare aream c-o, Vg. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ädelsten:</text:span> Juv., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yllărus <text:line-break/>(Cyllăros), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Castors häst.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yllēnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Arcadien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cyllēnĭus,<text:line-break/>Cyllēnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cyllenisk, arcadisk, Mercurius tillhörig, mercurisk.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cyllēnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳlon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cyllōnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cȳma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cȳma</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kålblad:</text:span></text:span> brassicæ frigoribus caules, vere cymata mittere, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cȳmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rik på</text:span> c.: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cȳmătĭle</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cūmătĭle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">damklädning af wattenblå färg:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cȳmătĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wåglikt stycke på jonisk colonncapitäl:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cymba</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cumba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Båt:</text:span></text:span> C., Ov., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cymbĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Båtformig bägare; lampa:</text:span></text:span> tepido spumantia c-a lacte, Vg.; Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cymbŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cymbălum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cymbal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bleckbäcken, hwarmed hölls musik, i det 2 och 2 slogos emot hwarandra; tillhörde mest den asiatiska</text:span> Magnæ Matris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cult):</text:span> C., Lucr., Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cymbălisso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slå cymbal:</text:span> Non.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cymbălista</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cymbălistrĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">musikant på c.:</text:span> Ap., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cymbium,<text:line-break/>Cymbula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cymba.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳmē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadsnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cȳmæus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cymosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cyma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆nægīrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆nĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (hundartad):</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har hundsjuka:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cynisk = som tillhör cyniska philosophien l. philosopherne:</text:span> institutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lära),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆nĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cynisk philosoph, cyniker:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆nĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: (cunice): potiusne in subsellio c. accipimur, quamde in lectis?, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆nŏcĕphălos,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hundhöfdad) ett slags apa:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆nŏsarges, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gymnasium i Athen.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆noscĕphălæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. ortsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆nŏsūra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hundswans), lille björnen, nordstjernan:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>Cy̆nŏsūris, idis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: ursa c. = c-a, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆nŏsūrus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: c-um ovum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">windelägg,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ynthus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg på Delos.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cynthĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.<text:line-break/></text:span>Cynthĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Apollo.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cynthĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Diana; äfwen qwinnonamn l. tillnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cyparissus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cupressus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Cypris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cypros.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳ̆prĭus vicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom på sluttningen af</text:span> Esquilinus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳ̆pros <text:line-break/>(Cȳ̆prus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Medelhafwet.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cȳ̆prĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cyprisk:</text:span> æs C-um = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">koppar.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Koppar-:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cȳ̆prĭcus,<text:line-break/>Cȳ̆prĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cȳ̆pris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym. = Venus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ypsĕlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳrēnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Cȳrēnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cyrene, grekisk coloni i Africa.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cȳrēnăĭcus,<text:line-break/>Cȳrēnæus,<text:line-break/>Cȳrēnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yrnos,<text:line-break/>Cyrnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Corsica.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cyrnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>ȳrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">persiskt personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cȳrēa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af C. uppförda byggnader:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆thēra, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekisk ö.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆thĕrēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆thĕrēis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Venus.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆thērĭăcus,<text:line-break/>Cy̆thĕrēĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt Venus helgad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆thēris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cy̆tĭsus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cy̆tĭsum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>y̆tōrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Paphlagonien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cy̆tōrĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">C</text:span>yzĭcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>Cyzĭcum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad wid Propontis.</text:span><text:line-break/>Cyzĭcēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom abbreviationstecken:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. = Decimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnamn).</text:span><text:line-break/>2. = 500.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T3">a. d.</text:span> = ante diem.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="T3">D. M.</text:span> = Diis Manibus.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="T3">D. D. D.</text:span> = dat, dicat, dedicat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>aae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ahae, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i inre Asien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dacia, -cicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dacus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dacty̆lus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dacty̆los), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: finger; deraf benämning på åtskilliga föremål efter deras form, serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dactyl,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> versfoten</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"> —⏑⏑:</text:span> C., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dacty̆lĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dactylisk:</text:span> numerus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dacty̆liŏthēca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för l. samling af ringar l. caméer:</text:span> Mt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ācus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> -i, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ācia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">östre delen af Ungern och Wallachiet samt westre delen af Moldau. -</text:span> Dācĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Geta).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ædăla, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fästning i Carien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dædalēus, -lĕus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Dædalus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ædălĭon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Dædălus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konstfärdig, -rik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (act. och pass.) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">konstrikt skapande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bildad, smyckad:</text:span></text:span> Circe; d-a tecta apum, Vg.; signa; carmina; d-a tellus summittit flores; natura rerum d-a, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ædălus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythisk konstnär.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dædălēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Icarus (D-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>Dædălĕus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dæmon,</text:span> ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ande, dæmon</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om Socrates’</text:span> Dæmonium): Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dæmŏnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dahæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Daæ.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>almătæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>almătia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Dalmatien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dalmătĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dāma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rå, dofhjort, -hind:</text:span></text:span> timidi; figere, Vg.; pavidæ, Hor.; d-as agitare, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ămălis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āmărātus <text:line-break/>(Dēmărātus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ămascus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Syrien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dămascēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ămăsippus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Damiurgus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Demiurgus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Damnum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af roten i</text:span> do?): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plikt, böter:</text:span></text:span> morte, exsilio, vinclis, d-o coërcere; d-o cogere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlust, afbräck:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: (eg. i oeconomiskt, men äfwen i andra hänseenden):</text:span> jactura et d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppoffring och förlust);</text:span> d. et detrimentum; d. facere in aliquā re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och blott</text:span> aliquā re; d. contrahere, perferre; magno d-o affici; d. dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillfoga)</text:span> alicui; d. sarcire, restituere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ersätta);</text:span> emptori d. præstare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(answara honom för, ersätta);</text:span> d-i infecti promittere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbinda sig att hålla skadeslös),</text:span> C.; ad paucos maximæ divitiæ, in rempublicam d-a atque dedecora pervenerunt; egestas facile habetur sine d-o, Sa.; d. apportare, Ter.; d. leve, gravius, reparabile; d. explere; d. pati <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fördraga),</text:span> L.; d. accipere, d-a caelestia reparant celeres lunæ, Hor.; d. ferre, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förlust i spel, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spelskuld:</text:span></text:span> d. aleatorium; d. dissolvere, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i krig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nederlag:</text:span></text:span> d. duarum cohortium, Cs.; d-a bello accepta; carpi d-is quotidie, L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = det som förlorats:</text:span> matrem circum sua d-a volantem corripuit serpens, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnĭfĭcus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnĭgĕrŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skadlig:</text:span></text:span> bestia, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pliktfälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om åklagaren: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">få pliktfälld), döma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till plikt, straff, præstation:</text:span> pecuniā; capitis, capite; octupli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till 8-faldig skadeersättning),</text:span> C.; poenæ capitalis; decem milibus æris; voti d-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förpligtad (af en bönhörande gud) till löftes fullgörande),</text:span> L.; Sisyphus d-tus longi laboris; d-tus dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till att gifwa),</text:span> Hor.; Orco (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Vg.; in opus, in metallum, Pn.; d-ri, ut -, T.; ad opus, ad metalla, ad bestias, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fälla, sakfälla, förklara för brottslig, skyldig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ett brott):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">juridiskt:</text:span> aut d. aut absolvere; judicio, sententiis judicum d-ri; lege aliqua, per arbitrum; furti, injuriarum, rei capitalis; de vi, de pecuniis repetundis; crimine aliquo; causā aliquā, C.; d-tum poenam sequi oportebat, ut igni cremaretur; ambitūs d., Cs.; lege Porcia exsilium d-tis permittitur, Sa.; sacrilegii, proditionis, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: förklara skyldig till, absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fördöma, förkasta:</text:span></text:span> aliquem stultitiæ; vitam alicujus, C.; libros suos jam editos, Qu.; aliquid in totum, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förderfwa:</text:span></text:span> Neptunus solet d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.: låta dem plikta?)</text:span> dites, pauperibus parcere, Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnātus</text:span>, tior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. quis te d-ior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mera kraftigt l. afgjordt förklarad brottslig)?,</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fördömlig:</text:span></text:span> Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fördömlig, -kastlig:</text:span></text:span> Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnās</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">indecl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmodligen af</text:span> damnatus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dömd, pligtig:</text:span></text:span> dare, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fällande, fördömelse:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fällande:</text:span></text:span> judicium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oeconomiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlustbringande, ruinerande, förstörande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ödslande, slösaktig:</text:span></text:span> homo, Ter., Pt.; res divitibus d-issima, L.; (discere, per quæ) crescere res posset, minui d-a libido; Venus, Hor.; alea parva nuces et non d-a videtur, Mt.; Nero non in alia re d-ior, quam in ædificando, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förderflig, förstörande, -tärande:</text:span></text:span> consuetudo minime famæ d.; discordia reipublicæ, L.; d-a quid non imminuit dies?, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ruinerad:</text:span></text:span> senex, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Damnōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förderfligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = till förlust för ngn, till ngns ruin:</text:span> bibere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condemno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pliktfälla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (få pliktfälld), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">döma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till straff, plikt o. s. w.):</text:span> denis milibus æris, L.; ad bestias, ad metalla, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">absol.:</text:span> hominem Veneri absolvit, sibi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sig till godo)</text:span> c-at, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fälla, (få fälld), sakfälla, förklara skyldig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">juridiskt:</text:span> vos, judices, a quibus c-tus sum; istum paucis horis - omnium sententiis c-vi; furti alqm; publicæ pecuniæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(underslef af -);</text:span> iisdem criminibus; de alea, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förklara skyldig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förkasta, ogilla:</text:span></text:span> alqm inertiæ; <text:soft-page-break/>temeritatem alicujus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condemnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fällande:</text:span></text:span> Asc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condemnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som fått ngn fälld, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åklagare:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indemnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Icke dömd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fälld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lagligen förwunnen:</text:span></text:span> cives i-i et incolumes, C.; i-um necare, Sa., Vell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indemnis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oskadd:</text:span></text:span> per ferrum et ignes i-em evadere, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prædamno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På förhand fälla, förklara skyldig; förkasta:</text:span></text:span> p-tum venire ad judicium; spes p-ta, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āmŏcles, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āmoetas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āmon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āmŏphĭlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ănăē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dănăēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> (heros = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Danae’s son, Perseus).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ănăus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dănăus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">argivisk, grekisk;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dănăi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Greker.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dănăĭdes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Danai döttrar, Danaiderna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>andărĭdæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">scythiskt folk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dandărĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deß land.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dănista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utlånare), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ockrare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dănistĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ockrare-:</text:span></text:span> genus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dăno,</text:span> ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(archaistiskt verbum</text:span> = Do): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gifwa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ānŭbius <text:line-break/>(Dānŭvius), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Donau (öfre delen; jfr</text:span> Ister).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dapalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Daps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Daphnē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lager:</text:span></text:span> Petr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. person- och stadsnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>aphnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Daphnon</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagerlund:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dăpīno,</text:span> 1.: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bekosta:</text:span></text:span> æternum tibi d-bo victum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Daps,</text:span> dăpis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offermåltid, offer:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg.</text:span> ”res divina, quæ fiebat aut hiberna sementi aut verna”, Fs.): d. Jovi assaria, Cato; facere, reddere Jovi d-em, Catl., Hor.; adhibiti ad ministerium d-emque Potitii et Pinarii, L.; Saliaribus d-bus ornare pulvinar deorum, Hor.; sollemnes d-es libabat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dödsoffer),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måltid, mat, rätter:</text:span></text:span> Siculæ; meusæ brevis; die ter mutatæ d-is spectaculum, Hor.; inemptæ; impositæ auro d-es; opimæ, Vg.; d-es Neronis, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dapālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Jupiter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt hwilken offras),</text:span> Cato; coena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kostlig),</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dapsĭlis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dapsĭlus, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Riklig, rik, kostsam:</text:span></text:span> dotes, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dapsĭle</text:span> (Su.),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dapsĭlĭter</text:span> (Non.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikligt.</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ardănus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. konung i Troja.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dardănus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trojansk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dardănĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Dardanien (Troja).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dardănĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Dardănis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym. (Trojan, Trojanska).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dardănĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trojansk).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ăres, ētis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ārēus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ārīus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">persiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>assarēsii, ōrum, <text:line-break/>Dassarētæ, ārum, <text:line-break/>Dassarenses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslagsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>atămes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">asiatiskt namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Datarius, -tatim, Datio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Do.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ātis, ĭdis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> Datim), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">persiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dativus, Dato, -tor, -tum, -tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Do.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>aulis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phocis.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Daulĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är ifrån Daulis.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Daulĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>aunĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Apulien (Apulien).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Daunius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>aunus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>āvus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slafnamn (eg.</text:span> = Dacus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dē,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedifrån; nerifrån:</text:span></text:span> dejectus quî potest esse, nisi in inferiorem locum de superiore missus?; de manibus deponere aliquid, C.; de muro jacere, Cs.; stella de caelo lapsa; de imo pectore ducere suspiria, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Från, ut ifrån, af:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utmärkande ett utgående från ett rum, ett håll, skiljande ifrån (i yttre och inre men.):</text:span> de finibus suis exire, Cs.; de vita excedere; de tribunali pronunciare, C.; de castris procedere, Sa.; gemmæ se trudunt de cortice, Vg.; de officio, de jure decedere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utmärkande ett tagande, hemtande, wäljande ifrån en massa l. ett antal o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af, ifrån:</text:span></text:span> de meo facit sumptum, Ter.; de suo coenat, Pt.; de publico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på det offentligas bekostnad)</text:span> est elatus, L.; partem sumere de solido die, Hor.; de classe legit geminas biremes; hausit lymphas de gurgite, Vg.; de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i)</text:span> consuetudine mutavit nihil, N.; res de medio sumptæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utmärkande hem, wistelseort, klaß, härkomst, det tillstånd, hwarifrån ngn öfwergår till ett annat; ämne: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Från, af:</text:span></text:span> homo de schola; de circo astrologus; accusator de plebe; de templo fit carcer; quid de me, de illo fiet?, C.; Volsca de gente Camilla; myrtus de solido robore; Aeneadasque meo nomen de nomine fingo, Vg.; de <text:soft-page-break/>nihilo nihil gignitur, Ps.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i partitiv men.:</text:span> quivis de iis; unus de nobis, C.; pauci de nostris cadunt, Cs.; de servis, quem habuit fidelissimum, misit, N.; de spinis pluribus una, Hor. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(taga, få höra, fråga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> emere, quærere, discere, audire de aliquo; bene, male mereri de aliquo, C.; supplicium sumere de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på)</text:span> aliquo, N.; rapiamus, amici, occasionem de die, Hor.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ifrån, alltifrån:</text:span></text:span> somnus de prandio, Pt.; statim de auctione venire, C.; diem de die <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dag från dag)</text:span> ducere, L.; incestos amores de tenui ungui meditari, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (inträdet af), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynnerhet wid verba, som uttrycka en rörelse, i det tiden fattas såsom utgångspunkt):</text:span> de nocte venit, vigilat; de nocte, media nocte, multa de nocte facere aliquid, C.; de tertia vigilia profectus est; de media nocte misit, Cs.; ut jugulent homines, surgunt de nocte latrones, Hor. <text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utmärkande orsak, grund: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af, öfwer:</text:span></text:span> de nihilo irasci, Pt.; flere de amici morte; gravi de causa, C.; qua de causa, Cs., Sa.; de rapto fratre dolens, Hor.; fessus de æstu maris, Gell.<text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(norm, sätt): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enligt, efter, på:</text:span></text:span> de consilii sententia; de improviso; de integro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på nytt);</text:span> de occulto; de insidiis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. från bakhåll)</text:span> agere, C.; de novo, L.; de more, Vg.; de sententia legati sta - tuunt tempus, quo - ferro invadant, T. <text:line-break/>V. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Om, angående, rörande, i fråga om, med afseende på:</text:span></text:span> de immortalitate animi disserere, exponere, disputare, explicare; hi de philosophia libri; desperare de re; de artificiis et quæstibus, qui liberales, qui sordidi habendi sint, hæc fere accepimus; de vi accusare; Regulus missus est Romam de captivis commutandis; de captivis redimendis impetrare, C.; de stipendio recusare; de numero dierum fidem servant, Cs.; de pace legatos mittere, Cs., L.; spes de re, Cs.; conscientia de culpa; referre ad senatum, consulere senatum de aliquo, Sa.; de aliquo arbitria facere, Hor.<text:line-break/>VI. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammansät</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ningar:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ned:</text:span></text:span> dejicio.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Från, bort:</text:span></text:span> decedo, desisto, demo.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upphäfwande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">o-, miß-, wan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> desuesco, despero, dedecet.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ut-, för-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afgörande; ytterlighet):</text:span> decerto, debello, defleo, depereo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deus.<text:line-break/>Deartuo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Artus (us).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deascio</text:span>, 1.: (ascia): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afyxa, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillyxa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lura, drifwa gäck med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēbeo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 2.: (de-habeo?):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förblifwa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skyldig, hafwa, stå i skuld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">böra gifwa, betala</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bewisa) ngn ngt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillkomma, wara hemfallen åt, böra gifwas</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ngn har att fordra, fordran på ngt; man</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jag, du) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">är ngn ngt skyldig):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">absol.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om yttre skuld:</text:span> nihil unquam debuit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hade ingen skuld);</text:span> quod debuit, nondum solvit; ii, qui debent, quibus d-etur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gäldenärer, borgenärer),</text:span> C.; fateri se d-re, Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">relativt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i widsträcktaste betydelse):</text:span> huic pecuniam debet, C.; d. <text:soft-page-break/>grandem pecuniam; gratiam d. alicui, Sa.; navis Virgilium finibus Atticis; ventis ludibrium d-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(du är skyldig</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjelf dömd att bli en lekboll),</text:span> Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: quid tibi hic d-etur [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwad har du här att fordra (göra</text:span>)]<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">?,</text:span> Pt.<text:span text:style-name="T2">;</text:span> legioni frumentum d-batur, Cs.; præsidia vitæ d-entur iis maxime; sunt officia, quæ aliis magis, quam aliis d-antur; tibi misericordia nulla d-etur; sua cuique laus, poena facinoribus, supplicium hostibus d-etur; oratio juventuti d-ri jam non potest (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jag kan ej längre fortfara att wara skyldig);</text:span> d-ri (a me) hoc tantis ingeniis putavi, ut memoriam eorum immortalem redderem, C.; morti d-tus destinatusque; d-batur fatis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ödet fordrade)</text:span> tantæ origo urbis, L.; d-emur morti nos nostraque, Hor.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara ngn förbunden; hafwa ngn att tacka för ngt:</text:span></text:span> bonis omnibus debeo; non minus tibi respublica d-et, quam tu reipublicæ; Q. Mucio summum beneficium d-ui, quod statim consilium dimisit, C.; alicui plurimum pro beneficio, Cs.; alicui, Sa.; multum virtuti, plus fortunæ, Ct.; rei inventio ei d-etur, Pn.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara pligtig, böra</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om det moraliskt rätta l. blott tillbörliga, logiskt nödwändiga (måste, kan ej annat än</text:span> -)]: d-emus naturam ducem sequi; deserunt, quos tueri d-ent; non d-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hade bort)</text:span> frumentarius celare Rhodios; hoc eo mirabilius videri d-et, C.; d-re se suspicari, Cæsarem sui opprimendi causa exercitum habere, Cs.; - jam nunc dicat jam nunc d-entia dici; d-es hoc etiam rescribere, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det man är skyldig l. har att fordra), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skyldig, tillbörlig, wederbörlig:</text:span></text:span> solvere d-am pecuniam alicui; honores alicui decernere d-os; referre gratiam meritam et d-am; solvere poenas justas et d-as; fungi officio d-o, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skuld:</text:span></text:span> solvere, remittere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efterskänka),</text:span> C.; exigere, Sen.; naturæ d. reddere, N. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det att wara skyldig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skuld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> dissimilis est pecuniæ d. et gratiæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gäldenär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som är förbunden till l. för ngt):</text:span> condonare d-bus creditas pecunias; appellare d-em de pecunia, C.; æris, Hor.; ingratus, Pn.; vitæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indēbĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som man ej har att fordra, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej tillkommande:</text:span></text:span> non i-a posco regna meis fatis, Vg.; præmia, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēbĭlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (de-habilis? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> habilis): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till tjenst kroppsligen oskicklig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanför, orkeslös, lytt, ofärdig, lam:</text:span></text:span> homo claudus, cæcus, d., Pt; omnibus membris captus ac d.; senex imbecillus ac d., C.; miles, L.; equus, Pn.; membra metu, Ter.; humero, lumbis d., Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlamad, ofärdig, wanmäktig:</text:span></text:span> conjurati sine Catilina infirmi ac d.; præfectura manca et d.; ingenio d., T.; utraque res sine altera d., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanförhet, lamhet, ofärdighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> integritas); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(andlig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">swaghet:</text:span></text:span> dolores, morbi, d-es; linguæ d., C.; subita d., L.; animi d., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: Pac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭlĭto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra wanför, lytt, förlama:</text:span></text:span> membra fustibus; ferro; terrore; vox fletu d-ta, C.; L millia hominum d-ta sunt, T.; lingua d-ta, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlama, krossa, förkrossa, bryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kraft, anfall):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om materiella object:</text:span> oppositis pumicibus d-atur mare, Hor.; nulla est vis, quæ non ferro et virtute d-ri possit, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer l. abstracta object:</text:span> me d-tum metu vidit; animi d-antur et franguntur; spem, furores alicujus reprimere et d.; Drusi tribunatus d-ri jam et frangi videbatur; dolor magnitudinem animi se d-rum minatur; audaciam alicujus; veritas d-ta, C.; opes Lacedæmoniorum, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēbĭlĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: animi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förkrosselse),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subdēbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lam:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subdēbĭlĭtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Modlös:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Debit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Debeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcastȳlus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har tio colonner i fron</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decaulesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Caulis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ĕcĕlēa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dĕcĕlīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. ortsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcem,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Nom. Num. indecl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tio.</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sammansättn.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-dĕcim</text:span>: Undecim, Duodecim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w. se</text:span> Unus, Duo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcember</text:span>, bris, bre, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tionde = tionde månaden, då Mars war den förste):</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcember</text:span>, bris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">December, julmånad:</text:span></text:span> mensis D.; Nonæ, Idus, Calendæ D-es, Varr., C., L.; libertate uti D-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Saturnaliernas);</text:span> hic tertius D., ex quo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tredje wintern) -,</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decemjugis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcempĕda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (pes): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mätstång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af 10 fots längd:</text:span> C., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcempĕdātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Landtmätare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcemplex</text:span>, ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tiofaldig:</text:span></text:span> N. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcemplĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decemprimi, -remis, -scalmus, -vir (-viralis, -viratus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Primus, Remus, Scalmus, Vir.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcies</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dĕciens), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tio gånger:</text:span></text:span> d. anno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om året),</text:span> Pn.; d. centena millia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. ensamt</text:span> d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en million,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tionde, den tionde:</text:span></text:span> pars, hora, C.; d. = decumanus, e., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för tionde gången:</text:span> L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭma</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tionde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. offer åt ngn gud l. afgift till staten):</text:span> d-am vovere deo, Varr.; Orestis prandia in semitis decumæ nomine; vini, olei, frugum; plus d-ā auferri ab aratore non potest; singulæ, tres, ternæ decumæ; exigere, accipere, vendere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bortarrendera),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmānus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭmānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör tionde (legionen):</text:span> miles, T.<text:line-break/>b. porta d-na = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bakporten i ett romerskt läger (mots.</text:span> prætoria): L., T.<text:line-break/>c. limes d-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> cardo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">från wester till öster dragen gränslinie wid jordmätning:</text:span> Col., Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tionde-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som gifwes i tionde l. hwaraf tionde gifwes:</text:span> frumentum; ager, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ofantligt stor:</text:span></text:span> acipenser, Luc. ap. C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmāna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tiondeförpaktare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som af staten arrenderade och af</text:span> aratores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spec. på Sicilien) uppbar tionde af</text:span> ager decumanus; [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med allmännare benämningar:</text:span> redemptor, publicanus (C. Verr. III. 10 ff.)]: utrum æquius est d-um petere, an aratorem repetere?; quantum d. edidisset -, tantum arator dare cogebatur; d-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> publicana) mulier, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmo</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭmo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">taga tionde:</text:span> Fs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttaga hwar tionde soldat till dödsstraff:</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcĭmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afdelning af tio, tiomanna-collegium, -nämnd; afdelning, samfund af tio</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ryttare, senatorer, domare,</text:span> scribæ, lictores): C., L., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭrio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anförare för en</text:span> decuria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ryttare l. tjenstemän:</text:span> Varr., Su. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senator, rådman</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i municipier och colonier:</text:span> C., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭriōnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">decurions-beställning wid rytteriet:</text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Senatorsembete</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i coloni l. municipium):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭrio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indela i decurier l. i allm. flockar (eg. och oeg.):</text:span> equites, L.; tribules <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för röstwärfning),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭriātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŭriātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indelning:</text:span> tribulium, C.; equitum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēni</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Distrib.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tio för hwar, tio och tio:</text:span></text:span> armigeri, Ct.; bis d. anni, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> = decimus: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utgör, håller tio:</text:span> numerus, Vitr.; fistula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tio fots-),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett silfwermynt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Denarius</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (10 l. 16 aß = 4 sestertier):</text:span> emit d-o, quod est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är wärdt)</text:span> mille d-ium, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">guldmynt (= 25 silfwerdenarier):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wigt</text:span> = drachma: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decenn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Annus.<text:line-break/>Decens, -center, -centia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decet.<text:line-break/>Deceptor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decipio, Capio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcēris,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skepp med tio årrader:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Decermen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decerpo, Carpo. <text:line-break/>Decert . . ., Decess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cerno, Cedo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcet</text:span>, uit, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anstå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om opersonligt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">nomen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom subject; med obj. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Ter. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om drägt och yttre utstyrsel: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kläda, passa, anstå:</text:span></text:span> vestis alicui; ut te et ingenio (tuo) d-uit, Asin. III. 2. 31; arta d-et sanum comitem toga, Hor.; sparsis (eam) d-et esse capillis, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara anständigt; höfwas, böra:</text:span></text:span> quod honestum est, d-et, et quod d., honestum est; prætorem d-et manus abstinentes habere; ratione et oratione uti prudenter d-et; oratorem irasci minime d., C.; quæ ab imperatore d-rint, omnia provisa esse; omnes homines summa cura niti d-et, ut - -, Sa.; candida pax homines, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (æsthetiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">passande, wara öfwerensstämmande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ngns character), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anstå:</text:span></text:span> caput est artis d-re; tum illud, quod d-et, servare poētas dicimus, quum ea, quæ personæ conveniunt, et dicuntur et fiunt; velle experiri, quam se aliena d-eant; nihil d. invitā Minervā, C.; parvum parva d-ent, Hor.; perge, d-et (te pergere), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som kläder wäl), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Full af behag; skön:</text:span></text:span> Venus, Hor.; forma, facies, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Passande, höfwisk:</text:span></text:span> quid verum atque d., curo et rogo, Hor.; reverentia, Ov.; poena d-ior, Sen.; habitus, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med behag:</text:span></text:span> lasciva d-ius ætas, Hor.; lacrimare, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På passande sätt, med smak; riktigt:</text:span></text:span> talia verba pudoris gratia d. subtrahuntur, Qu.; jura d-issime (= elegantissime) descripta, C.; singula quæque locum teneant sortita d., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prydlig form:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Behag, skönhet, fägring:</text:span></text:span> divini d-is signa, Vg.; juventa et d., Hor.; virgineus; tener corporis, Sen.; virtutem spoliare suo d-e, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det passande, characteristiska, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Character:</text:span></text:span> mobilibus annis et naturis dare d-em, Hor.; in personis servare d-em, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcor</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">passande:</text:span> Næv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som kläder wäl l. är klädd, prydd med), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prydlig, skön, prydd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> forma, C.; arma, facies, Sa.; cæsaries; auro d-us, Vg.; Medi pharetrā d-i; nigro crine d-us, Hor.; facundiā, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Passande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. l. i moralisk mening = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anständig, höfwisk, wacker, hederlig:</text:span></text:span> facinora neque te neque tuis virtutibus d-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(constr.</text:span> = dignus), Pt. Mil. gl. 618. Aul. II. 2. 43; d-um est, quod ita naturæ consentaneum est, ut in eo moderatio et temperantia appareat cum specie liberali; omnia justa d-a; id viro dignum et d-um; valde est d-um, principum domos patere hospitibus, C.; dulce et d-um est pro patria mori, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Passande, lämplig:</text:span></text:span> harum rerum disputatio principibus (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) civitatis non d-a videtur; color albus præcipue d. deo est, C.; magis d-a fabulis, quam incorruptis rerum monumentis; ordo ex <text:soft-page-break/>censu et bello et paci d-us, L.; temporibus Augusti dicendis non defuere d-a ingenia, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcōrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det passande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i sedlig men. och = det characteristiska:</text:span> C. (de Off. 1. 27).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcōre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På anständigt, på passande sätt, hederligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ära):</text:span> corporis partes aspiciuntur non d.; si non d., at non indecore facere aliquid, C.; res publica bene ac d. gesta, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">D<text:span text:style-name="T1">ĕcus</text:span>, cŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prydnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skönhet):</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre (concret och abstract) men.:</text:span> d-a et ornamenta fanorum, C.; columnas rupibus excidunt, scenis d-a alta futuris; manus ebori addunt d.; divinum, Vg.; Phoebus et Diana lucidum caeli d., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Heder:</text:span></text:span> Cn. Pompeius imperii Romani lumen ac d.; ingenium est decus hominis, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det passande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sedlig l. blott conventionel men.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anständighet, heder, ära, wärdighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i enskilda och offentliga hänseenden):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstract:</text:span> animos attentos habere ad d-is conservationem; honestas et d.; labentem populum ad d. excitare; verum d. in virtute positum est; est magistratus civitatis dignitatem et d. sustinere, C.; ei cariora semper omnia, quam d. atque pudicitia fuit; d-i esse alicui; potentiæ paucorum d. atque libertatem suam gratificari; Jugurtha contra d. regium miserabili cultu Romam venit, Sa.; oblitus d-risque sui sociûmque salutis; proprium d. tenere, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hederlig, ärofull handling; hedersbragd:</text:span></text:span> belli d-a, L.; tanti d-is testis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pryda, smycka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.:</text:span> oppidum monumentis, C.; nostris (regiis) insignibus d-tus incedit consul, L.; corpus, Qu.; templa, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> delubra deorum pietate; domos suas gloriā, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hedra:</text:span></text:span> populari gloriā; amplissimis honoribus et præmiis, C.; nemo me lacrimis d-et, Enn. ap. C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dĕcŏrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prydnad:</text:span></text:span> Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Addĕcet</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condĕcet</text:span>, 2. = Decet: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condĕcŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pryda:</text:span></text:span> ludos scenicos, Ter.; loca picturis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēdĕcet</text:span>, uit (ui, St.), 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illa kläda, wanpryda; illa anstå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i yttre och inre men.; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wara opassande; göra skam:</text:span></text:span> eam non d-uit ferre pedem choro, Hor.; comæ eam non d-uere, Ov.; oratorem simulare non d-t; illud assequi possunt, ut ne d-eat; si quid d-eat in illis, vitemus ipsi, C.; imagines Claudiorum Atticus d-re videbatur, T.; non d-ui tua jussa, S<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēdĕcor</text:span>, ŏris (Sa.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēdĕcōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Opassande, skamlig:</text:span></text:span> barbaris, T.; vita, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēdĕcus</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(moralisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanheder, -ära, skam:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., abstract men.:</text:span> se fugere sine suo d-e non posse; senectus concipit<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ådrager sig)</text:span> d.; judicia operta d-e et infamiā; sumptus effusi cum probro et d-e; flagitii et d-is plenum factum; domino d-i fit ampla domus, si est in ea solitudo; majorum gloriæ d-i esse, C.; <text:soft-page-break/>vitam per d. amittere, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret.</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanärande handling, skambragd:</text:span></text:span> admittere d., C., Cs.; nullo d-e abstinere; in d-a incurrere, C.; decemviris d-a militiæ objiciebantur, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande warelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skamfläck:</text:span></text:span> naturæ d., Phdr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēdĕcŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanhedra, utskämma, fläcka:</text:span></text:span> te et me et familiam d-as, Ter.; inanem (Athenis te) redire turpissimum est, d-tem auctoritatem et urbis et magistri, C.; se flagitiis, Sa.; utcunque defecere mores, d-ant bene nata culpæ; non te d-ant poētæ tui Varius Virgiliusque, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcet</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanpryda:</text:span></text:span> juvenes confusa adhuc quædam non i-ent, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ohöfwisk:</text:span></text:span> Qu., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcenter</text:span>, -issime, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ohöfwiskt:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oanständighet:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcor</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanhedrande; som gör ngn skam:</text:span></text:span> vita, Acc.; non erimus regno indecores, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som icke kläder), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ful:</text:span></text:span> forma (Livillæ), T.; gestus, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ohöfwisk, oanständig:</text:span></text:span> injusta omnia ut turpia, sic i-a, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om personer) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ärelös, utskämd, utan anseende:</text:span></text:span> i. et humilis precario præfuit, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕcōre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På ett opassande, förwändt sätt:</text:span></text:span> facere aliquid, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Perdĕcōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Serdeles prydlig:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decianus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decius.<text:line-break/>Decīdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cædo. <text:line-break/>Decĭdo, -ciduus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cado.<text:line-break/>Decies (-ens), Decim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ĕcĭmus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. förnamn</text:span> (D.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decip . . ., Decisio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Capio, Caedo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ĕcius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dĕciānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Decoct . . ., Decollo, Decolo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Coquo, Collum, Colum.<text:line-break/>Decor, -cŏramen, -cōre, -cŏro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decet.<text:line-break/>Decortic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cortex. <text:line-break/>Decōrus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decet.<text:line-break/>Decrementum, Decrepitus, Decret . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cresco, Crepo, Cerno. <text:line-break/>Decumbo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo.<text:line-break/>Decum . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för öfrigt och</text:span> Decuri . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decem.<text:line-break/>Decurs . . ., Decurtatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Curro, Curtus.<text:line-break/>Decus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decet.<text:line-break/>Decussatim, -cussatio, -cussis, -cusso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> As.<text:line-break/>Decutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quatio. <text:line-break/>Dedec . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decet.<text:line-break/>Dedit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dedo, Do. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Defæco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fæx.<text:line-break/>Defect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deficio, Facio.<text:line-break/>Defens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Defendo, Fendo. <text:line-break/>Defetigo, Defetiscor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fatim.<text:line-break/>Deficio, Definit . . ., Deflex . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facio, Finis, Flecto. <text:line-break/>Deflu . . ., Deform . . ., Defringo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fluo, Forma, Frango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēfrŭtum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inkokt win, must:</text:span></text:span> facere, Varr., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēfrŭtārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: vas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kärl, hwari</text:span> d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förwaras),</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēfrŭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inkoka:</text:span></text:span> vinum, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Defunct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fungor.<text:line-break/>Degener <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Genus.<text:line-break/>Dego <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ago.<text:line-break/>Degredior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior.<text:line-break/>Dehinc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hinc, Hic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēĭănīra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēĭdămīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Deject . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dejicio, Jacio.<text:line-break/>Dejero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juro, Jus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dein</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">Deinde,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos poeter läses</text:span> dejn, dejnde <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en- och twåstafwigt); af</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och stammen i</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwaraf</text:span> in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> inde; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Exin, Exinde, Proin, Proinde, Perinde; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förhålla</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det mellan formerna är owißt, liksom det emellan</text:span> In <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Inde; dein et exin pro deinde et exinde dicimus, C.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rumsförhållande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dernäst, derefter:</text:span></text:span> via, d. campus, L.; Leptis, d. Philænon aræ, Sa. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tids-förhållande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Derefter, sedan, derpå, sedermera:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> agit hoc, d. illud, Ter.; quas ad te d. literas mittimus; primo inter nos pauca de literis, d. Torquatus: - inquit -; primum agit gratias, d. -; quum accidisset, ut alter alterum videremus, surrexit statim. D. prima illa, quæ in congressu solemus, (locuti sumus), C.; profugit in provinciam, ac d. Romam contendit; alia, d. alia loca petivit; cum parte equitatus in solitudines, dein Thalam pervenit; d., ubi Jugurtha respondere jussus est, C. Bæbius eum tacere jubet, Sa.; Cæsar primum suo, d. omnium ex conspectu remotis equis - proelium commisit; primum equestre proelium commiserunt, d. pedestres copias ostenderunt, Cs.; primum Corcyræos fregit, d. - mare tutum reddidit, N.; obstipuit primo adspectu Sidonia Dido, casu d. viri tanto, Vg.; primo prudentes, dein vulgum, diutissime provincias fefellit, T.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alltsedan; hädanefter:</text:span></text:span> sic d., quicunque alius transsiliet mea moenia -; obversatur animo patriæ futura ea d. fortuna, quam ipsi fecissent; nulla d. impudica Lucretiæ exemplo vivet, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttryckande ordning i wigt och betydelse l. af indelningsmoment, grunder o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Derefter, -näst; widare, för det andra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (t. ex.</text:span> primum - d. - tum - postremo -): prima societas est in conjugio, proxima in liberis, d. una domus, communia omnia; primum de genere belli, d. de magnitudine, tum de imperatore deligendo dicendum est, C.; conjurandi has esse causas (inveniebat), primum quod vererentur, ne ad eos exercitus noster ad duceretur, d. quod -, <text:soft-page-break/>Cs.<text:line-break/>4. = Proinde: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Derefter,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i proportion, förhållande derefter:</text:span> deinde ex censu additus honos, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deinceps</text:span> (dein <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och roten i</text:span> capio; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> princeps):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> -cĭpis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> -cĭpĭtis: Paul. Diac., Ap.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I rad efter hwarandra, dernäst, derefter:</text:span></text:span> arbores d. constitutæ, Varr.; prima Cyrene est, d. duæ Syrtes, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tidsförhållande:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I följd, efter hwarandra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hwartannat,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den ene efter den andre); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">näst efter, derefter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i ordningen):</text:span> mos fuit, ut d., qui accubarent, canerent ad tibiam clarorum virorum laudes; reliqua d. persequamur; d., ut erat propositum, de beneficentia dicatur, C.; alios alii d. excipiebant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(aflöste);</text:span> reliquis d. diebus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under de närmaste dagarne),</text:span> Cs.; duo d. reges, alius aliā viā, civitatem auxerunt; intuemini horum d. annorum vel secundas res vel adversas, L.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sedermera, derefter, alltsedan:</text:span></text:span> res d. multæ consecutæ sunt, L.; d. (post bellum Mutinense) nec in senatu nec ad populum locutus est, nisi meditata oratione, Su.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttryckande ordning i wigt och wärde: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Efter hwarandra:</text:span></text:span> prima officia diis, secunda patriæ, tertia d. gradatim reliquis debentur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēīŏnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym. (Deione’s son = Apollo).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēĭŏpēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēĭphŏbē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Dēĭphŏbus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ejŏtărus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Delatio, -lator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Defero, Fero. <text:line-break/>Delebilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deleo.<text:line-break/>Delectabilis, -tamentum, -tatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delecto, Lacio.<text:line-break/>Delectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deligo, Lĕgo.<text:line-break/>Delen . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lenis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēleo,</text:span> ēvi, ētum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> lino, lēvi?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utstryka, utplåna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> jam scripseram: d-re nolui; epistolam lacrimis, C.; d-re licebit, quod non edideris, Hor.; in ceris facillima ratio est d-ndi, Qu. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. och bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplåna, utrota, tillintetgöra, omöjliggöra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om städer) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förstöra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om härar) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nedgöra, förgöra:</text:span></text:span> maculam bello susceptam; infamiam; memoriam rei ex animis; hæc epistola omnem mihi molestiam ex animo d-vit; id oblivio d-vit; bella non solum præsentia, verum etiam futura Scipio d-vit; Magna Græcia olim floruit, nunc d-ta est; in patria funditus d-da occupati sunt; hostium copias, exercitum; plures homines d-ti sunt hominum impetu, quam omni reliqua calamitate; omnia morte d-entur, C.; turpitudinem fugæ virtute; hostem; equitatum; urbem, Cs.; Numantiam; Carthaginem, Sa.; uon si quid olim lusit Anacreon, d-vit ætas, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēlēbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplånlig:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēlētĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: spongia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utplånande):</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēlētio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedgörande:</text:span></text:span> Lucil. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēlētrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: sica hujus imperii paene d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= som så när beredt rikets undergång),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indēlēbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Outplånlig, oförgänglig:</text:span></text:span> nomen; decus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Delet . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deleo.<text:line-break/>Deliacus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delos. <text:line-break/>Deliberabundus, Deliberat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delibero, Libra.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlībūtus</text:span> (delibuo, ui, Sol., Ter.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smord, bestruken:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> capillus compositus et d.; medicamentis propter dolorem articulorum, C.; coeno, Pt.; cruore, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Betagen, full</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af:</text:span> gaudio, Ter.; perjuriis, Sa. (inc.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Delicate, -catus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacio.<text:line-break/>Delicia = Deliquia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liqueo.<text:line-break/>Deliciæ, -ciolæ, -ciolum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delicio, Lacio.<text:line-break/>Delico = Deliquo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liqueo.<text:line-break/>Delictum, -licuus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delinquo, Linquo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dēlĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lac?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afwand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från modersmjölken):</text:span> porci; oves, Cato, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Deligo, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕgo.<text:line-break/>Delīni . . . = Deleni . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lenis.<text:line-break/>Deliquia, -liquo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liqueo.<text:line-break/>Deliquium, -liquus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linquo. <text:line-break/>Delir . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lira.<text:line-break/>Delitesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lateo. <text:line-break/>Delius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēlos <text:line-break/>(Dēlus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Archipelagen.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēlĭăcus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēlĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>elphi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phocis (med Apollos orakel) och deß inwånare (Delpher).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Delphĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>Delphicus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den delphiske guden, Apollo:</text:span> N. <text:line-break/><text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/>Delphĭce, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på delphiskt sätt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Delphin,</text:span> īnis (Ov., Vg.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Delphīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Delphin, tumlare, marswin:</text:span></text:span> ludunt in undis d-es, Ov.; d-um silvis appingere, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wigter eller lod i en wattenorgel,</text:span> d-i ærei, Vitr.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>elta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">indecl. def. n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Delta:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bokstafwen D.</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landbildning wid Nilens utlopp.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>eltōton, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en stjernbild (Triangeln):</text:span> C. Arat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlūbrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> deluo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">reningsort?): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tempel, helgedom:</text:span></text:span> d-a consecrata religionibus; certamen pro deorum templis et d-is; ex d-is <text:soft-page-break/>religiosissimis simulacra tollere; Musarum d-a colere, C.; d-a adeunt pacemque per aras exposcunt; altum d-i culmen, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Delumbis, -bo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lumbus.<text:line-break/>Delus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delos.<text:line-break/>Demaratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Damaratus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēmarchus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">embetsman i grekiska städer, motsw.</text:span> tribunus plebis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom:</text:span> Pt., Sp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Demensio, -mensus, -mensum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Metior. <text:line-break/>Dement . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Demens, Mens. <text:line-break/>Demers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Demergo, Mergo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmētrĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēmētrĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Dēmētrĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ortsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Demiss . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Demitto, Mitto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēmiurgus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dāmiurgus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">högste embetsmannen i wissa grekiska samhällen:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Demo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Emo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏchăres, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏcrĭtus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn (philosoph).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēmŏcrĭtēus, <text:line-break/>Dēmŏcrĭtīus, <text:line-break/>Dēmŏcrĭtĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏdŏcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏlĕon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏlĕos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏphĭlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmŏphŏon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēmosthĕnes, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēmosthĕnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Demptio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Demo, Emo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēmum,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">præp.</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom</text:span> summus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> sup-(er)?; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.:</text:span> Demus, Fs.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Först</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">först (icke förr än) på en wiß tid, ett wißt rum, under ett wißt wilkor, med en wiß beskaffenhet - sål.):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid tidsbestämninga</text:span>r, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med adverb, substantiv l. satser:</text:span> nunc d. intelligo, Pt., Ter.; novus maritus LXV:mo d. anno fio, Ter.; nunc d. literis tuis rescribo, C.; tum d. - compertum est, in bello plurimum ingenium posse, Sa.; tum d. Liscus oratione Cæsaris adductus, quod ante tacuerat, proponit, Cs.; tum d. impulsi Latini, L.; his d. exactis -, Vg.; nox d. legiones pugnæ exemit, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid rumsbestämningar:</text:span> me - fortuna - hac d. voluit consistere terrā, Vg.; ea d. animo naturalis est sedes, quum ad sui simile penetravit, C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid uttryck för wilkor:</text:span> quod si convenerit, tum d. decebit, C.; ita d. mihi satisfacies, Qu.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid determinativa och demonstrativa pronomina: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Först</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blott) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">den, han, en sådan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> ea d. magna res est; ea sunt d. non <text:soft-page-break/>ferenda in mendacio, quæ ne fieri quidem potuisse cernimus, C.; is d. mihi vivere et frui animā videtur; idem velle atque idem nolle, ea d. vera amicitia est, Sa.; id d. compar connubium fore (dicebant), L.; illa seges demum votis respondet avari agricolæ, bis quæ solem, bis frigora sensit, Vg.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos silfwerålderns förff. i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blott, endast:</text:span></text:span> hoc nomen bonis d. tribui volunt; non est superstitiose cogitatis d. inhærendum, Qu.; nobis utilitas d. spectanda est, Pn.<text:line-break/>6. ut d. = ut primum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så snart):</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Denarius, Deni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Decem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēnĭcālis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> neco?; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span> denecalis): feriæ d-es = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dödsfest,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēnĭque,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slutligen, till sist, till slut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (införande det, som sker sist af flera ting, l. uti en utweckling det sista momentet, skälet, alternativet):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan bibetydelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slutligen, till sist:</text:span></text:span> d. (post Thucydidem, Herodotum, ceteros) a philosophia profectus Xenophon scripsit historiam; d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter flera skäl för wänskapens wärde)</text:span> ceteræ res opportunæ sunt singulæ fere rebus singulis: amicitia plurimas res continet -; oratio tripertita fuit: (primum -, tum -,) d. ipse pro mea vos salute rogavit, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Till slut:</text:span></text:span> multum diei processerat, quum etiamtum eventus in incerto erat. D. Metellus, ubi videt Numidas minus instare, paulatim milites in unum conducit, Sa.; lubet experiri, quo evasurus est d., Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibetydelse af stegring, der det sista framhålles såsom högre, wigtigare (eller twärtom) eller mera owäntadt, än de föregående händelserna eller momenten:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Till sist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till råga på allt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till och med), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nej</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (icke ens), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i bästa, sämsta fall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> ii d., qui omni tempore in præda et in sanguine versabantur, S. Roscio temporis illius acerbitatem - objicient!; tantus dolor oculis, vultu, gestu, digito d. isto tuo significari solet; non solum sententias, sed etiam verba, - vultus d. omnes perspiciamus; non otium, non voluptas, non d. somnus; ubi erant? d. ubi sunt?, C.; (ille) perditus. Risu emoriri omnes (qui audiebant). D. metuebant me, Ter.; quid misero mihi d. restat?, Vg.; vitavi d. culpam, non laudem merui, Hor.; Campaniæ pulcherrima plaga est: - d. bis vernat, Fl. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åtminstone:</text:span></text:span> Galli nostros præsidia deducturos aut d. indiligentius servaturos crediderant, Cs.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sammanfattande de förut nämnda momenten och alla af samma slag l. till samma sak hörande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med ett ord, öfwerhufwud:</text:span></text:span> fodere aut arare aut aliquid ferre d., Ter.; d. nullum potest esse orationis genus, quod sit exceptum; (dicendum est), quid liberaliter, quid fortiter, quid d. cum aliqua virtute fecerit is, qui laudatur, C.; nobis est domi inopia, foris ae s alienum, mala res, spes multo asperior: d. quid reliqui habemus præter miseram animam?, Sa.; d. hæc (Pelopidæ) fuit altera persona Thebis, N.; d. sit quidvis, simplex duntaxat et unum, Hor.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Först</text:span></text:span> (= demum): quo quum venerimus, tum d. vivemus; tum d. oratione vestire et ornare; nunc d. amare vid eor; is d. honos mihi videri solet, C.; multo d. die Cæsar (id) per exploratores cognovit; octavo d. mense, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dens,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tand:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men., hos menniskor och djur:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> primores, Pn.; adversi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framtänder),</text:span> C.; canini <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ögontänder),</text:span> Varr.; maxillares, Ce.; genuini <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kindtänder),</text:span> C.; d-bus mandere, C.; infrendere, Vg.; aliæ bestiæ d-bus se tutantur; d-ium crepitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skallrande med -),</text:span> C.; d. Indus, Libycus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(elfenben),</text:span> Ov.; d-es solidi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hela),</text:span> concavi, duplices, exserti, cariosi, foetidi; d-es cadunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fällas);</text:span> d-es evellere, eruere, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck (gnagande tand) för: tadla, förtala:</text:span> alqm maledico d-e carpere, C.; rodere invido, Hor.; injusto, Ov.; d. leti, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = tandlikt utskott, spets, udd:</text:span> aratri; falcis; ancoræ, Vg.; pectinis, Varr.; serræ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plogbill:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentarpăga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. hybr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tång, hwarmed tänder uttagas:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som har tänder:</text:span></text:span> mulier, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taggig:</text:span></text:span> crates, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. charta d-a: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med tand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (instrument) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">glattad:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten tand:</text:span> Ap.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">architecturstycke,</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taggig, spetsig:</text:span></text:span> serra, Col.; forceps, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭfrangĭbŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭfrangĭbŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tandbräcka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om person (comiskt) och instrument:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭfrĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (frico): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pulver, hwarmed tänder gnidas l. poleras:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentĭlĕgus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tandsamlare l. -plockare (som får plocka upp sina utslagna tånder):</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Få tänder:</text:span></text:span> tarde d-entes pueri, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. auribus perhauriendum est, ne dentes d-iant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärka?;</text:span> comice <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hunger?),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tändernas framkomst:</text:span></text:span> ea res mire prodest d-i, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dentiscalpium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tandpetare:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har twenne tandrader besatta:</text:span> hostia, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twåspetsig, -bladig:</text:span></text:span> ferrum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offerdjur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">får),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som har begge tandraderna fullsatta</text:span> (quæ superioribus et inferioribus est dentibus, Paul. Diac.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">annan härledning se</text:span> Gell. XVI. 6); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fullwuxet offerdjur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (får):</text:span> mactare lectas de more b-es, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hacka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med twenne blad:</text:span> Vg., Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bĭdental</text:span>, ālis <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af blixten träffadt ställe eller föremål, öfwer hwilket ett får</text:span> (bidens) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offrats:</text:span> movere triste b., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēdento</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slå ut tänderna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beröfwa tänderna:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ēdentŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tandlös;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kraftlös:</text:span></text:span> vetula; vinum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Quădrĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fyrtandad, fyrspetsig:</text:span></text:span> rastrum, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tretaggig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spetsig:</text:span></text:span> rastrum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭdens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Treudd, harpun,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> brukad af fiskare; deraf attribut för hafsguden Neptunus:</text:span> mihi - imperium pelagi sævusque t. sorte datus; levat ipse t-i (naves) et vastas aperit Syrtes, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭdentĭfer</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭdentĭger</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trĭdentĭpŏtens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Treuddbäraren, den med treudden mäktige</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rådande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> epithet till Neptunus:</text:span> Ov., Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Densus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> rarus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">synon.</text:span> creber):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät, tjock, tätt packad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stående:</text:span></text:span> silvæ, sæpes, hostes, Cs.; aër, Hor.; d-is incurrimus armis, Vg.; ignes, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tätt besatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> loca sæpibus, C. (poēt.); corpora sætis, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> d-us sententiis Euripides; d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tankediger)</text:span> Thucydides, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som sker, inträffar med korta mellanskof:</text:span> pericula, Ov.; ictus, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dense</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stående l. följande på hwartannat):</text:span> C., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Denseo</text:span>, 2.: 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtäta; ställa, packa, tränga tätt tillsammans, -hopa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (låta komma, följa tätt på hwartannat):</text:span> ignes poterunt d-ri rarique relinqui, Lucr.; lac d-etur, Pn.; agmina d-entur campis, Vg.; mixta juvenum ac senum d-entur funera, Hor. - lenta manu spargens hastilia d-et, Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ofta wacklar läsarten mellan</text:span> densere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> densare.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Densētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Densĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Täthet:</text:span></text:span> humoris, Pn.; sententiarum, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Denso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtäta; sammantränga, packa; göra tidt och ofta:</text:span></text:span> ordines; scuta, L.; tenebræ d-antur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> -entur), Vg.; āer, Qu.; ictus, Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Addenseo</text:span>, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Addenso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanpacka, förtäta:</text:span></text:span> extremi a-ent (-ant) aciem, Vg.; aqua a-atur, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condensus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tät; tätt packad, sammanträngd:</text:span></text:span> nubila, Lucr.; acies, L.; c-æ atrā tempestate columbæ; puppes, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tätt besatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med -:</text:span> vallis arboribus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condenseo</text:span>, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condenso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtäta; tätt sammantränga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">pressa:</text:span></text:span> aër se c-t, Lucr.; caseum c-re, Col.; pedites, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Perdensus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket tät:</text:span></text:span> humus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prædensus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">owanligt tät:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Dent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dens.<text:line-break/>Denuo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Novus. <text:line-break/>Denus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Deni, Decem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ēōis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Deo’s dotter, Proserpina.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēōĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör Ceres.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕorsum,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> verto, vorsus, q. v.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedåt, (nedåtwändt):</text:span></text:span> sursum d.; clivus d. versus est, Ter.; d. ferri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Depalatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pālus.<text:line-break/>Depeciscor (-pectus) = Depac . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pago.<text:line-break/>Depecul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Peculium.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēpĕtīgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utslag:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Depilatus, -pilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pilus.<text:line-break/>Deplexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Plecto.<text:line-break/>Deplumis, Depontani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pluma, Pons.<text:line-break/>Deposit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pono. <text:line-break/>Deprehensio, Depress . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> -primo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Prehendo, Premo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Depso,</text:span> psui, pstum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knåda; garfwa:</text:span></text:span> farinam; coria, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Depstīcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: panis, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Condepso</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanknåda:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Depuls . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Depello, Pello.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēpȳgis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (framstående) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bakdel:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>erbes, ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslagsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ercĕtis, is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ercĕto, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">syrisk gudomlighet.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Deripio, Deris . . ., Derosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rapio, Rideo, Rodo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">D</text:span>ertōna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Ligurien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Deruptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rumpo.<text:line-break/>Descendo, Descens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scando.<text:line-break/>Descript . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Describo, Scribo.<text:line-break/>Desecro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sacer. <text:line-break/>Desert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Desero, II. Sero.<text:line-break/>Deses, Desideo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sedeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēsīdĕro,</text:span> 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Considero): 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Längta efter; åtrå, åstunda, söka, önska, fordra:</text:span></text:span> noctes diesque me ames, me d-es, Ter.; d-ndo cruciari, angi; d-o audire; (considerandum putavi), utrum amicitia propter imbecillitatem et inopiam d-ta sit, an - esset causa magis ab ipsa natura profecta; gloriam d-at mercedem rerum gestarum; quod ipsi non tribuunt, ab amicis d-ant; neque hanc disputationem a Crasso d-bam; hanc ego absolutionem in oratore d-ns injuste facio; num epilogum d-amus?, C.; imperium; a milite modestiam, Cs.; si beneficia d-nda erant, uti debitis uterer (vellem), Sa.; d-tem, quod satis est, non tumultuosum solli-</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>